Ukwanda okusheshayo kwesibalo esihlanganisiwe sesifo se-coronavirus (i-COVID-19) e-European Union/European Economic Area nase-United Kingdom, kusukela ngo-1 Januwari kuya ku-15 Mashi 2020
Izinga lokuqhamuka kwezigameko zesifo se-coronavirus (i-COVID-19) libonisa ukuthambekela okufanayo emazweni e-European Union/European Economic Area nase-United Kingdom okuqinisekisa ukuthi, nakuba kusesigabeni esihlukile kuye ngezwe, ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luqhubeka ngokushesha kuwo wonke amazwe.
Ngokusekelwe kokuhlangenwe nakho okuvela e-Italy, amazwe, izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okugxile kufanele akhulise ukulungela kwawo ukwamukela ukwanda kweziguli ezine-COVID-19 ezizodinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, ikakhulukazi ukunakekelwa okugxile.
Ngo-31 Disemba 2019, kwaqashelwa iqembu lamacala omdlavuza wamaphaphu angenayo imbangela engaziwa eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
Ngo-9 Januwari 2020, iChina Center for Disease Control and Prevention yabika ukuthi i-agent ebangela lesi sifo yi-coronavirus entsha manje ebizwa ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, lesi sifo esibangelwa ukutheleleka yi-SARS-CoV-2 saqanjwa ngokuthi isifo se-coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubufakazi obukhona kuze kube manje ukuthi abantu abangaba ngu-80% abane-COVID-19 banesifo esincane, okungukuthi, ukutheleleka kwezindlela zokuphefumula noma ngaphandle kwesifo samaphaphu, futhi iningi labo liyaphulukana naso.
Ezimweni ezingaba ngu-14%, i-COVID-19 iba isifo esibi kakhulu esidinga ukulaliswa esibhedlela kuyilapho ama-6% asele eba nesifo esibucayi esidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile.
Ukufa kweziguli ezilaliswe esibhedlela ngenxa ye-COVID-19 cishe kungu-4%.
Kulolu cwaningo, sihlola ukuthambekela kokugcwala kwe-COVID-19 ezweni ngalinye le-European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) nase-United Kingdom (UK) futhi sikuqhathanise nalokho kwesifundazwe saseHubei, eChina.
Siphinde siqhathanise inani lamanje lamacala e-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK nalawo ase-Italy phakathi kuka-31 Januwari15 Mashi 2020.
Amacala e-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Ngemva kweChina, i-COVID-19 yasakazeka ngokwengeziwe futhi isimo esiphuthumayo sobhadane lwe-COVID-19 emhlabeni wonke njengamanje silandela leso sezwe.
Ngo-March 11, 2020, uMqondisi-Jikelele weNhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba (i-WHO) wamemezela ukuthi i-COVID-19 iyisifo esiwumqedazwe.
Umagazini i-Eurosurveillance 2020, ka-March 5, ubika ukuthi u-Spiteri nabanye babika ngecala lokuqala laseYurophu eliqinisekisiwe le-COVID-19 ngokwencazelo yecala le-WHO.
E-EU/EEA, amacala amathathu okuqala aqinisekisiwe abikwa yiFrance ngo-24 Januwari 2020 kubantu ababuya eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
Kusukela ngo-15 Mashi 2020, amacala e-COVID-19 abonwe kuwo wonke amazwe angama-30 e-EU/EEA nase-United Kingdom (UK), lapho phakathi kuka-31 Disemba 2019 nalolo suku kufakwe, kwabika amacala angu-39,768 nokufa kwabantu abangu-1727, kanti amacala angu-17,750 nokufa kwabantu abangu-1441 kwavela e-Italy kuphela.
Ukuthola inani elihlanganisiwe kanye nokugcwala okuhlanganisiwe kwamacala e-COVID-19
E-European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), izibalo zezigameko ze-COVID-19 eziye zabikwa ezweni ngalinye emhlabeni wonke, ezitholakala emithonjeni esemthethweni kuphela njenge-Ministry of Health yamazwe, iziphathimandla zezempilo zikazwelonke nezesifunda kanye ne-WHO, zibuyekezwa nsuku zonke ngo-8:00 ekuseni.
Le mininingwane yasetshenziselwa ukuhlola ukuthambekela kwe-COVID-19 e-EU/EEA nase-UK, nokuqhathanisa nalokho e-Italy.
Njengommeleli wokwanda kwamacala asebenzayo e-COVID-19, sibale izigameko ezihlanganisiwe ze-COVID-19 ezinezinsuku eziyi-14, ngaleyo ndlela sicabangela inkambo yemvelo ye-COVID-19, ezweni ngalinye le-EU/EEA nase-UK, phakathi nenkathi ka-1 Januwari-15 Mashi 2020.
Siphinde saveza inani elihlanganisiwe lamacala azisiwe ezweni ngalinye ngo-15 Mashi 2020 ngo-8: 00 ekuseni uma liqhathaniswa nelase-Italy esikhathini sango-31 Januwari-15 Mashi 2020.
Ukuthambekela kwe-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Izitayela zezinsuku ezingu-14 eziqoshiwe zokugcwala kwamacala e-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK ngokuvamile zilandela lezo zesifundazwe saseHubei (eChina) (Umdwebo 1).
E-EU/EEA nase-UK jikelele, izinga lokuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 laqala ukwanda cishe ngo-21 kuFebhuwari futhi laphinde landa kakhulu cishe ngo-28 kuFebhuwari 2020 (Izinto ezengeziwe).
Lokhu kwakubangelwa kakhulu ukwanda okusheshayo kwezinga lamacala abikiwe avela e-Italy, kodwa wonke amanye amazwe e-EU/EEA ne-UK abonisa ukuthambekela okufanayo kokwanda kokwanda kwezigameko eziqoqiwe ze-COVID-19 (Izinto ezengeziwe).
Umdwebo 2 ukhombisa inani lamacala e-COVID-19, emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK uma liqhathaniswa nalawo ase-Italy esikhathini sika-31 Januwari-15 Mashi 2020.
Ibonisa ukuthi, ngo-15 Mashi ngo-8:00 ekuseni, amanye amazwe angu-15 e-EU/EEA ne-UK ayesevele ebike inani eliphelele lamacala eliqhathaniswa nelase-Italy emasontweni amathathu nje adlule noma ngaphansi.
Imiphumela yethu ibonisa ukuthi inani lamacala abikiwe e-COVID-19 liyanda ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Izitayela ezibonwe ekwandeni kwe-COVID-19 zibonisa ukuthi ubhadane luqhubeka ngesivinini esifanayo kuwo wonke amazwe.
Lokhu kwenzeka naphezu kokuba amazwe esezigabeni ezihlukene, ukuhlukahluka kwezimpendulo zezempilo yomphakathi kazwelonke, futhi mhlawumbe izincazelo ezahlukene zamacala emazweni kanye nezinqubo ezahlukene zokukhetha iziguli okumele zihlolwe ukuze kuqinisekiswe i-COVID-19, kuhlanganise nokuhlolwa kokubamba.
Ekuqaleni kuka-March 2020, odokotela ezindaweni ezithintekile e-Italy bachaza isimo lapho iziguli ezingaba ngu-10% ezine-COVID-19 zazidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile futhi imithombo yezindaba yabika ukuthi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile kulezi zindawo zase zifinyelele umthamo wazo omkhulu.
Idatha yokwamukelwa kwamacala e-COVID-19 esibhedlela kanye/noma e-unit yokunakekelwa okujulile okwamanje iyatholakala ezingeni le-EU/EEA ngamacala angu-6% no-1% kuphela, ngokulandelana (idatha ayiboniswa).
Kodwa-ke, kufanele ziqoqwe ngendlela ehlelekile ukuze zengeze idatha yamanje yokuqapha egxile enanini lamacala abikiwe kanye nenani lokufa.
Ucwaningo olwenziwa ngo-201011 lwabonisa ukwehluka okukhulu ekutholakaleni kwemibhede yokunakekela abagula kakhulu nabanakekeli abaphakathi eYurophu, kusukela ku-29,2 eJalimane kuya ku-4,2 imibhede kubantu abangu-100 000 ePortugal.
Lokhu kusho ukuthi amazwe angase abe nezinsiza eziningi noma ezimbalwa kune-Italy (imibhede engu-12,5 yokunakekela enzulu neyesikhashana kubantu abangu-100 000 ngo-201011).
Izimo zokumodela ezihlobene nokugcwala kwamandla ezempilo, ngezilinganiso zezwe ngalinye le-EU/EEA ne-UK zokwanda kwamacala e-COVID-19 alaliswa esibhedlela ahlobene nengozi engu-&gt; 90% yokweqa amandla emibhede yokunakekelwa okujulile, zinikezwa ekubuyekezweni kwesithupha kokuhlolwa kwengozi okusheshayo kwe-ECDC nge-COVID-19.
Njengoba amacala kuze kube manje aye ahlangana ezindaweni ezithile emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK, futhi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okugula kakhulu ngokuvamile zisebenzela abantu ababekelwe imingcele ethile, ulwazi mayelana namacala nemibhede yokunakekelwa okugula kakhulu kufanele lube khona ezingeni le-Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Okuhlangenwe nakho okuvela e-Italy kanye nezindlela ezikhona kwamanye amazwe zibonisa ukuthi ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luqhubeka ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Ngakho-ke, amazwe, izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa kwabantu abagula kakhulu kufanele azilungiselele isimo sokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nokwanda kwesibalo seziguli ezine-COVID-19 ezidinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, ikakhulukazi ukunakekelwa kwabantu abagula kakhulu, njengalokhu okwenzeka ezindaweni ezithintekile zase-Italy.
Njengoba kukhonjisiwe ekuhlolweni kwengozi okusheshayo kwakamuva kwe-ECDC, indlela esheshayo, esebenzayo futhi ebanzi ibalulekile ukubambezela ukusabalala kwe-SARS-COV-2, ngokushintshela endleleni yokuvimbela ibe yindlela yokunciphisa, njengoba ukwanda okusheshayo okulindelekile kwenani lamacala kungase kunikeze abenzi bezinqumo nezibhedlela isikhathi esanele sokuqonda, ukwamukela nokulungisa impendulo yabo ngokufanele uma kungasetshenziswa kusenesikhathi.
Ukuhlolwa kwezingozi okusheshayo kubuye kubhale nezinyathelo zezempilo zomphakathi zokunciphisa umthelela walolu bhubhane.
Kunesikhathi esifushane lapho amazwe enethuba lokukhulisa imizamo yawo yokulawula ukuze anciphise ukusabalala kwe-SARS-CoV-2 futhi anciphise ingcindezi ekunakekelweni kwezempilo.
Uma lokhu kungenzeki, kungenzeka ukuthi izinhlelo zezempilo zamanye amazwe e-EU/EEA zizobhekana nokwanda okukhulu kweziguli ezidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile ezinsukwini noma emasontweni azayo.
Ukuqubuka kwesifo seCoronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), okubangelwa i-severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kuze kube manje kubulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3 000 futhi kwafaka abantu abangaphezu kuka-80,000 eChina nakwezinye izindawo emhlabeni, okwaholela enhlekeleleni kubantu.
Ngokufanayo negciwane layo elifanayo, i-SARS-CoV, eyabangela i-SARS ezinkulungwaneni zabantu ngo-2003, i-SARS-CoV-2 nayo ingadluliselwa izimpukane futhi ibangele izimpawu ezifanayo ngendlela efanayo.
Nokho, i-COVID-19 inesifo esibi kakhulu futhi iyabulala kunesifo se-SARS kodwa idluliselwa kakhulu futhi ithinta abantu abadala kunentsha futhi ithinta amadoda amaningi kunabesifazane.
Ngenxa yokwanda ngokushesha kwezincwadi ezikhuluma ngalesi sifo esisha, lesi sihloko sizama ukuhlinzeka ukubuyekeza okufike ngesikhathi nokuphelele kwalolu cwaningo oluthuthuka ngokushesha.
Sizohlanganisa izinto eziyisisekelo mayelana nesifo, izizathu, amagciwane, ukuxilongwa, ukwelashwa, ukubonwa kusengaphambili nokuvinjelwa kwalesi sifo.
Nakuba kusenezicelo eziningi, sethemba ukuthi lokhu kubuyekezwa kuyosiza ekuqondeni nasekucedeni lesi sifo esisongelayo.
UMkhosi Wentwasahlobo ngoJanuwari 25, 2020 ube yisikhumbuzo esingakaze sibe khona futhi ongasoze wasikhohlwa kuwo wonke amaShayina anxuswa ukuba ahlale endlini kulo lonke leli holide nangamasonto amaningi ngemva kwalokho ngenxa yokuqubuka kwesifo esibangelwa amagciwane.
Leli gciwane lifana kakhulu ne-coronavirus (CoV) eyabangela ukuqubuka kwesifo esibi kakhulu sokuphefumula (i-SARS) ngo-2003; ngakho-ke, yaqanjwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yi-World Health Organization (WHO) ngoFebhuwari 11, 2020, futhi isifo esihambisana nayo sabizwa ngokuthi i-CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Lesi sifo saqala eWuhan, eChina, futhi ngokushesha sasakazeka kulo lonke izwe safinyelela kwamanye amazwe angaba ngu-50 emhlabeni wonke.
Kusukela ngo-March 2, 2020, leli gciwane liye laholela emacaleni angaphezu kuka-80,000 aqinisekisiwe e-COVID-19, iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-40,000 zadedelwa kanti iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-3,000 zafa.
I-WHO ixwayisa ngokuthi i-COVID-19 isitha somphakathi esingu-1 futhi kungenzeka inamandla kunobuphekula.
NgokwePubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), esikhathini esingaphansi kwezinyanga ezimbili, sekushicilelwe amaphepha angaphezu kuka-200 nge-COVID-19 kuhlanganise ne-virology, i-epidemiology, i-etiology, ukuxilongwa, kanye nokwelashwa kwayo kusukela embikweni wokuqala ngoJanuwari 7, 2020 owanquma ukulandelana kwegciwane elihlukaniswe ezigulini eziningi.
Lesi sibuyekezo sizama ukufingqa inqubekela phambili yocwaningo emkhakheni omusha futhi othuthuka ngokushesha.
Noma nini lapho kungenzeka, sizozama ukuqhathanisa i-COVID-19 ne-SARS kanye nesinye isifo esibangelwa i-CoV, i-Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, ukuqubuka kuka-2012).
Sizoxoxa nangalokho esikufundile kuze kube manje ngokuvimbela nokulinganisa lesi sifo kanye neminye imibuzo esisele kodwa ephuthumayo.
Ama-CoV ayebhekwa njengamagciwane angabulali kubantu, ikakhulukazi abangela cishe u-15% wokubanda okuvamile 4.
Nokho, kuleli khulu leminyaka, siye sabhekana nama-CoV abantu anezifo eziningi kabili, okungukuthi, i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, eyabangela ukuqubuka ekuqaleni eChina ngo-2003 naseSaudi Arabia ngo-2012, ngokulandelana, futhi ngokushesha yasakazekela kwamanye amazwe amaningi ngamanani amabi kakhulu okugula nokufa.
Ngakho-ke, i-COVID-19 yamanje ingukugqashuka kwe-CoV kwesithathu emlandweni obhaliwe wabantu.
Njengoba kuboniswe ku-Fig. Fig.1,1, amaqembu omdlavuza wamaphaphu owawunemvelaphi engaziwa abikwa okokuqala eWuhan ngoDisemba 31, 2019 eChina National Health Commission.
Ngemva kwezinsuku ezingu-7 kwavulwa ukulandelana kwe-CoV.
NgoJanuwari 15, 2020 kwabikwa icala lokuqala lokufa eWuhan.
Phakathi naleso sikhathi, lesi sifo sasakazekela ngokushesha emadolobheni angomakhelwane, ezifundazweni nasemazweni.
Ngo-January 20, kwabikwa ukuthi kunabantu abahlinzeka ngezempilo abathelelekile, okusikisela ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi abantu bangadluliselana.
Ngo-January 23, idolobha laseWuhan lavalwa futhi zonke izinto zokuhamba zomphakathi zamiswa.
Ngo-January 24, ucwaningo lokuqala lomtholampilo ngesifo lwabika ukuthi, ezigulini ezingu-41 ezinezimo eziqinisekisiwe, ezingu-21 kuphela ezazithintane ngqo nemakethe yezilwane zasolwandle yaseWuhan okwakuthiwa yindawo okuqala kuyo lesi sifo esivela emthonjeni wezilwane ongaziwa.
Ngo-January 30, i-WHO yamemezela ukuthi lesi sifo siyisimo esiphuthumayo emhlabeni wonke.
