Ukushisa ngokuvamile kuwuphawu oluyinhloko nolokuqala lwe-COVID-19, olungahambisana nokungabi nazimpawu noma ezinye izimpawu ezinjengokukhwehlela okomile, ukuphefumula kanzima, ubuhlungu bemisipha, isiyezi, ikhanda, ubuhlungu bomphimbo, i-rhinorrhea, ubuhlungu besifuba, isifo sohudo, isicanucanu nokuhlanza.
