Iziguli zivame ukuba nesifo samaphaphu esingavamile, ukulimala okukhulu kwamaphaphu, kanye nesifo sokucindezeleka okubangelwa ukuphefumula (ARDS).
Lapho i-ARDS isenzeka, ukuvuvukala okungalawulwa, ukwanda koketshezi, kanye ne-fibrosis eqhubekayo kuphazamisa kakhulu ukushintshana kwamagesi.
Ukungasebenzi kahle kwama-pneumocyte ohlobo I nohlobo II kunciphisa izinga le-surfactant futhi kwenze kube nokungezwani komhlaba, ngaleyo ndlela kunciphise ikhono lamaphaphu lokwanda futhi kwandise ingozi yokuwa kwamaphaphu.
