Sethemba ukuthi, le ndlela entsha ingakuthuthukisa kakhulu ukuzwela nokusebenziseka kahle uma iqinisekiswa kumasampula omtholampilo.
Ngenxa yokuntuleka kokuhlangenwe nakho nge-CoV entsha, odokotela ngokuyinhloko banganikeza ukunakekelwa okusekelayo ezigulini ze-COVID-19, ngenkathi bezama izindlela zokwelapha ezihlukahlukene ezisetshenzisiwe noma ezihlongozwayo ngaphambili zokwelapha ezinye i-CoV ezifana ne-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV nezinye izifo ezibangelwa amagciwane (Ithebula (Ithebula2).2).
Lezi zindlela zokwelapha zihlanganisa ukwelashwa kwamanje nokungaba khona ngezidakamizwa ezilwa namagciwane, ama-immunosuppressants, ama-steroid, i-plasma ezigulini esezilulama, imithi yamaShayina nokusekelwa ngokwengqondo.
