Noma kunjalo, ukungasebenzi kahle nokuphelelwa amandla okuphefumula kuyisongo esikhulu ezigulini futhi kuyimbangela eyinhloko yokufa.
Ngakho-ke, ukusekela ukuphefumula kubalulekile ekunciphiseni izimpawu nasekusindiseni ukuphila futhi kuhlanganisa ukwelashwa okuvamile komoya-mpilo, umoya-mpilo ophakeme, umoya-mpilo ongenabungozi, nokuhogela umoya ngokuya ngobukhulu besifo.
Iziguli ezinezimpawu ezibucayi zokuphefumula kufanele zisekelwe nge-extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO), indlela yokwelashwa yokwelashwa kwenhliziyo noma yokuphefumula esongela ukuphila.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukugcina ibhalansi ye-electrolyte, ukuvimbela nokwelapha ukutheleleka kwesibili nokushaqeka kwe-septic, nokuvikela imisebenzi yezitho ezibalulekile nakho kubalulekile ezigulini ze-SARS-CoV-2.
Kuyaziwa ukuthi isiphepho sama-cytokine sibangelwa ukusabela ngokweqile kwesimiso somzimba sokuzivikela ezigulini ze-SARS ne-MERS.
Isiphepho se-cytokine siyindlela yokuphendula okuvuvukalayo okubangelwa ukukhululwa kwama-cytokine amaningi kuhlanganise ne-TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, ne-MCP-1.
