Ngakho, abahlinzeki bezempilo kufanele futhi bagqoke izivikelo zobuso ezibonakalayo noma izibuko lapho besebenza neziguli.
Emphakathini jikelele ezindaweni ezithintekile noma ezingase zithinteke, kunconywa kakhulu ukuthi wonke umuntu ageze izandla zakhe ngensipho yokubulala amagciwane kaningi kunokujwayelekile, azame ukuhlala endlini ukuze azihlukanise futhi anciphise ukuxhumana nabantu abangase batheleleke.
Amamitha amathathu abhekwa njengobude obufanele abantu abafanele bahlale kude nesiguli.
Lezi zinyathelo ziyizindlela eziphumelelayo zokunciphisa ingozi yokutheleleka kanye nokuvimbela ukusabalala kwegciwane.
Nakuba i-SARS-CoV-2 yafika njengegciwane elisha emhlabeni wabantu, ukufana kwayo okuphezulu ne-SARS-CoV njengoba kwabikwa ngo-7 Januwari 2020 bekufanele kubangele ukuxwayisa okukhulu eChina ngokususelwa enkumbulweni yayo ejulile yokuqubuka kwe-SARS ngo-2003.
Nokho, kwaze kwaba ngo-19 January 2020 lapho umqondisi we-Center of Disease Control yaseWuhan aduduza izakhamuzi ngokuthi leli gciwane elisha linobuthi obuncane futhi linamandla alinganiselwe okuzala kusuka kumuntu kuya kumuntu nokuthi akuyona inkinga ukuvimbela nokuvimbela lesi sifo.
Lo myalezo wawususa kakhulu uvalo emphakathini, ikakhulukazi lapho izwe lonke lilungiselela uMkhosi Wentwasahlobo, futhi isikhathi esibucayi sokubamba lesi sifo esilinganisweni esincane eWuhan saphuthelwa.
Izikhungo zokulawula izifo eChina zingase zithathe lesi sifundo esinzima futhi zenze izinguquko ezibalulekile esikhathini esizayo.
Ngokwesibonelo, lezi zinhlaka kufanele (1) ziqaphele lapho zenza izimemezelo zomphakathi njengoba wonke amazwi ebalulekile ezakhamuzini futhi zingashintsha isimo sazo sengqondo nezinqumo; (2) ziqaphele futhi zisabele olwazini olungavamile oluvela emitholampilo kunokuba zilinde imibiko esemthethweni evela kodokotela noma ezikhulwini; (3) zinqande kakhulu ukuvimbela ubhadane olungaba khona esigabeni salo sokuqala kunokuba zizame ukududuza umphakathi; futhi (4) zivame ukukhipha imishini eqondile nephumelelayo yokwandisa ukuqwashisa komphakathi ngezifo eziwumqedazwe nokuhlola nokuthuthukisa uhlelo lokuphendula lomphakathi ngezikhathi ezithile.
Ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 okubangelwa igciwane elisha i-SARS-CoV-2 kwaqala ekupheleni kuka-December 2019.
Ezinyangeni ezingaphansi kwezingu-2, isakazeke kulo lonke elaseChina nakwamanye amazwe angaba ngu-50 emhlabeni wonke ngesikhathi kulotshwa lesi sihloko.
Njengoba leli gciwane lifana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV futhi izimpawu nazo zifana phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 kuye kwabangela ukuba kube nomuzwa wokuthi i-SARS iyaphinda.
Nokho, kunokwehluka okuthile okuphawulekayo phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, okubalulekile ekuvimbeleni ubhadane nasekwelapheni iziguli.
I-COVID-19 ithinta abantu asebekhulile abaningi kunentsha futhi ithinta amadoda amaningi kunabesifazane, futhi izinga lokuqina nokufa nalo liphezulu kubantu asebekhulile kunentsha.
I-SARS inabantu abaningi abafayo kune-COVID-19 (10.91% uma kuqhathaniswa no-1.44%).
Iziguli ze-COVID-19 zidlulisela igciwane ngisho nalapho zingenazo izimpawu kanti iziguli ze-SARS zivame ukukwenza lokho lapho zigula kakhulu, okubangela ubunzima obukhulu kakhulu ekuvimbeleni ukusabalala kwe-COVID-19 kune-SARS.
Lokhu kuchaza ngokwengxenye ukuthi kungani i-SARS-CoV-2 isakazeka ngokushesha okukhulu futhi kabanzi kune-SARS-CoV.
Ukuhlolwa kwe-RNA okuvamile kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungaba okungalungile kwezinye iziguli ze-COVID-19.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, iziguli eziphulukisiwe zingaphinde zibe naleli gciwane.
Lezi zinto ezitholakele zandisa kakhulu ingozi yokusabalala kwegciwane.
Njengoba kunikezwe inqubekela phambili esheshayo ocwaningweni lwe-COVID-19, kusasele izinkinga eziningi ezibalulekile okufanele zixazululwe, ngokulandelayo:
Ivela kuphi i-SARS-CoV-2?
Nakuba i-96% ye-homologue yezakhi zofuzo itholakale phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nama-COV amabili afana namalulwane, asikwazi ukufinyelela esiphethweni sokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ivela kumalulwane.
Yisiphi isilwane esasiwuhlobo oluphakathi kokudlulisela igciwane kumuntu, sisho, amalulwane?
Ngaphandle kokwazi izimpendulo zemibuzo engu-1 no-2, asikwazi ukuwuqeda ngokuphumelelayo lo mkhuba, futhi ukuqubuka kungaphinde kwenzeke noma nini.
Nakuba ukuhlaziywa kwamangqamuzana nokuhlaziywa kwamakhemikhali okuphilayo kuye kwabonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ibopha i-ACE2, igciwane lingena kanjani ngqo emangqamuzaneni omgudu wokuphefumula futhi libangele izinguquko ezingokwenyama ezalandela?
Ingabe leli gciwane liyazibopha futhi nangamaseli akhipha i-ACE2 kwezinye izitho?
Ngaphandle kwezimpendulo ezicacile zale mibuzo, asikwazi ukuthola ukuxilongwa okusheshayo nokunembile nokwelashwa okuphumelelayo.
Lolu bhubhane luyoqhubeka isikhathi esingakanani?
Leli gciwane liguquka kanjani ngokwemvelo lapho lisakazeka phakathi kwabantu?
Ingabe iyoba ubhadane lomhlaba wonke, iphele njenge-SARS noma ibuye njalo njengesifo somkhuhlane?
Kubalulekile kodwa kungathatha isikhathi ukufuna izimpendulo zale mibuzo engenhla neminye eminingi.
Nokho, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kudingekani, asinakukhetha ngaphandle kokuqeda lesi sifo ngokushesha okukhulu futhi sibuyisele ukuphila kwethu kokujwayelekile.
Imvelaphi ye-zoonotic yama-coronavirus abantu
Ukuguquka nokuzivumelanisa nezimo kuye kwaholela ekuziphendukeleni kwemvelo okuhlangene kwama-coronavirus (ama-CoV) kanye nezilwane eziwuphethe, kuhlanganise nabantu, izinkulungwane zeminyaka.
Ngaphambi kuka-2003, ama-CoV amabili abantu (ama-HCoV) ayaziwa ukuthi abangela ukugula okuncane, njengokubanda okuvamile.
Ukuqubuka kwesifo esibi kakhulu sokuphefumula (i-SARS) kanye nesifo sokuphefumula saseMpumalanga Ephakathi (i-MERS) kuye kwaveza ukuthi ukutheleleka yi-HCV kungabulala kanjani.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 eChina ephakathi ekupheleni kuka-2019 kwaphinde kwafaka ama-CoV obala futhi kwasimangaza ngokudluliseka kwawo okuphezulu kodwa kwehlisa izifo uma kuqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV engumfowabo.
Ukutheleleka nge-HCoV kuyisifo esibangelwa yizilwane futhi ukuqonda imvelaphi ye-zoonotic yama-HCoV kungasisiza kahle.
Ama-HCoV amaningi avela emalulwaneni lapho engenawo amagciwane.
Ama-HCoV athile nawo ayaziwa ukuthi angamakhosikazi aphakathi.
Ukuhlonza izilwane eziwumbungazi kunemiphumela eqondile ekuvimbeleni izifo zabantu.
Ukucwaninga ukusebenzisana kwe-Cov-host ezilwaneni nakho kunganikeza ukuqonda okubalulekile nge-Cov pathogenesis kubantu.
Kulokhu kubuyekezwa, siveza ukubuka konke kolwazi olukhona mayelana nama-HCoV ayisikhombisa, sigxile emlandweni wokutholwa kwawo kanye nemvelaphi yawo ye-zoonotic nokudluliselwa phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Okubalulekile, siqhathanisa futhi sifanise ama-HCoV ahlukene ngokombono wokuziphendukela kwegciwane nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwezakhi zofuzo.
Isifo samanje se-Covid-19 (COVID-19) sixoxwa ngaso kulo mongo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izidingo zokushintsha kwe-host ngokuphumelelayo nemiphumela yokuziphendukela kwegciwane ebucayi besifo nayo iyagqanyiswa.
Ama-Coronavirus (ama-CoV) angawomndeni we-Coronaviridae, ohlanganisa iqembu lamagciwane e-RNA agqokwa, anokuzwela okuhle, anezintambo ezilodwa.
La magciwane anezakhi zofuzo ezinkulu kakhulu ezingama-26 kuya ku-32 kilobases phakathi kwamagciwane e-RNA abizwa ngokuthi CoVs ngenxa yokuma kwawo okufana nomqhele ngaphansi kwesibonakhulu se-electron.
Ngokwesakhiwo, ama-CoV anezinhlayiyana zofuzo ezingalingani ezihlanganyela inhlangano efanayo.
Cishe izingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu ze-genome ziqukethe amafreyimu amabili amakhulu avulekile (i-ORF1a ne-ORF1b), ahunyushelwa kuma-pp1a nama-pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Ama-polyprotein aqhubeka esebenza ukuze akhiqize ama-protein angu-16 angawokwakheka, abizwa ngokuthi i-nsp1~16.
Ingxenye esele ye-genome iqukethe ama-ORF amaprotheni esakhiwo, kuhlanganise ne-spike (S), envelope (E), i-membrane (M) ne-nucleoprotein (N).
Amaprotheni amaningi angawesekeli ahlukile emlandweni nawo abhalwe ngamakhodi emindeni ehlukene yama-CoV.
Ngokusekelwe umehluko kumakhodi amaprotheni, ama-CoV ahlukaniswa abe izinhlobo ezine (i-alpha-CoV, i-beta-CoV, i-gamma-CoV ne-delta-CoV), phakathi kwazo i-beta-CoV iqukethe ama-HCoV amaningi futhi ihlukaniswe yaba izinhlanga ezine (A, B, C no-D).
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic buye babonisa ukuthi amalulwane nezilwane ezihlushwa amagundane ziwumthombo wezakhi zofuzo we-alpha-CoVs nama-beta-CoVs amaningi, kuyilapho izinyoni ziyizinqolobane eziyinhloko zama-gamma-CoV nama-delta-CoV.
Izinkulungwane zeminyaka, ama-CoV aye adlula njalo imingcele yezinhlobo futhi amanye avele njengama-pathogen abalulekile kubantu.
Kuze kube manje, ama-CoVs ayisikhombisa abantu (ama-HCoVs) ayaziwa.
Phakathi kwazo i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-NL63 yi-alpha-CoVs.
Amanye ama-beta-CoV amahlanu afaka i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1, i-coronavirus yesandulela-kuphefumula esibucayi (i-SARS-CoV), i-coronavirus yesandulela-kuphefumula yaseMpumalanga Ephakathi (i-MERS-CoV) ne-SARS-CoV-2.
I-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 ne-HCoV-NL63 ngokuvamile zibangela izimpawu ezincane, njengokubanda okuvamile kanye/noma isifo sohudo.
Ngokuphambene, i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 esanda kutholakala i-pathogenic kakhulu, ibangela ukutheleleka okunzima emithonjeni yokuphefumula ephansi ezigulini eziningi kakhulu ezinamathuba amaningi okuthuthukisa i-acute respiratory distress syndrome (ARDS) kanye nokubonakaliswa okungaphandle kwamaphaphu.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E, i-B814, lwahlukaniswa nokukhishwa komphimbo kweziguli ezinomkhuhlane ovamile maphakathi nawo-1960.
Kusukela lapho, ulwazi oluningi lwaqoqwa ngezifundo ezibanzi ze-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43, zombili ezibangela izimpawu ezizimele.
Ngempela, umqondo wawamukelwa kabanzi wokuthi ukutheleleka ngama-HCoV ngokuvamile akulimazi kuze kuqubuke i-SARS.
Ukuqubuka kweSARS okwenzeka ngo-2003 kungenye yezinto ezibhubhisa kakhulu emlandweni wamanje, okuthelele abantu abangaphezu kuka-8 000 ngesilinganiso sokufa kwabantu abangaba ngu-10%.
Eminyakeni eyishumi kamuva, ukuqubuka kwesifo sokuphefumula saseMpumalanga Ephakathi (i-MERS) kwabangela ubhadane oluqhubekayo eNhlonhlweni yase-Arabia futhi lwasakazekela emhlabeni wonke.
I-HCoV (2019-nCoV) ka-2019, kamuva eyaqanjwa kabusha ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2, iyimbangela yokuqubuka kwesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19), esibulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3 120 futhi sathelela abantu abangaphezu kuka-91 000 kusukela ngo-March 3, 2020.
I-alamu ibilokhu ikhala futhi umhlaba kufanele ulungiselele ubhadane oluzayo lwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Wonke ama-HCoV ayisikhombisa anomsuka wezilwane ovela kumalulwane, amagundane noma izilwane zasekhaya.
Imigqa eminingi yobufakazi isekela imvelaphi yokuziphendukela kwemvelo yawo wonke ama-HCoV avela kumalulwane, lapho amagciwane ezilungele kahle futhi engenabo ubuthi kodwa ebonisa ukwehluka okukhulu kofuzo.
Ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 lulethe izinselelo ezinkulu kwezokwelapha, ezesayensi, ezenhlalo nezokuziphatha eChina nasemhlabeni jikelele.
Ukulandelela imvelaphi ye-zoonotic yama-HCoVs kunikeza uhlaka lokuqonda umlando wemvelo, amandla ashukumisayo kanye nezici zokunciphisa ukweqa kwezinhlobo.
Lokhu kungaqondisa noma kusize ekufuneni izilwane eziphethe i-SARS-CoV-2, eziphakathi nezandisayo, ezinemiphumela ebalulekile ekuvimbeleni ukuchitheka kwesikhathi esizayo.
Kulokhu kubuyekezwa siveza umbono wemvelaphi ye-zoonotic, ukudluliselwa phakathi kwezinhlobo kanye ne-pathogenesis yama-HCoV.
Ikakhulukazi, sigqamisa futhi sixoxe ngesihloko esivamile sokuthi amagciwane omzali ama-HCoV ngokuvamile awabangelwa izifo emizini yawo yemvelo kodwa aba yizimbangela zezifo ngemva kokudluliselwa phakathi kwezinhlobo kumuntu omusha.
Siphinde sihlaziye ukuthambekela kokuziphendukela kwe-HCoV lapho ukwanda kokudluliselwa ngokuvamile kuza nokwehla kwe-pathogenicity.
Umphumela wokuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 okuqhubekayo nawo uyaxoxwa kulokhu.
Ama-CoV asezilwaneni abelokhu eyaziwa kusukela ngasekupheleni kwawo-1930.
Ngaphambi kokuhlukaniswa kokuqala kwe-HCoV-229E strain B814 kusuka ekukhishweni komphimbo kweziguli ezazinomkhuhlane ovamile, ama-CoV ahlukahlukene ayehlukaniswe ezilwaneni ezihlukahlukene ezitheleleke, kuhlanganise i-turkey, igundane, inkomo, ingulube, ikati nenja.
Emashumini eminyaka adlule, kuye kwahlolwa ama-HCoV ayisikhombisa.
Ukufingqa kafushane umlando wokutholakala kwe-HCoV ngokulandelana kwezikhathi (Ithebula 1) kungaba ngolwazi nokufundisa.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E lwahlukaniswa emathunjini okuphefumula ezigulini ezinesifo somgudu wokuphefumula ongaphezulu ngonyaka we-1966, futhi kamuva lwaguqulwa ukuze lukhule emigqeni yamangqamuzana ephaphu i-WI-38.
Iziguli ezitheleleke nge-HCoV-229E zabonisa izimpawu ezivamile zokubanda, kuhlanganise ikhanda, ukuthimula, ukuzizwa kabi nomphimbo obuhlungu, nomkhuhlane nokukhwehlela okubonwe emacaleni angu-10~20%.
Kamuva ngo-1967, i-HCoV-OC43 yahlukaniswa nesikhumba sezitho zomzimba kanye nokuhamba okuqhubekayo ebuchosheni bamagundane ancelayo.
Izici zokwelashwa zokutheleleka nge-HCoV-OC43 zibonakala zifana nalezo ezibangelwa yi-HCoV-229E, ezingakwazi ukuhlukaniswa ngezibonakaliso nokutheleleka ngezinye izifo ezibangela izifo zokuphefumula ezifana namagciwane omkhuhlane A nama-rhinovirus.
Kokubili i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43 zisakazeka emhlabeni wonke, futhi zivame ukudluliselwa kakhulu ngesikhathi sasebusika esimweni sezulu esipholile.
Ngokuvamile, isikhathi sokufukama kwalezi zigciwane ezimbili singaphansi kwesonto elilodwa, silandelwe ukugula cishe amasonto amabili.
Ngokwesifundo esenziwa kubantu, abantu abaphilile abanegciwane le-HCoV-229E baba nomkhuhlane omncane.
Iziguli ezimbalwa kuphela ezazinamasosha omzimba ayesengozini zabonisa ukutheleleka okunzima emithonjeni yokuphefumula engezansi.
I-SARS, eyaziwa nangokuthi i-atypical pneumonia, yayiwubhubhane lokuqala olubhalwe kahle olubangelwa i-HCoV emlandweni wesintu futhi i-agent ye-etiological yi-SARS-CoV, i-HCoV yesithathu etholakele.
Icala lokuqala le-SARS lingalandelwa emuva ngasekupheleni kuka-2002 esifundazweni saseGuangdong eChina.
Ubhadane lwe-SARS lwabangela ukuba kubikwe iziguli ezingu-8 096 kanye nokufa kwabantu abangu-774, lwasakazeka emazweni amaningi nasemazwekazini.
Ngaphandle kwabasakazayo, kulinganiselwa ukuthi icala ngalinye lingadala cishe amacala amabili wesibili, nesikhathi sokufukama sezinsuku ezingu-4 kuya kwezingu-7 futhi inani eliphakeme kakhulu legciwane livela ngosuku lwe-10 lokugula.
Iziguli ezitheleleka nge-SARS-CoV ekuqaleni zibonisa i-myalgia, ikhanda, umkhuhlane, ukuzizwa kabi nokuthuthumela, bese kulandela i-dyspnea, ukukhwehlela nokucindezeleka kokuphefumula njengezimpawu zokugcina.
I-lymphopenia, ukuphazamiseka kokuhlolwa kokusebenza kwesibindi, nokwanda kwe-creatine kinase kuyizici ezivamile ze-SARS.
Ukulimala kwe-alveolar okuxakanisiwe, ukwanda kwamangqamuzana e-epithelial nokwanda kwama-macrophage nakho kuyabonakala ezigulini ze-SARS.
Cishe iziguli ezingu-20 kuya kwezingu-20% kamuva zidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile nokuphefumula ngomshini.
Ngaphezu komgudu wokuphefumula ophansi, izitho eziningi kuhlanganise nomgudu wokudla, isibindi nezinso nazo zingase zitheleleke kulezi zimo ezinzima, ngokuvamile zihambisana nesiphepho sama-cytokine, okungase kubulale ikakhulukazi ezigulini ezinamasosha omzimba.
Leli gciwane laqala ukuhlukaniswa ngokuhlolwa kwamaphaphu okuvulekile kwesihlobo sesiguli esibhalwe phansi esafika eHong Kong sisuka eGuangzhou.
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, kuye kwenziwa imizamo emikhulu yokucwaninga nge-HCV.
I-HCoV-NL63 yahlukaniswa nengane eneminyaka engu-7 ubudala yaseNetherlands ngasekupheleni kuka-2004.
Ekuqaleni kwatholakala ukuthi yayivame kakhulu ezinganeni ezincane, asebekhulile nasezigulini ezinamasosha omzimba anciphile anezifo zokuphefumula.
Ukuvela kwe-coryza, i-conjunctivitis, umkhuhlane, ne-bronchiolitis kuvamile esifweni esibangelwa i-HCoV-NL63.
Olunye ucwaningo oluzimele lwachaza ukuhlukaniswa kwegciwane elifanayo esibukweni sezinzwa somfana oneminyaka engu-8 ubudala owayenesifo samaphaphu eNetherlands.
Nakuba yabonakala eNetherlands, empeleni isakazeke emhlabeni wonke.
Kulinganiselwa ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 ibangela cishe u-4.7% wezifo ezivamile zokuphefumula, futhi izinga layo eliphakeme lokugqashuka livela ekuqaleni kwehlobo, entwasahlobo nasebusika.
I-HCoV-NL63 ihlotshaniswa ne-laryngitis evimbelayo, eyaziwa nangokuthi i-croup.
Ngalowo nyaka, i-HCoV-HKU1 yahlukaniswa nendoda eneminyaka engu-71 ubudala eyayisesibhedlela ihlushwa i-pneumonia ne-bronchiolitis eHong Kong.
Ngaphandle kwe-pneumonia ne-bronchiolitis etholakala emphakathini, i-HCoV-HKU1 yabikwa ukuthi ihlotshaniswa nokuqina kwesifuba somoya.
Ngokufana ne-HCoV-NL63, i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 yatholakala emhlabeni wonke, ibangela izifo zokuphefumula ezingatheni.
Wonke la ma-HCoV amane atholakala emphakathini aye ahambisana kahle nabantu futhi ngokuvamile mancane amathuba okuba aguquke abangele izifo eziyingozi kakhulu, nakuba izingozi zenzeka ngenxa yezizathu ezingaziwa njengasendabeni engavamile ye-HCoV-NL63 eyisigaba esinamandla kakhulu, okuye kwabikwa ukuthi isanda kubangela ukutheleleka okunzima emithonjeni yokuphefumula ephansi eChina.
Ngokuvamile, lapho la ma-HCoV ethola ikhono lokudlulisela ngempumelelo futhi azigcine ehlala ngaphakathi kwabantu, nawo aba mabi kakhulu noma abe nezinkinga ezingaba khona.
I-MERS-CoV yaqala ukuhlukaniswa ngo-2012 emaphashini esiguli esineminyaka engu-60 ubudala esaba nesifo samaphaphu esibi kanye nokwehluleka kwezinso eSaudi Arabia.
Nakuba iningi lamacala aqinisekiswe elelabhorethri livela eMpumalanga Ephakathi, kuye kwabikwa amacala angenisiwe anezinkinga ezithile ezibangelwa abantu ababesondelene nabo emazweni ahlukahlukene aseYurophu naseTunisia.
Olunye ugqugquzela lwesibili lwenzeka eNingizimu Korea ngo-2015 nezigameko ezingu-186 eziqinisekisiwe.
Izimpawu zomtholampilo ze-MERS zifana nezika-SARS, ezibonakala nge-pneumonia eqhubekayo.
Ngokungafani ne-SARS, iziguli eziningi ezine-MERS nazo zabhekana nokwehluleka kwezinso okukhulu, okuyinto kuze kube manje eyingqayizivele nge-MERS phakathi kwezifo ezibangelwa yi-HCoV.
Iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-30% zinezimpawu zesisu, njengokusheshe uhlelwe yisifo sohudo nokuhlanza.
Kusukela ngoFebhuwari 14, 2020, kwaqashelwa amacala angaphezu kuka-2500 aqinisekisiwe elabhoratri ngesilinganiso esiphezulu sokufa kwabantu abangama-34.4%, okwenza i-MERS-CoV ibe ngelinye lama-virus abhubhisa kakhulu abantu.
Phakathi naphakathi noDisemba 2019 kuya ngasekupheleni, kwabonakala izixuku zeziguli ezinesifo samaphaphu ezaziwa ukuthi zihlobene nokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba yamemezela ukuqubuka okuqhubekayo kwesifo sokuphefumula esibangelwa i-SARS-CoV-2 njengeSimo Esiphuthumayo Sezempilo Yomphakathi Esikhathaza Amazwe Omhlaba futhi yabiza lesi sifo ngokuthi i-COVID-19.
Kusukela ngo-March 3, 2020, sekufakazelwe amacala angu-90,053 emhlabeni wonke, kanti inani labantu ababulawa yi-HIV lingamaphesenti angu-3.4.
Okuphawulekayo ukuthi inani labantu ababulawa yi-Hubei, eChina lingama-4.2%, kanti elingaphandle kwalo lingama-1.2%.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ibangela ukutheleleka okubuhlungu okubangelwa ukuphefumula njenge-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, okuboniswa njengomkhuhlane, ukukhwehlela kanye ne-dyspnea.
Isifo sohudo sibonakala nakwesinye isiguli.
Isifo samaphaphu singesinye sezimpawu ezinzima kakhulu futhi singasheshe siphenduke isifo esibangela ukucindezeleka okujulile emaphashini okuphefumula.
Nakuba i-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 zifana kakhulu ngenxa yokufana kokulandelana kwama-nucleotide okuphezulu okungu-82%, zihlanganiswa zibe amagatsha ahlukene esihlahleni se-phylogenetic.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ngokusobala ayinawo amagciwane amaningi kodwa iyadluliseka uma iqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV.
Kubikwe abantu abangenazimpawu abanegciwane le-SARS-CoV-2 futhi bangase bafake isandla ekusakazekeni kwalo ngokushesha emhlabeni wonke.
Ukuqhathanisa nokuqhathanisa i-SARS-CoV-2 namanye ama-HCoV ayisithupha kwembula ukufana nokungafani okuthakazelisa kakhulu.
Okokuqala, isikhathi sokufukama nesikhathi sokugqashuka kwesifo se-HCoV kuyafana kakhulu.
Kulokhu, i-SARS-CoV-2 ilandela ukuthambekela okujwayelekile kwamanye ama-HCoV ayisithupha.
Okwesibili, ubukhulu bezimpawu ze-COVID-19 buphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV nama-HCoV amane atholakala emphakathini (okungukuthi, i-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 ne-HCoV-NL63).
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ukutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 kubonisa izici ezivame kakhulu lapho umuntu etheleleke ngama-HCoV atholakala emphakathini, kuhlanganise nokubonakaliswa kwezimpawu ezingathandeki, ezingatheni noma ezingekho nhlobo.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, kunengxenye encane yamacala abucayi e-COVID-19 njengoba kunjalo nangesifo se-SARS-CoV, nakuba isilinganiso singaphansi kancane.
Okwesithathu, ukudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kubonisa amaphethini athakazelisayo abonakala kokubili kuma-HCoV atholakala emphakathini nase-SARS-CoV.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 okungenani kuphakeme njengalawo ama-HCoV atholakala emphakathini.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, kusazobonakala ukuthi ingabe ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kuyancipha yini ngemva kokudlula kubantu njengoba kwenzeka nge-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV.
Ekugcineni, njengamanye ama-HCoV, i-SARS-CoV-2 ingatholakala kumasampula endle.
Ukuthi ukudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngomlomo nge-fecal kudlala indima ebalulekile yini njengoba kunjalo nge-SARS-CoV okungenani ngaphansi kwezimo ezithile kusazocaciswa yizifundo ezizayo.
Kuyathakazelisa futhi ukubona ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ingabonisa yini ukuthi isizini iyashintsha njengoba kunjalo ngama-HCoV atholakala emphakathini.
Noma kunjalo, izici ze-SARS-CoV-2 ezihlanganisa ukudluliseka kwayo, izifo kanye nokusabalala okuqhubekayo ngemuva kokudlula kubantu kuzoba nomthelela ekufezeni ekugcineni kokuqubuka kwe-COVID-19.
Wonke ama-HCoV amane atholakala emphakathini abangela izimpawu ezincane aye ahambisana kahle nabantu.
Ngokwesinye isimo, kungase kube yiqiniso nokuthi abantu baye bazivumelanisa kahle nalezi zinhlobo ezine ze-HCoV.
Ngamanye amazwi, bobabili bangaba abasindile ezifweni zasendulo ze-HCV.
Ama-HCoV abangela izifo ezinzima kubantu nabantu abahlakulele izifo ezinzima ze-HCoV aqedwe.
Ukuze lokhu kwenzeke, ama-HCoV kufanele aphinde aphindwe kubantu ngezinga elanele ukuze avumele ukuqoqwa kwezinguquko ezivumelanayo ezivimbela izici zokunciphisa umninikhaya.
Ngalo mqondo, uma ukuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kuqhubeka isikhathi eside futhi abantu abaningi betheleleka, amathuba okuba ivumelane ngokuphelele nabantu ayanda.
Uma ilungela kahle, ukudluliselwa kwayo kubantu kungaba nzima ukukumisa ngokuvalelwa noma ngezinye izindlela zokulawula ukutheleleka.
Sekuyiminyaka eminingi, ama-CoV amane atholakala emphakathini esakazeka kubantu, okubangela umkhuhlane ovamile kubantu abangakwazi ukuzivikela.
La magciwane awadingi indawo yokugcina izilwane.
Ngokuphambene, i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV ezibangela izifo kakhulu azikaze ziguqukele kubantu kahle futhi ukudluliselwa kwazo kubantu akukwazi ukuqhubeka.
Kumelwe zigcine futhi zande ezindaweni zazo zokulondoloza izilwane futhi zifune ithuba lokudlulela kubantu abangaba izisulu, mhlawumbe ngokusebenzisa isilwane esisodwa noma eziningi eziphakathi nendawo nezandisayo.
I-SARS-CoV-2 inezici ezifanayo ne-SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV kanye nama-HCoV amane atholakala emphakathini.
Isidluliselwa kakhulu njengama-HCoV atholakala emphakathini, okungenani okwamanje.
Nokho, ihlasela kakhulu kune-HCoV etholakala emphakathini futhi ayibangeli izifo kangako kune-SARS-CoV noma i-MERS-CoV.
Kusazobonakala ukuthi izovumelana ngokugcwele nabantu futhi izungeze abantu ngaphandle kwesikhungo noma isilwane esiphakathi.
Ngaphambi kokuxoxa ngemvelaphi yezilwane yama-HCoV, kuzosisiza ukuxoxa ngemigomo nezici zezinto eziphilayo, zemvelo, ezihlala endaweni, eziphakathi nendawo nezandisayo zama-HCoV.
Isilwane sisebenza njengendlalifa yokuziphendukela kwe-HCoV uma sinokhokho ohlobene eduze onobunye obuphezulu ezingeni lokuhlelwa kwe-nucleotide.
Igciwane elivela kumzali livame ukuzivumelanisa kahle nezimo futhi alibi nezifo kulowo muntu.
Ngokufanayo, i-reservoir host igcina i-HCoV ngokuqhubekayo nangesikhathi eside.
Kuzo zombili lezi zimo, ama-host atheleleke ngokwemvelo futhi ayizindlalifa zemvelo ze-HCoV noma igciwane layo eliwumzali.
Ngokuphambene, uma i-HCoV isanda kwethulwa kumuntu ophethe ngaphambi noma lapho isanda kwethulwa kubantu, ayivumelani kahle nomuntu omusha futhi ngokuvamile iyisifo.
Lo mdlali ophakathi angasebenza njengomthombo we-zoonotic wokutheleleka kwabantu futhi adlale indima yomdlali okhulisa ngokuvumela igciwane ukuba liphinde likhule okwesikhashana bese lilidlulisela kubantu ukuze likhulise izinga lokutheleleka kwabantu.
I-HCoV ingase ithole ukutheleleka okungenabungozi uma ingakwazi ukuqhubeka idluliselwa kumuntu ophakathi.
Ngokuphambene nalokho, ama-HCoV nawo angakwazi ukuzivumelanisa nomgcini ophakathi futhi aze asungule ubhubhane lwesikhathi eside.
Kulokhu, isidumbu esiphakathi siba isidumbu esingokwemvelo.
Idatha yezifo eziwumshayabhuqe yembula emuva kwesikhathi ukuthi lesi simo se-SARS sasinomlando wokuthintana nezilwane zasendle.
Ukuphenywa kokwanda kwe-seroprevalence okwalandelwa kwabonisa ukuthi abathengisi bezilwane babenesilinganiso esiphakeme se-anti-SARS-CoV IgG uma kuqhathaniswa nesabantu abavamile.
Ama-civet esundu (Paguma larvata) kanye nenja ye-racoon emakethe yezilwane eziphilayo kwaqala kwabonakala ukuthi ayathwala amagciwane afana ne-SARS-CoV cishe afana ne-SARS-CoV.
Lokhu kwaxhaswa ngokungaqondile ukuthi akuzange kubikwe okunye nge-SARS ngemva kokubulala wonke ama-civet ezimakethe.
Nokho, kubikwe ukuthi ama-civet esundu afakwe izifihla-buso avela endle noma emapulazini ngaphandle kokuchayeka ezimakethe zezilwane eziphilayo ayebhekene ne-SARS-CoV, okusikisela ukuthi ama-civet esundu afakwe izifihla-buso angase abe yindawo ephakathi yokukhulisa kodwa hhayi indawo yemvelo yokugcina i-SARS-CoV.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi njengoba izilwane ezingu-80% ezimakethe zaseGuangzhou zine-anti-SARS-CoV antibodies, kungenzeka ukuthi izinhlobo eziningi zezilwane ezincelisayo zingase zibe yizinambuzane eziqinisa i-SARS-CoV.
Zonke lezi zibonakala zingama-host of SARS-CoV.
Ukufuna okwalandela umninikhaya wemvelo we-SARS-CoV kwaveza i-bat CoV ehlobene kakhulu, ebizwa ngokuthi i-SARS-related Rhinolophus bat CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3), ekhona kumalulwane aseChina.
Lezi zimvemvane zinama-antibodies e-anti-SARS-CoV kanye nokuhlelwa kwezakhi zofuzo ze-SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3.
Le namanye ama-bat CoVs anokufana okulingana ngo-88-92% kokulandelana kwama-nucleotide ne-SARS-CoV.
Lezi zifundo ziye zabeka isisekelo somqondo omusha wokuthi amalulwane aphethe amagciwane abantu abavelayo.
Ama-CoV amaningi afana ne-SARS (SL-CoVs) nawo atholakele emalulwaneni, kodwa awekho ngaphandle kwe-WIV1 eyodwa engahlukaniswa njengegciwane eliphilayo.
I-human angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) yaziwa ukuthi iyisi receptors se-SARS-CoV.
I-WIV1 ethathwe kusampula yokukhishwa kwamalulwane yaboniswa ukuthi isebenzisa i-ACE2 yamalulwane, i-civet kanye neyamuntu njengendlela yokwamukela ukungena kwamangqamuzana.
Ngokuthakazelisayo, i-serum yeziguli ze-SARS ezivuselelekayo yakwazi ukuvimbela i-WIV1.
Kuze kube manje, i-WIV1 imelela okhokho abahlobene kakhulu be-SARS-CoV emalulwaneni, ihlanganyela i-95% ye-homology ye-nucleotide sequence.
Nakuba kunokufana okukhulu phakathi kwalezi zigciwane ezimbili, ngokuvamile kukholakala ukuthi i-WIV1 akuyona igciwane eliyisihlobo esiqondile se-SARS-CoV futhi amalulwane akuwona amagumbi okuhlala ngokushesha kwe-SARS-CoV.
Ukuhlaziywa kwe-phylogenetic kuhlanganisa i-MERS-CoV eqenjini elifanayo ne-bat CoV-HKU4 ne-bat CoV-HKU5.
I-bat CoV-HKU4 ne-MERS-CoV zisebenzisa i-host receptor efanayo, i-dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), ukuze igciwane lingene.
Ukulandelana kwe-RNA polymerase okuxhomeke ku-RNA kwe-MERS-CoV kusondele kakhulu kuma-beta-CoVs eminenke atholakala eYurophu nase-Afrika.
Kuze kube manje, ayikho i-MERS-CoV ephilayo etholakala kumalulwane asendle.
I-MERS-CoV nesihlobo sayo esiseduze kakhulu i-bat CoV-HKU25 banokufana okulingana ngo-87% kuphela kokulandelana kwama-nucleotide.
Ngakho-ke, amalulwane angase angabi yindawo yokugcina i-MERS-CoV.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ucwaningo olwenziwe eMpumalanga Ephakathi lubonise ukuthi amakamela e-dromedary ane-seropositive kuma-antibody angenawo amandla e-MERS-CoV, njengoba kunjalo nangamakamela avela eMpumalanga Ephakathi emazweni amaningi ase-Afrika.
I-MERS-CoV ephilayo efana negciwane elitholakala kubantu yahlukaniswa namathambo emphumulo amakamela, okukhombisa ukuthi amakamela asebenza njengendawo yokugcina i-MERS-CoV.
Kuyaphawuleka nokuthi izimpawu ezivamile ezincane kodwa ukuchitheka okukhulu kwegciwane kwabonwa kumakamela atheleleke ngokuhlolwa nge-MERS-CoV.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi amakamela athelelekile awadluliseli amagciwane ngomgudu wokuphefumula kuphela kodwa nangomgudu we-fecal-oral, nawo oyindlela eyinhloko yokudlulisa amagciwane emalulwaneni.
Nokho, kusenezicelo ngoba abantu abaningi abaqinisekisiwe abane-MERS abanalo ulwazi oludlule mayelana nokuxhumana namakamela ngaphambi kokuba kuqale izimpawu, okubonakala sengathi kungenxa yokudluliselwa komzimba noma izindlela zokudlulisela ezingaziwa ezihilela izinhlobo zezilwane ezingaziwa eziqukethe i-MERS-CoV.
I-SARS-CoV-2 inokufana kwama-nucleotide angama-96.2% ne-bat CoV RaTG13 ehlukaniswe namalulwane aseRhinolophus affinis.
Njengasendabeni ye-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, ukwehluka kokulandelana phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 kukhulu kakhulu ukuba kunikezwe ubuhlobo babazali.
Okusho ukuthi, amalulwane angase angabi yizinambuzane eziphethe i-SARS-CoV-2 ngaphandle uma kutholakala ama-Cov alingana kakhulu esikhathini esizayo.
Cishe, izilwane eziphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kufanele zibe phakathi kwezinhlobo zezilwane zasendle ezithengiswayo futhi zibulawe eHuanan Seafood Wholesale Market, lapho amacala amaningi okuqala e-COVID-19 ayehlotshaniswa khona, okubonisa ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi isilwane sidluliselwe kubantu.
Ucwaningo oluthile lwakamuva olususelwa ekuhleleni ukulandelana kwe-metagenomic luye lwabonisa ukuthi iqembu lezilwane ezincelisayo ezincane ezisengozini yokuqothulwa ezaziwa ngokuthi ama-pangolin (Manis javanica) lingase libe nama-beta-CoVs okhokho ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Lezi zinhlobo ezintsha ze-pangolin CoV genomes zine-85-92% ye-nucleotide sequence homology ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, zihlobene eduze ne-RaTG13 cishe ngo-90% ezingeni lokuhleleka kwe-nucleotide.
Zihlanganiswa zibe yizinhlobo ezimbili zamagciwane afana ne-SARS-CoV-2 esihlahleni se-phylogenetic, enye yazo enesizinda sokuxhuma ama-receptor (RBD) esifana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2, ene-97.4% ye-amino acid sequence identity.
Ngokuphambene, ama-RBD e-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ahluke kakhulu, nakuba enamazinga aphezulu okufana kwezakhi zofuzo.
Ucwaningo lwangaphambilini kuma-pangolin agulayo nalo lubike ukuthi kutholakale ama-contigs egciwane kumasampula wamaphaphu, okubonakala ukuthi ahlobene ngokufanayo ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Lolu cwaningo lwasebenzisa izindlela ezahlukene zokuhlanganisa nokuhlolwa ngesandla ukuze kukhiqizwe ukulandelana kwe-genome okuyingxenye okuhlanganisa cishe u-86.3% we-genome egcwele yegciwane.
Asikwazi ukukhipha ukuthi i-pangolin ingenye yezilwane eziphakathi nezingamukela i-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, okwamanje abukho ubufakazi obusekela imvelaphi eqondile ye-pangolin ye-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokwehluka kokulandelana phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nama-beta-CoVs ahlobene ne-pangolin SARS-CoV-2.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ibanga eliphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 libuye libe lifushane kunalelo eliphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nama-beta-CoVs ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 e-pangolin.
Indlela yokuziphendukela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 emalulwaneni, ama-pangolin nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo isazosungulwa.
Nakuba i-RBDs etholakele ine-homology yezinqubo eziphakeme kakhulu phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin, ama-beta-CoVs ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2, i-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 anokufana kwezinqubo eziphakeme kakhulu ku-genome yonke.
Kucatshangwa ukuthi ukufana okukhulu phakathi kwama-RBD e-pangolin SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoVs ne-SARS-CoV-2 kubangelwa ukuguquka okuguquguqukayo okubangelwa ukukhetha.
Isiphakamiso esiphikisayo sivuna ukuhlanganiswa kabusha phakathi kwe-beta-CoV ehlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ye-pangolin ezinhlotsheni zezilwane zasendle zesithathu.
Njengamandla ashukumisayo ekuziphendukeleni kwemvelo, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kusakazeke kakhulu phakathi kwama-beta-CoV.
Ijaji lisalokhu likhona ngemvelaphi ye-zoonotic esheshayo ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Ngaphandle kwama-HCoV anezifo eziningi, kwaphinde kwahlolwa imvelaphi ye-zoonotic ye-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-NL63 ne-HCoV-HKU1.
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bubonisa ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 ne-HCoV-229E kungenzeka ukuthi zivela kuma-Cov amagundane, kuyilapho amagciwane omzali e-HCoV-OC43 ne-HCoV-HKU1 etholakala ezigulini.
Kubikwe ukuthi i-bat CoV ebizwa nge-ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) etholwe kumalulwane aseNyakatho Melika anemibala emithathu yabonisa ubudlelwane obuseduze ne-HCoV-NL63.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-HCoV-229E yayihlobene ngofuzo nenye i-bat CoV, ebizwa ngokuthi i-Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, eyatholakala eGhana, kuyilapho kusolwa ukuthi ama-camellid nawo ayizinambuzane eziphakathi.
Ukuze kucace, ulwazi lwamanje ngemvelaphi yezilwane yama-HCoVs aziwayo lufingqiwe ku-Figure 1 naku-Table 2.
Ukuhlaziywa kwe-phylogenetic kuye kwanikeza ubufakazi bokudluliselwa kwe-HCoVs phakathi kwezinhlobo emlandweni.
Lapho i-HCoV-OC43 iwela izinhlobo ukuze ithelele abantu besuka ezilwaneni zasekhaya cishe ngo-1890, kwaqoshwa ubhadane lokutheleleka ngezindlela zokuphefumula.
Umlando wokudluliselwa kwe-HCoV-229E phakathi kwezinhlobo awucaci kangako.
Ama-bat alpha-CoVs ahlobene kakhulu ne-HCoV-229E atholakele.
Phakathi kwazo kukhona i-alpaca alpha-CoV.
Kunobufakazi obuningi obusekela ukudluliselwa kwegciwane kusuka kumalulwane kuya kubantu ngokuqondile.
Okokuqala, abantu kodwa hhayi ama-alpaca bangase baxhumane namalulwane endaweni efanayo.
Kunalokho, abantu basondelene nama-alpaca.
Okwesibili, ama-alpha-CoVs ama-bat ahlobene ne-HCoV-229E ahlukahlukene futhi awabangelwa izifo kumalulwane, kuyilapho i-alpaca-alpha-CoV ibangela ukuqubuka kwesifo sokuphefumula ezilwaneni ezithelelekile.
Ekugcineni, i-alpaca alpha-CoV ayitholakalanga ezilwaneni zasendle.
Ngakho-ke, akunakuphikwa ukuthi ama-alpacas angathola i-alpha-CoV ehlobene ne-HCoV-229E kubantu.
Eqinisweni, amalulwane angumthombo oqondile wamagciwane abangela izifo kubantu kuhlanganise negciwane lamathumba, igciwane le-Ebola, igciwane le-Nipah kanye negciwane le-Hendra.
Ngakho-ke, akumangazi ukuthi amalulwane angadlulisela i-HCoV-229E kubantu ngokuqondile.
Uma kungenjalo, kuyilapho ama-bat alpha-CoVs esebenza njenge-gene pool ye-HCoV-229E, ama-alpaca namakamela ama-dromedary angase abe yizinambuzane eziphakathi ezihambisa amagciwane kubantu, njengoba kunjalo nge-MERS-CoV.
I-MERS-CoV iyisibonelo esihle kakhulu sokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo ezivela kumalulwane ziye kumakamela asezingeni eliphezulu futhi isuka kumakamela asezingeni eliphezulu iye kubantu.
Umsuka we-MERS-CoV ovela emalulwaneni uyaziwa lapho iqala ukubonakala futhi uye waqiniswa nokutholakala kamuva.
Kuyacaca ukuthi amalulwane anikeza izinhlobo eziningi zegciwane ukuze kushintshaniswe izingcezu zofuzo phakathi kwezinhlobo futhi kudluliselwe phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Ukuphila isikhathi eside, amakoloni agcwele abantu, ukusebenzisana eduze nabantu kanye nekhono eliqinile lokundiza konke kuyizinto ezenza amalulwane abe 'abasabalalisi bamagciwane' abafanele.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-MERS-CoV iye yabonwa amakamela ase-dromedary amashumi eminyaka.
Ivumelane kahle nalezi zinkamela esezisuswe ekubeni yizilwane ezihlala emgodini zibe yizilwane ezihlala endaweni ezinzile futhi ezihlala endaweni yemvelo.
I-MERS-CoV ibangela isifo esincane kakhulu futhi igcina izinga lokuziphendukela kwemvelo eliphansi kulezi zilwane.
Ukudluliselwa kwayo okungahleliwe kubantu kuyingozi futhi abantu basale bengumgcini we-MERS-CoV njengoba ukudluliselwa kwayo kungeke kuqhubeke.
Ngokungafani nendima yamakamela ekusakazeni i-MERS-CoV, indima yama-pangolin, uma ikhona, ekusakazeni i-SARS-CoV-2 ihlukile.
Ikakhulukazi, ama-beta-CoVs ama-pangolin ane-pathogenicity ephezulu kuma-pangolin.
Zingaba yizinambuzane ezibulala ama-beta-CoVs ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2, ezifana nama-civet uma kuziwa ku-SARS-CoV.
Amathuba amaningana okudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 phakathi kwezinhlobo kusuka ezilwaneni kuya kubantu kufanele akhanselwe noma akhanselwe ezifundweni ezizayo.
Okokuqala, amalulwane angaba yindawo yokugcina igciwane elihlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 elicishe lifane ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bangase bahlanganyele indawo yabo neminenke ngokuyibulala noma ngokuyimbiwa kwamalahle.
Okwesibili, ama-pangolin angaba omunye wabaphathi abaphakathi abaqinisa lapho igciwane elihlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 lisanda kwethulwa khona.
Abantu bathola leli gciwane ngokubulala nokudla inyama yezilwane zasendle.
Kungenzeka ukuthi izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane zasekhaya zingase zithole i-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuhlola izilwane zasekhaya nezasendle ukuthola ama-antibody kuyafaneleka.
Okwesithathu, njengoba kushiwo ngenhla, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha nokuzivumelanisa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungenzeka kwenzeka ohlotsheni lwesithathu oluxhumana nabashaywa-mkhombe nama-pangolin.
Ukufuna imvelaphi yezilwane ye-SARS-CoV-2 kusaqhubeka.
Ngaphandle kwezinhlobo ezahlukene zezilwane ezihlala kuzo, kunezici ezintathu eziyinhloko ezingase zibe yingxenye yegciwane ezibalulekile ekwenzeni kube lula ngama-CoV ukuba adlule izithiyo zezinhlobo.
Okokuqala, izinga eliphezulu kakhulu lokuziphendukela kwemvelo ekuziphendukeleni kwe-RNA.
Uma kuqhathaniswa namanye amagciwane e-RNA anezintambo ezingashadile, izinga lokuguquka kwe-CoVs lingathathwa ngokuthi eliphakathi kuya ku-eliphakeme ngezinga lokuguqulwa eliphakathi kuka-~10-4 ngonyaka endaweni ngayinye 2, kuye ngokuthi isigaba sokuzivumelanisa ne-CoV kumgcini omusha.
Ama-CoV anesifo esibizwa ngokuthi i-exoribonuclease, lapho ukususwa kwaso kubangela ukuguquguquka okukhulu kakhulu nokuqedwa noma ngisho nokungaphili.
Kuyathakazelisa ukuthi i-analogue ye-nucleotide i-Remdesivir yaziwa ukuthi icindezela ukuphindaphindeka kwe-CoV ngokuvimbela le-exoribonuclease ne-RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
I-Remdesivir ingenye yezindlela ezithembisa kakhulu zokulwa ne-SARS-CoV-2 ezizohlolwa ezivivinyweni zemitholampilo.
Noma kunjalo, amazinga okuguquka kwama-CoV aphindwe izikhathi ezingaba yisigidi kunalawo ama-host.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga lokuziphendukela kwemvelo livame ukuba phezulu lapho ama-CoV engakwazi ukuzivumelanisa kahle nomgcini.
Uma kuqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV enezinga eliphakeme lokuziphendukela kwemvelo, izinga lokuziphendukela kwemvelo le-SARS-CoV-2 libonakala liphansi, okusikisela izinga eliphakeme lokuzivumelanisa nabantu.
Cishe, isivele isilungele omunye umninikhaya osondelene nabantu.
Ngaphezu kwe-SARS-CoV-2, lokhu kusebenza nase-MERS-CoV, evumelana kahle namakamela.
Ngokombono, akunakwenzeka ukuthi ukuguquguquka kwezakhi zofuzo kungenza imithi yokugoma nemithi elwa namagciwane yokulwa ne-SARS-CoV-2 ingasebenzi ngokushesha.
Okwesibili, i-RNA enkulu ye-genome kuma-CoVs yenza kube lula ukuguqula i-genome ukuze iguquke futhi ihlanganiswe kabusha, ngaleyo ndlela kwandise amathuba okuziphendukela kwemvelo phakathi kwezinhlobo, okuwusizo ekuveleni kwama-CoV amasha lapho izimo sezifanele.
Lokhu kusekelwa yizinhlaka eziningi ezihlukile ezivulekile zokufunda nemisebenzi yamaprotheni ekhodiwe ngasekupheleni kwe-3' kwe-genome.
Okwesithathu, ama-CoV ashintsha amafomu ngokuzenzakalelayo futhi kaningi ngesikhathi sokuphindaphinda kwe-RNA ngokusebenzisa indlela eyingqayizivele yokukhetha ikhophi.
Emkhosini osebenza njengesitsha sokuxuba, ukushintshwa kwe-strand kwenzeka kaningi ngesikhathi sokudluliselwa kwe-RNA ye-CoV.
Ama-RNA asezingeni eliphezulu kanye nama-subgenomic RNAs angahlanganiswa kabusha ukuze akhiqize ama-CoV amasha.
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwemvelo butholakale kokubili ku-HCoV-HKU1 naku-HCoV-OC43, kanye nasezilwaneni ze-CoVs ezifana ne-bat SL-CoV ne-batCoV-HKU9.
Ukuxhumana kwegciwane nomgcini ngokuphathelene nokudluliselwa
Ngaphandle kwezinto ezintathu ezibangelwa amagciwane ezichazwe ngenhla, ukusebenzisana kwegciwane nomamukeli womgcini kungenye into ebalulekile ethonya ukudluliselwa phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Lapha, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kwe-SARS-CoV kuthathwa njengesibonelo esivamile, esiphinde sibonise ubufakazi bokukhethwa okuhle ngesikhathi sezenzakalo zokudluliswa phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Ngokusekelwe ekuhlaziyweni okuqhathanisayo phakathi kwe-SARS-CoVs yabantu kanye ne-civet, i-SARS-CoV kucatshangwa ukuthi iguqulwa ngokushesha kumagumbi ahlukene, ikakhulukazi nge-mutations ku-RBD yeprotheni ye-S.
Ngokuvamile, i-RBD e-S protein ye-CoV isebenzisana ne-cellular receptor futhi ikhethwa kakhulu impendulo ye-host antibody.
Ku-SARS-CoV, i-RBD isezinhlayiyeni ezingama-318 kuya kwezingu-510 zama-amino acid engxenyeni ye-S1, ebopha i-ACE2 yomuntu kanye nama-coreceptors ayo ukuze ingene igciwane.
I-RBD ye-SARS-CoV iyakwazi ukubona ama-ACE2 receptors ezilwane ezihlukahlukene, kuhlanganise namalulwane, ama-civet, amagundane nezinja zama-raccoon, okuvumela ukudluliselwa kwegciwane phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Eqinisweni, kwatholakala ukuthi izinsalela zama-amino acid ezingu-6 kuphela zahlukile kuma-virus abantu nama-civet e-RBD futhi ezingu-4 zazo zitholakala kumklamo obopha ama-receptor ukuze zixhumane ne-ACE2 receptor.
I-Civet SARS-CoV inezinguquko ze-K479N ne-S487T ku-RBD yayo, ezingase zandise ukuzwana kokusebenzisana kwe-spike protein ne-ACE2 receptor yomuntu.
Ngamanye amazwi, lezi zinguquko ezimbili zama-amino acid zingase zibaluleke kakhulu ekuzivumelaniseni kwegciwane nabantu.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 inemvamisa efanayo ne-SARS-CoV.
Umehluko ongu-30% phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-SARS-CoV e-S1 protein unit usho ukuthi ukuhlangana kwe-S protein yayo ne-ACE2 yomuntu kungenzeka kushintshile.
Ngempela, ucwaningo lwe-cryo-EM lukhombisa ukuthi lokhu kubopha kunobungani obuphindwe izikhathi ezingu-10 kuya kwezingu-20 kunobuphakathi kwe-ACE2 yomuntu ne-SARS-CoV S protein.
Kuyoba nesithakazelo futhi ukunquma ukuthi ngabe kukhona yini okunye okudingekayo ukuze kudluliselwe i-SARS-CoV-2.
Kuyathakazelisa ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 nayo ibopha i-ACE2 kodwa ngengxenye ehlukile ye-S.
Kunamanye ama-receptor amaningi e-HCoV, njenge-aminopeptidase N ye-HCoV-229E, ne-9-O-acetylated sialic acid ye-HCoV-OC43.
Zingabuye zichaze ukuguquguquka ngempumelelo kwalezi CoV kubantu ngemuva kokudluliselwa phakathi kwezinhlobo ezivela ezilwaneni ezihlala kuzo.
Ngaphezu kwama-receptor amangqamuzana, umphumela wokudluliselwa kwama-HCoV phakathi kwezinhlobo nawo ulawulwa ezinye izinto ezihlobene nomgcini kanye nezimo zokunqanda.
Ukwehluka kwalezi amaprotheni omgcini phakathi kwabantu kanye nama-reservoir emvelo ama-HCoV afana namalulwane, amakamela kanye nezilwane ezihuquzelayo kungase kube yisithiyo ekusakazeni phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Ama-HCoV kufanele athathe izakhi zokuxhomeka komgcini futhi aphule izakhi zokunciphisa umgcini ukuze adluliselwe phakathi kwezinhlobo ngempumelelo.
Mayelana nalokhu, izakhi zezinhlayiyana kule ndawo ebalulekile yokuxhumana kwegciwane nomgcini zisalindeleke ukuba zikhonjwe futhi zichazwe.
Ukuhlolwa kwe-genome yonke okungabandlululi kokuncika komgcini kanye nezimbangela zokunciphisa i-SARS-CoV-2 kusetshenziswa ubuchwepheshe obusha be-CRISPR kungahle kube nomphumela omuhle.
Ukuvela kwama-HCoV amasha: buyela endaweni yokuqala
Ukwehlukahluka kwama-Cov amagundane kunikeza amathuba amaningi okuvela kwama-HCoV amasha.
Ngalo mqondo, ama-bat CoVs asebenza njengama-HCoVs.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukuguquka kwezakhi zofuzo okusheshayo nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwezakhi zofuzo nakho kuqhuba ukuziphendukela kwemvelo kwe-HCoV futhi kusebenza njengezinyathelo ezimbili ezibalulekile kule nqubo.
Ngokwesibonelo, ukuthola noma ukulahlekelwa yizakhi zofuzo ezintsha ezakha amaprotheni kunamandla okuguqula kakhulu ama-phenotype egciwane.
Phakathi kwamaprotheni angawesekeli e-SARS-CoV, i-ORF8 iye yacatshangwa ukuthi ibalulekile ekuzivumelaniseni nabantu, njengoba kwahlukaniswa amagciwane amalulwane ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV kodwa atholakala ukuthi abhala amaprotheni e-ORF8 ahlukile.
Kuye kwatholakala isici sokususwa kwama-nucleotide angu-29 kuma-SARS-CoV ezinhlotsheni ezahlukaniswa ekuqaleni kobhadane kubantu.
Lokhu kususwa kwe-ORF8 kuhlukanisa i-ORF8a ne-ORF8b futhi kucatshangwa ukuthi kungukuguquka okuguqukayo okukhuthaza ukushintshwa kwama-host.
Ngaphandle kwalokho, i-SARS-CoV inomlando wokuhlanganiswa kabusha okungenzeka nemindeni yama-alpha- kanye nama-gamma-CoV, lapho kwahlolwa khona izifunda eziningi ezincane zokuhlanganiswa kabusha ku-RNA-based RNA polymerase.
Izindawo zokuhlanganisa kabusha zabuye zabonakala ku-nsp9, ingxenye enkulu ye-nsp10, nasezingxenyeni ze-nsp14.
Ngokufanayo, kuye kwaboniswa ukuthi ubhadane lwe-MERS-CoV lwabhekana nezimo zokuhlanganiswa kabusha phakathi kwezinhlanga ezahlukene, okwenzeka kumakamela e-dromedary eSaudi Arabia.
Ngaphandle kwe-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, izenzakalo zokuhlanganisa kabusha ziye zabonwa nakwezinye i-HCoVs, lapho ama-HCoV ahlangana khona namanye ama-CoVs ezilwane kumagciwane awo angawokwakheka.
Kufanele futhi kuxwayiswe ukuthi ukukhetha okufakelwayo kungasiza ekuguqulweni okungahlosiwe kwezakhi zofuzo zegciwane, okungenzeka ukuthi kubangelwa ukukhulula amagciwane ekucindezelweni kokukhetha, njengokucindezelwa isimiso somzimba sokuzivikela.
Isibonelo sale miphumela ukulahleka kwe-ORF4 yobude obugcwele ku-HCoV-229E prototype strain, ngenxa yokuqedwa kwama-nucleotide amabili.
Nakuba i-ORF4 engaphazanyiswa ingabonwa kumagciwane amalulwane namakamela ahlobene ne-HCoV-229E, i-alpaca alpha-CoV ibonisa ukufakwa kwe-nucleotide eyodwa, okuholela ekushintsheni kwefreyimu.
Okokugcina, ukuvela kwama-HCoV amasha nakho kubangelwa ingcindezi yokukhetha kumgcini wawo.
Kwabonwa izimpawu ezingenazimpawu noma ezincane kuphela lapho amalulwane etheleleke ngama-Cov, okukhombisa ukuzivumelanisa phakathi kwama-Cov namalulwane.
Kwabonakala ukuthi amalulwane azivumelanisa kahle nama-CorV ngokomzimba nangokwenyama.
Ngokwesibonelo, amaphutha ekusebenzeni kwempendulo evikela ukuvuvukala kumalulwane anciphisa ngokuphumelelayo izifo ezibangelwa ama-CoV.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, umsebenzi wamangqamuzana abulala ngokwemvelo emalulwaneni ucindezelwa ukuvuselelwa kwe-NKG2/CD94 kanye nezinga eliphansi lokuveza ama-molecule amakhulu e-histocompatibility complex class I.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga eliphakeme lezinhlobo ze-oxygen (ROS) ezisebenza ngempumelelo ezivezwa umsebenzi ophakeme we-metabolism wamalulwane zingavimbela ukuphindaphindeka kwe-CoV futhi zithinte ukufundwa kwe-exoribonuclease, ngaleyo ndlela zinikeze ingcindezi yokukhetha yokukhiqizwa kwama-virus strains anezifo eziningi lapho engeniswa kumninikhaya omusha.
Izinhlobo ze-CoV ezibangela izifo ezingatheni zingase zivele ngokuhlangana kabusha, okuholela ekutholeni amaprotheni amasha noma izici zamaprotheni ukuze zilungele umninikhaya.
Ngakho-ke, akuyona into engahleliwe ukuthi ama-HCoV amathathu amasha avele emashumini amabili eminyaka adlule.
Ama-CoV awabangelwa izifo noma abangela izimpawu ezincane kumagumbi awo okuhlala kuwo njengama-bat namakamela.
Ziphindaphindeka ngamandla ngaphandle kokubangela ukusabela okunamandla kwamasosha omzimba.
Lapha kulapho kulele khona izimfihlo zokuthi kungani abantu abangenazo izimpawu zokutheleleka bebonakala futhi yini ebangela amacala anzima okutheleleka kwabantu.
Izimpawu ezinzima zibangelwa kakhulu ukusebenza ngokweqile kwempendulo yomzimba yokulwa nezifo kanye nesivunguvungu sama-cytokine lapho lapho impendulo yomzimba enamandla, ukulimala kwamaphaphu kuba kubi kakhulu.
Ngokuphambene, kubantu abangenazimpawu, ukuzivikela komzimba kuye kwahlukaniswa nokwanda kwe-CoV.
Isu elifanayo lokuhlukanisa impendulo yokuzivikela emzimbeni lingase libe nemiphumela ezuzisayo ekwelashweni kwe-anti-SARS-CoV-2.
Impendulo ye-interferon inamandla kakhulu emalulwaneni.
Ngakho-ke, ukusetshenziswa kwe-interferon yohlobo I okungenani esigabeni sokuqala sokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu kufanele kube nenzuzo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, i-NLRP3 inflammasome activation emalulwaneni ayisebenzi kahle.
Ngalesi sizathu, ukuvimbela i-NLRP3 inflammasome nge-MCC950 kungase kube wusizo ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kulandela isihloko esivamile okwavela ngaso i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV.
Nakuba i-beta-CoV ye-bat eye yahlangana ne-SARS-CoV ngama-95%, i-bat-CoV eye yahlangana ne-SARS-CoV ngama-96% nayo ikhona.
Nakuba kutholakale ukuthi ama-civet nezinye izilwane ezimakethe zinamagciwane afana ne-SARS-CoV, akuzange kutholakale ukuthi yiziphi izilwane eziphethe i-SARS-CoV-2 ngokushesha.
Ama-pangolin beta-CoVs afana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2 atholakele, okukhombisa ukuthi ama-pangolin angasebenza njengenye yamakhosikazi aphakathi noma ama-pangolin beta-CoVs anganikela ngezingcezu zofuzo enguqulweni yokugcina ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba kusenezicelo, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yenziwe umuntu ngamabomu noma ngephutha.
Ama-CoV abuyele endaweni yokugqama ngenxa yokuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 muva nje.
Ucwaningo lwama-CoV kumalulwane nakwezinye izilwane lushintshe kakhulu umbono wethu ngokubaluleka kwemvelaphi yezilwane kanye nezikhungo zezilwane zama-HCV ekusakazweni kwabantu.
Ubufakazi obubanzi buye babonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 zivela kumalulwane futhi zidluliselwa kubantu ngokusebenzisa ama-host aphakathi.
Njengoba ukutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV kuvela ekuxhumeni phakathi kwabantu nama-civet ezimakethe, ukuvala izimakethe ezimanzi nokubulala ama-civet lapho bekungaqeda ngempumelelo ubhadane lwe-SARS.
Ngenxa yesizathu esifanayo, ama-pangolin kufanele asuswe ezimakethe ezimanzi ukuvimbela ukudluliselwa kwe-zoonotic, ngenxa yokutholakala kwezinhlobo eziningi zama-pangolin beta-CoVs ahlobene kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 idluliselwa kubantu kanjani ngama-pangolin nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo kusafanele kucaciswe ekuhlolweni okuzayo.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-MERS-CoV ibikhona kumakamela asezingeni eliphezulu isikhathi eside.
La makamela asebenza njengethuluzi elibalulekile lokuthutha kanye nomthombo oyinhloko wezinkomo, ubisi, isikhumba nemikhiqizo yoboya kubantu bendawo.
Zisakazeke kabanzi eMpumalanga Ephakathi nase-Afrika.
Ngakho-ke akunakwenzeka ukudela wonke amakamela ukuze kulawulwe i-MERS, njengoba kwakwenziwa ezimakethe zezilwane zasendle eChina ukuvimbela ukusabalala kwe-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuze kunqandwe ukuqubuka kwe-MERS okuphindaphindwayo, kufanele kwenziwe indlela ebanzi yokuthuthukisa imithi yokugoma esebenzayo yokulwa ne-MERS-CoV yamakamela, kanye nezinye izindlela zokulawula ukutheleleka.
Njengoba singakwazi ukuqeda la magciwane, kungase kuvele ama-genotype amasha abangela ukuqubuka.
Ama-CoV amaningi atholakala ezilwaneni ayajikeleza endle.
Ikakhulukazi, ama-Cov amagundane anekhono lokubulala izilwane ahlukahlukene kakhulu.
Kunamathuba amaningi okuthi la ma-CoV atholakala ezilwaneni aguquke futhi ahlanganiswe kabusha, okuholele ekuveleni kwama-CoV amasha adluliseka kalula futhi / noma abulalayo kubantu esikhathini esizayo.
Isiko lokudla izilwane zasendle kwezinye izindawo zaseChina kufanele lishiywe ukuze kuncishiswe ukuxhumana okungadingekile phakathi kwabantu nezilwane.
Njengoba kunezinkinga ze-SARS, MERS ne-COVID-19, kufanele kube nohlelo olungcono lokulungiselela nokuphendula.
Eqinisweni, amagciwane amaningi abekhona kule planethi isikhathi eside kakhulu.
Zihlala emadamu azo emvelo kuze kube yilapho kunethuba lokudluliselwa.
Nakuba amalulwane enezici eziningi ezenza kube lula ukuba amagciwane asakazeke, amathuba okuba abantu baxhumane namalulwane nezinye izinhlobo zezilwane zasendle angancishiswa uma abantu befundiswa ukuba bangaxhumani nawo.
Ukuqapha okuqhubekayo ezilwane ezincelisayo kuyadingeka ukuze kuqondwe kangcono imvelo yama-CoV kanye nezilwane ezihlala kuzo, okuyobonakala kuwusizo ekuvimbeleni ukudluliselwa kwezilwane kubantu kanye nokuqubuka kwesikhathi esizayo.
Ekuphetheni, indlela ephumelela kunazo zonke yokuvimbela i-zoonosis yegciwane iwukuba abantu bahlale kude nezindawo zemvelo eziyindawo yemvelo yamagciwane ezifo.
Izingcezu eziningana zepuzzle yemvelaphi ye-zoonotic ye-SARS-CoV-2 zisalahlekile.
Okokuqala, uma amalulwane edlulisela igciwane elidala le-SARS-CoV-2 kuma-pangolin, kuyoba mnandi ukubona ukuthi ngaphansi kwaziphi izimo amalulwane nama-pangolin angabelana ngendawo efanayo engokwemvelo.
Okwesibili, uma amalulwane edlala indima eqondile ekusakazekeni kubantu, kufanele kutholakale ukuthi abantu baxhumana kanjani namalulwane.
Okwesithathu, uma isilwane sesithathu esincelisayo sisebenza njengesifuyo sangempela esiphakathi, kufanele kucaciswe ukuthi sisebenzisana kanjani nezinhlobo ezahlukene kuhlanganise nabantu, amalulwane nama-pangolin.
Ekugcineni, njengoba izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane zasekhaya zingase zibhekane ne-SARS-CoV-2, kufanele kuqhutshwe kokubili ukuqapha nokutheleleka okuhlolwayo.
Uma kuwumgundane, i-pangolin noma esinye isilwane esincelisayo, kulindeleke ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 noma amagciwane ayo omzali acishe afane atholakale kumgcini wayo wemvelo esikhathini esizayo.
Ukuqhubeka kophenyo kule ndawo kuzocacisa indlela yokuziphendukela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ezilwaneni, okunomthelela obalulekile ekuvikeleni nasekulawuleni i-COVID-19 kubantu.
Ukuvuselela imigomo yokuxilonga i-COVID-19 isimo esingasolwa kanye nesimo esiqinisekisiwe kuyadingeka
Ngo-6 February 2020, ithimba lethu laphrinta umhlahlandlela weluleko olusheshayo wokuxilongwa nokwelashwa kwesifo se-coronavirus (2019-nCoV) sika-2019, futhi lo mhlahlandlela wanikeza ulwazi lwethu futhi wenza inkomba enhle yokulwa nalolu bhubhane emhlabeni wonke.
Kodwa-ke, isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19) yisifo esisha, ukuqwashisa kwethu nolwazi lwethu kukhula kancane kancane ngokususelwa kokutholakele kocwaningo olwenziwayo kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho kokusebenza kwemitholampilo; ngakho-ke, amasu okuxilonga nokwelashwa nawo ayaqhubeka nokuvuselelwa.
Kule ncwadi, siphendule ukuphawula okukodwa mayelana nesiqondiso sethu futhi sanikeza imigomo yokuxilonga yakamuva ye-isimo esisolisayo ne-isimo esiqinisekisiwe ngokusho kwe-Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines yakamuva ye-COVID-19 (inguqulo yesikhombisa) ekhishwe yiNational Health Committee ye-People's Republic of China.
NgoDisemba 2019, i-coronavirus entsha ka-2019 (2019-nCoV) ibangele ukuqubuka, manje ebizwa ngokusemthethweni ngokuthi isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19) futhi leli gciwane labizwa ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (i-SARS-CoV-2).
Ngo-March 11, 2020, i-WHO yachaza i-COVID-19 njengobhadane.
Ukuze silwe nokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2, iqembu lethu selisungule umhlahlandlela weluleko olusheshayo futhi oshicilelwe ku-inthanethi ku-Military Medical Research ngo-06 February 2020.
Kusukela yanyatheliswa, iye yaheha ukunakwa okukhulu.
Nokho, phawula ukuthi i-COVID-19 iyisifo esisha, ulwazi lwethu nolwazi luyanda kancane kancane ngesisekelo semiphumela yocwaningo eqhubekayo kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho kokusebenza kwemitholampilo; ngakho-ke, amasu okuxilonga nokwelashwa nawo ayaqhubeka nokuvuselelwa.
Ngokwesibonelo, Imihlahlandlela Yokuxilongwa Nokwelashwa Kwe-COVID-19 ekhishwe yiKomiti Yezwe Yezempilo YaseChina (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), phakathi kuka-16 Januwari 2020 no-3 Mashi 2020, ikhishwe izikhathi eziyisikhombisa, ezinye zazo zashintshwa kakhulu.
Manje isiqondiso sethu sathola ukuphawula okuvela kuZhou et al., basungula isiphakamiso esilula sokunikeza amaphuzu esisekelwe ekuhlangenwe nakho kwabo emtholampilo.
Umsebenzi wabo ungeze ubufakazi obusha emikhombandlela yethu futhi futhi wenza inkomba ebalulekile yalolu bhubhane emhlabeni wonke.
Siyawusekela umsebenzi wabo obalulekile futhi sibabonge.
Nokho, umsebenzi wabo udinga ukubuyekezwa ngokuhambisana ne-Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines yakamuva ye-COVID-19 (Trial seventh version) kanye nezifundo zamuva.
Ngokwesigaba sesikhombisa (ngoMashi 3, 2020), ukuqinisekisa icala elisolisayo kudinga ukuhlanganisa noma yiliphi i-athikili yezinkomba zomlando wesifo nezinto ezimbili zokubonakaliswa komtholampilo ukwenza ukuhlaziywa okuphelele, noma kudinga ukuhlangabezana nezinto ezintathu zokubonakaliswa komtholampilo uma kungekho mlando ocacile wesifo:
Umlando wokugoma: (1) umlando wokuhamba noma wokuhlala edolobheni laseWuhan nasezindaweni ezizungezile, noma eminye imiphakathi lapho kwabikelwa khona ngamacala e-COVID-19 ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ezedlule ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (2) umlando wokuxhumana namacala atheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 (ngokuhlolwa kwe-nucleic acid okuhle); (3) umlando wokuxhumana neziguli ezinomkhuhlane noma izimpawu zokuphefumula ezivela edolobheni laseWuhan nasezindaweni ezizungezile, noma eminye imiphakathi lapho kwabikelwa khona nge-COVID-19 ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ezedlule ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (4) umlando wokuxhumana neqembu lamacala aqinisekisiwe (≥ amacala amabili anomkhuhlane kanye/noma izimpawu zokuphefumula kwenzeka kungakapheli amasonto amabili ezindaweni ezincane, njengekhaya, ihhovisi, ikilasi lesikole, njll.).
Izimpawu zomtholampilo: (1) umkhuhlane kanye/ noma izimpawu zokuphefumula; (2) ngezithombe zokutheleleka nge-COVID-19; (3) inani eliphelele lamangqamuzana amhlophe egazi abonisa inani elivamile, elincishisiwe, noma elincishisiwe lama-lymphocyte esigabeni sokuqala.
Ukuxilongwa kwesimo esiqinisekisiwe kufanele kusekelwe esimweni esisolisayo esinobufakazi obuthile be-pathogenic noma be-serological ngokulandelayo: (1) ukuhlolwa kwe-PCR kwesikhathi sangempela okubonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 iyatholakala; (2) ukulandelana kwe-genome yonke yegciwane okubonisa ukufana okuphezulu nama-coronavirus amasha aziwayo; (3) ukuhlolwa kwe-serum okubonisa ukuthi i-antibody ye-IgM ne-IgG ye-SARS-CoV-2 iyatholakala; noma ukuguqulwa kwe-antibody ye-IgG ye-SARS-CoV-2 kusuka kokubi iye kokuhle, noma i-titre inyuka izikhathi ezingu-≥4 esigabeni sokululama ngaphezu kwesesigabeni esibucayi.
Siyabona ukuthi ukuhlolwa kwe-PCR kwesikhathi sangempela kwe-nucleic acid emithonjeni yokuphefumula noma amasampula egazi kwengezwe kumagazini wesibili (Januwari 18, 2020) nowesithathu (January 22, 2020).
Ukutholwa kwe-pathogenic kwesampula yegazi kwengezwe kumagazini wesine (27 Januwari 2020) nowesihlanu (8 Februwari 2020); bese kufakwa ubufakazi be-serological kumagazini wesikhombisa.
Lezi zinguquko ezisekelwe kubacwaningi zaqhubeka nomsebenzi wokufuna ikhithi yokutholwa kwe-nucleic acid efanelekile yokuxilonga okusheshayo, kanye namasampula avela emithonjeni yokuphefumula kufaka phakathi ukuthathwa kwegazi, okwandisa ukutholakala kwamasampula ahlukene, futhi kwasekela ukuletha umphumela omuhle we-antibody ethile kumigomo eqinisekisiwe.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, kunobufakazi obuningi obusikhumbuza ukuba siqaphele iziguli ezinezimpawu ezingavamile nezingenayo.
Ngakho-ke, ishadi lokuhamba likaZhou et al. kufanele libuyekezwe, njengoba behlukanisa umuntu ongenazo izimpawu zomtholampilo ngokuthi unengozi ephansi.
Uhlelo lokulinganisa kufanele futhi luqinisekiswe eminye imikhuba nemiphumela yokuhlolwa kwemitholampilo.
Ekuphetheni, sinethemba lokuthi kuyoba nobufakazi obuqondile obengeziwe futhi simema abafundi ukuba banikeze imibono yabo.
Ukuze kutholakale ukuthi umuntu unaso yini "isimo esingasolwa" noma "isimo esiqinisekisiwe", siphakamisa ukuba balandele futhi balandele imihlahlandlela yakamuva yamazwe abo.
Ithimba lethu liyobuye libuyekeze ngesikhathi esifanele isiqondiso sethu ukuze linikeze usizo.
IBangladesh ibika ukufa kwabantu abahlanu ngenxa ye-COVID-19, okuyisilinganiso esiphakeme kakhulu sosuku
Izolo, iBangladesh iqinisekise ukufa kwabantu abahlanu abasha ngenxa ye-COVID-19 ngosuku.
Leli inani eliphakeme kakhulu labantu abafa ngosuku ngenxa yaleli gciwane.
Kusukela izolo, i-Institute of Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research (IEDCR) yaseBangladesh ibike ukuthi inani labantu abathelelekile eliqoshiwe lifaka abantu abangu-114 abasebenza kanye nabantu abangu-33 abasindile abahlala emakhaya.
Kuye kwaqoshwa abantu abangu-17 abashonile.
Engxoxweni yezindaba eku-inthanethi, umqondisi we-IEDCR, uDkt Meerjady Sabrina Flora, uthe ababulewe babehlanganisa abesilisa abane nowesifazane oyedwa.
NgokukaDkt. Meerjady, ababili babeneminyaka engaphezu kwengu-60, ababili babephakathi kuka-51 no-60 ubudala kanti oyedwa wayeneminyaka engu-41 kuya kwengu-50 ubudala.
Uphinde wathi ababili balaba babulawa babevela eDhaka.
Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba (i-WHO) yamemezela i-COVID-19 njengobhadane ngo-March 11.
Isikhulu sesibhedlela sathi ku-Anadolu Agency, i-news outlet yendawo, ukuthi omunye wabashonile kwakunguJalal Saifur Rahman, umqondisi we-Bengali Anti-Corruption Commission, owayelashwa eKuwait Maitree Hospital.
NgoMgqibelo, esethulweni sevidiyo esiku-inthanethi, uNgqongqoshe Wezokuthutha Emgwaqweni Namabhuloho eBangladesh u-Obaidul Quader uthe ezokuthutha zomphakathi zizovalwa isikhathi eside kunalokho obekuhleliwe ekuqaleni, kuze kube uMgqibelo ozayo.
Lokhu kuvalwa kwezokuthutha komphakathi kwaqala ngo-March 26 futhi kwakuhlelwe ukuba kuphele ngoMgqibelo, April 4.
Ukuthuthwa kwezimpahla ezibalulekile - ezokwelapha, uphethiloli nokudla - kwakusavunyelwe.
Izigameko zokuqala eziqoshiwe zokutheleleka nge-COVID-19 eBangladesh zenzeka ngo-March 8, kubantu ababili ababuya e-Italy kanye nomka omunye wabo.
Ngo-March 19, laba abathathu base belulame kakade.
I-SARS-CoV-2 idlula isibalo sabantu abayizigidi ezingu-1 abathelelekile emhlabeni wonke
NgoLwesine, inani eliphelele labantu abatheleleke nge-SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus ladlula isigidi emhlabeni wonke, ngokusho kwedatha yase-Johns Hopkins University.
Okungenani ukufa kwabantu abayizinkulungwane ezingu-52 kwakuhlobene ne-COVID-19, isifo esibangelwa i-coronavirus.
Lesi sigameko senzeka ngosuku olufanayo lapho iMalawi iqinisekisa khona ukuthi igciwane lokuqala le-coronavirus liyatholakala futhi iZambia yaba nokufa kwayo kokuqala okuhlobene ne-coronavirus.
INyakatho Korea yathi, kusukela ngoLwesine, ingelinye lamazwe ambalwa asele engenazo izifo ze-coronavirus.
Izolo, i-World Health Organization yabika iziguli ezingu-1,051,635, kuhlanganise neziguli ezingu-79,332 emahoreni angu-24 ngaphambi kuka-10 ekuseni ngesikhathi saseYurophu Ephakathi (0800 UTC) ngo-April 4.
E-United States, kwaqoshwa iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-244 000 ze-coronavirus, okuhlobene nokufa kwabantu okungenani abangu-5 900.
I-CBS News yabika, icaphuna idatha yase-Johns Hopkins University, kwaba nokufa kwabantu abangaphezu kuka-1 000 e-US ngoLwesithathu okubangelwa izifo ze-coronavirus.
Emhlabeni wonke, amazwe amemezela izinyathelo eziqinile zokuvimbela lesi sifo ukuba singasakazeki.
NgoLwesine, uSergei Sobyanin, umphathi-dolobha waseMoscow, wanweba isikhathi sokuvalwa komuzi kwaze kwaba ngo-May 1.
Ezweni lonke, uMengameli uVladimir Putin umemezele ukuthi abantu baseRussia bazoqhubeka bethola inkokhelo ngaphandle kokuya emsebenzini kuze kube ngu-April 30.
IPhalamende lasePortugal lavuma ukuqhubeka nesimo esibucayi sezinsuku ezingu-15; leli phasela lamukelwa ngamavoti angu-215 evuma, ayishumi enqaba, nelilodwa eliphikisayo.
ISaudi Arabia yelule isikhathi sokubuya ekhaya emadolobheni angcwele aseMecca naseMedina ukuba siqhubeke usuku lonke; ngaphambili, isikhathi sokubuya ekhaya sasisebenza kuphela phakathi kuka-3 ntambama no-6 ekuseni.
IThailand ihlele ukusebenzisa isikhathi sokubuya ekhaya phakathi kuka-10 ebusuku no-4 ekuseni.
Umbusi wase-Ohio, uMike DeWine, umemezele ukuthi lesi sifundazwe sesinwetshe umthetho wokuhlala ekhaya kuze kube ngo-May 1.
Izitolo zase-Australia zehlisa umkhawulo wephepha langasese ngokuthengiselana ngakunye
NgeSonto nangoMgqibelo kusihlwa, izitolo zase-Australia iWoolworths neColes zehlise imikhawulo yazo yokuthenga iphepha langasese yaba amaphakethe amabili nelilodwa ngokuthengiselana kuzo zonke izitolo ezingeni likazwelonke, ngokulandelana.
I-ALDI nayo yamisa umkhawulo wepakethe elilodwa, ngoMsombuluko.
Le mingcele yathunyelwa njengezindaba ezitolo zokuthenga, nasemakhasi e-Facebook alezi zinethiwekhi.
Kubikwa ukuthi abathengi babefaka izimpahla ngenxa yokwesaba i-COVID-19 uma kwenzeka abantu kudingeka bazihlukanise.
NgoLwesithathu, iWoolworths nayo yanciphisa ukuthengwa kwephepha langasese ukuze lithunyelwe ekhaya libe yiphakethe elilodwa ngomyalelo ngamunye.
Lezi zinguquko zalandela umkhawulo wangaphambilini wamaphakethe amane ngokuthengiselana owethulwe yiWoolworths neColes ngoMashi 4 no-5 ngokulandelana.
"I-Coles, ekumemezelweni kwayo kwabezindaba ngoMashi 8, yabika ukuthi ngokuvinjelwa kwamaphakethe amane, "izitolo eziningi zisathengisa kungakapheli ihora zihanjiswe", futhi yabiza isidingo ngokuthi "esingakaze sibe khona", kuyilapho i-ALDI, kokuthunyelwe kuFacebook ngoLwesibili, yakubiza ngokuthi "akunakulindeleka". "
"Ukuthengiswa kwezimpahla kukhuphuke kakhulu ngesonto eledlule, kusho okhulumela iWoolworths".
Isitolo seCostco eCanberra naso savimbela inani elivunyelwe ukuba libe amaphakethe amabili ngesonto eledlule.
Ukuze kuqedwe lokhu kuncipha, uColes wayala amaphakheji amakhulu kubaphakeli futhi wakhulisa imvamisa yokulethwa, uWoolworths wayala isitokwe esengeziwe, kuyilapho u-ALDI enza izimpahla zesiphakamiso esihleliwe ngoLwesithathu zingatholakali kusenesikhathi.
URussell Zimmerman, umqondisi omkhulu we-Australian Retailers Association, wathi abathengisi bazama ukwandisa isitokwe, kodwa imikhawulo yomkhandlu wendawo mayelana nesikhathi sokuthumela ngamaloli yenza kube nzima.
Ulindele ukuthi izindleko zokukhiqiza ziyokhuphuka, njengoba abahlinzeki bezama ukuhlangabezana nesidingo, futhi kube nezinhlobo ezincane zokudla okukhethekile.
NgoLwesibili, i-ALDI yamemezela ukuthi ngenxa yokukhululwa kwesitoko kusenesikhathi, ezinye izitolo azisakwazi ukuhambisa okhethekile ngoLwesithathu.
Embikweni weNews.com.au, uDkt. Gary Mortimer, onguchwepheshe wezentengiselwano waseQueensland University of Technology, wathi izitolo zigcwalisa isitoko njalo ebusuku.
Waphawula ukuthi iphepha langasese liyisitoko esikhulu, okuholela ekubeni kube nenani elincane lezinqolobane, futhi, lapho selishonile, lishiya izindawo ezinkulu zamashalofu zingenalutho, okwenza kube nomuzwa wokuthi asikho.
UColes noWoolworths banombono [wokuthi] uma bekunokuningi eshalofini, uma umkhiqizo onjengama-toilet roll kanye nosinki wokuhlanza ungathengwa [futhi ukhona] ngobuningi, cishe ubunganciphisa ukwethuka, kusho uRussell Zimmerman nge-ABC News.
Umkhiqizi wephepha langasese elivuselelekayo uWho Gives a Crap wathi ngoLwesithathu odlule babephelelwe isitoko.
UKimberly-Clark, owenza i-Kleenex Toilet Tissue, neSolaris Paper eyenza iSorbent, bagcizelela ukuthi basebenza amahora angu-24 ngosuku ukuze balondoloze izimpahla, ngokombiko weNews.com.au.
I-Domain.com, indawo yezindlu, yabika ukuthi abanye abathengisi bezindlu banikeza iphepha langasese mahhala kumthengi wokuqala lapho kudayiswa eMelbourne, lapho kudayiswa kancane ngenxa yokuthi abathengi banesikhathi sokuphumula ngempelasonto ende yoSuku Lwezisebenzi.
Umagazini wangoLwesine we-NT News, iphepha lansuku zonke elinyatheliswa eDarwin, wawuqukethe isembozo samakhasi angu-8 esasiklanyelwe ukusikwa futhi sisetshenziswe njengamaphepha angcolile.
Izitolo ekuqaleni zazingafuni ukubeka imikhawulo, ngokombiko we-ABC Australia ngo-March 3 lapho zithi azinakho ukuhlela ukufaka imikhawulo ekuthengeni.
URussell Zimmerman wanezela ukuthi eminye imikhiqizo nayo idingeka kakhulu, kuhlanganise namaski, isicoci sezempilo, izimpahla ezomisiwe, ukugeza izandla nofulawa.
Ngokufanayo, ngaphandle kwe-Australia, ngeSonto kusihlwa isitolo esikhulu saseBrithani i-Ocado sabonwa sinciphisa ukuthengwa kwephepha langasese lika-Andres emabhokisini amabili angu-12.
Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba imemezela ukuthi i-COVID-19 iyisifo esiwumshayabhuqe
NgoLwesithathu, i-World Health Organization (WHO) yamemezela ukuthi ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19  isifo esibangelwa i-coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  kuyisifo esiwumqedazwe.
"Nakuba igama elithi ""ubhubhane"" libhekisela kuphela ekutheni isifo sisakazeke kangakanani, hhayi ukuthi amacala athile ayingozi kangakanani, i-WHO yaphawula isidingo sokushayela ohulumeni ukuba benze okuthile:"
Wonke amazwe asengayiguqula inkambo yalolu bhubhane.
Uma amazwe ethola, ahlola, elapha, ahlukanisa, alandelela futhi ahlanganise abantu bawo ekuphenduleni, kusho uTedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, uMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO.
Sikhathazeke kakhulu ngezinga eliphazamisayo lokusabalala nobunzima kanye nezinga eliphazamisayo lokungenzi lutho.
"Ngokusho kukaDkt Tom Frieden, owayengumqondisi we-United States' Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, lolu bhubhane "aluzange lube khona ngaphambili".
"Wathi, emazwini ashicilelwe yi-CNN ngoFebhuwari, ""ngaphandle komkhuhlane, alikho elinye igciwane lokuphefumula eliye lalandelwa kusukela ekuveleni kwalo kuya ekusakazekeni kwalo emhlabeni wonke okuqhubekayo".
"UGhebreyesus waveza umbono ofanayo, ethi ""asikaze sibone ubhadane olubangelwa yigciwane le-coronavirus. """
Waqhubeka, ""futhi asikaze sibone ubhadane olungalawulwa ngasikhathi sinye".
Isimo esisha njengesifo esiwumqedazwe silandela isinqumo se-WHO ngoJanuwari sokumemezela ukuqubuka kwesimo esiphuthumayo sezempilo yomphakathi esiyinkinga yomhlaba wonke.
"Umqondisi we-United States' National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Disease, uDkt Anthony Fauci, wathi ngokuqubuka kwalo, ""ngokuyinhloko, kuzoba kubi kakhulu""".
Kusukela ngoLwesine, i-Associated Press yabika ukuthi okungenani kwakunezigameko ezingu-126 000 ze-COVID-19 emhlabeni wonke, okwaholela ekufeni kwabantu abangaphezu kuka-4 600.
Ubhadane lwe-coronavirus 201920 luwubhadane oluqhubekayo lwesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19), olubangelwa i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (i-SARS-CoV-2).
Lesi sifo saqala ukubonakala eWuhan, eChina, ngoDisemba 2019, samenyezelwa ukuthi siyisimo esiphuthumayo sezempilo yomphakathi esiphazamisa amazwe omhlaba ngoJanuwari 30, 2020, futhi samenyezelwa njengobhadane ngoMashi 11, 2020.
Kusukela ngo-April 10, 2020, cishe abantu abayizigidi ezingu-1.61 babike ukuthi bane-COVID-19 emazweni angu-210 nasezifundeni, okwaholela ekufeni kwabantu abangaba ngu-97,000.
Abantu abangaba ngu-364 000 baye balulama.
Izinga lokufa kweziguli lilinganiselwa ku-4% eChina, kanti emhlabeni wonke lisukela ku-13.04% e-Algeria kuya ku-0.08% eNew Zealand.
Izimpawu ezivamile zihlanganisa umkhuhlane, ukukhwehlela nokuphefumula kanzima.
Izinkinga zingase zihlanganise i-pneumonia kanye ne-acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Isikhathi esivela ekuvezweni kuya ekubonakaleni kwezimpawu ngokuvamile siyizinsuku ezinhlanu, kodwa singaba phakathi kwezinsuku ezimbili kuya kwezingu-14.
Awukho umuthi wokugoma noma ukwelashwa okuqondile kwegciwane okwaziwayo.
Ukwelashwa okuyisisekelo ukwelashwa okubonisa izimpawu nokwesekelayo. Izinyathelo zokuvimbela ezinconywayo zihlanganisa ukugeza izandla, ukumboza umlomo lapho ukhwehlela, ukugcina ibanga nabanye abantu, nokuqapha nokuzihlukanisa kubantu abasola ukuthi banegciwane.
Iziphathimandla emhlabeni wonke ziye zaphendula ngokubeka imingcele yokuhamba, ukuvalelwa kwabantu, isikhathi sokuphumula, ukulawula izingozi emsebenzini nokuvala izakhiwo.
Lesi sifo siholele ekuphazamisekeni okukhulu kwezenhlalo nezomnotho emhlabeni wonke, ukuhlehliswa noma ukukhanselwa kwemicimbi yezemidlalo, yenkolo, yezombusazwe neyezamasiko, kanye nokushoda okubanzi kwezinto zokuphakelayo okubangelwa ukuthenga ngokweqile.
Izikole namayunivesithi kuvaliwe ezweni lonke noma endaweni ethile emazweni angu-193, okuye kwathinta cishe amaphesenti angu-99.4 abafundi emhlabeni.
Ulwazi olungamanga mayelana naleli gciwane selusakazeke ku-intanethi, futhi kube khona izigameko zokwenyanya abantu bakwamanye amazwe nokucwasa abantu baseChina, abanye abantu abavela eMpumalanga naseNingizimu-mpumalanga ye-Asia kanye nokubukeka kwabo, nabanye abavela ezindaweni ezinamacala amakhulu egciwane.
Ngenxa yokwehla kwezinga lokuhamba nokuvalwa kwezimboni ezisindayo, kuye kwaba nokwehla kokungcola komoya nokukhishwa kwe-carbon.
