Kuleli qembu lokuqala lamacala abikwa ngoDisemba 2019, kwatholakala ukuthi izingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu zinokuxhumana nemakethe.
Ngo-March 13, 2020, umbiko ongaqinisekisiwe ovela kuyi-South China Morning Post wasikisela ukuthi icala elibuyele emuva ku-17 November 2019, kumuntu oneminyaka engu-55 ubudala waseSifundazweni saseHubei, kungenzeka ukuthi laqala. Ngo-February 26, 2020, i-WHO yabika ukuthi, njengoba amacala amasha kubikwa ukuthi ancipha eChina kodwa anda ngokuzumayo e-Italy, e-Iran naseNingizimu Korea, inani lamacala amasha angaphandle kweChina lidlule inani lamacala amasha ngaphakathi eChina okokuqala ngqa.
