Lezi zibalo ziyahlukahluka kuye ngendawo nangesikhathi, futhi zithonywa inani lokuhlolwa, ikhwalithi yohlelo lwezempilo, izinketho zokwelashwa, isikhathi kusukela ekuqubukeni kokuqala, kanye nezici zabantu ezifana nobudala, ubulili, nempilo jikelele. Isilinganiso sokufa ngecala sibonisa inani lokufa elihlukaniswe ngenani lamacala atholakele ngaphakathi kwesikhathi esinikeziwe.
