Izimpawu ze-COVID-19 zingase zingabi eziqondile futhi abantu abangenalo igciwane bangase bangabi nazo izimpawu.
Izimpawu ezimbili ezivame kakhulu ukushisa (88%) nokukhwehlela okomile (68%).
Izimpawu ezingavamile zihlanganisa ukukhathala, ukukhiqizwa kwe-sputum yokuphefumula (umnkantsha), ukulahlekelwa umuzwa wokuhogela, ukuphefumula kanzima, ubuhlungu bemisipha namalunga, ubuhlungu bomphimbo, ikhanda, ukushaya kwamakhaza, ukuhlanza, ukuvuvukala kwegazi, isifo sohudo noma i-cyanosis. I-WHO ithi cishe umuntu oyedwa kwabayisithupha ugula kakhulu futhi unenkinga yokuphefumula.
Izikhungo Zase-U.S. Zokulawulwa Nokuvikelwa Kwezifo (CDC) zibhala izimpawu eziphuthumayo njengobunzima bokuphefumula, ubuhlungu besifuba obuqhubekayo noma ingcindezi, ukudideka okungazelelwe, ubunzima bokuvuka, nobuso noma izindebe eziluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka; ukunakekelwa kwezokwelapha ngokushesha kuyalulekwa uma lezi zimpawu zikhona. Ukuthuthuka kwesifo kungaholela ekuvuvukeleni kwamaphaphu okunzima, i-acute respiratory distress syndrome, i-sepsis, i-septic shock nokufa.
Abanye balabo abathelelekile bangase bangabi nazo izimpawu, bangabi nazo izimpawu zomtholampilo kodwa babe nemiphumela yokuhlolwa eqinisekisa ukutheleleka, ngakho abacwaningi baye banikeza iseluleko sokuthi labo abaxhumana eduze nabantu abathelelekile kufanele babhekwe futhi bahlolwe ukuze kungatholakali ukutheleleka.
Izilinganiso zaseChina zesilinganiso sokungabi nezimpawu zisukela ku-44% kuya ku-45%.
Isikhathi esivamile sokufukamela (isikhathi esiphakathi kokutheleleka nokuqala kwezimpawu) sisukela ezinsukwini ezingu-1 kuya kwezingu-14; ngokuvamile siyizinsuku ezinhlanu. Njengesibonelo sokungaqiniseki, ukulinganiselwa kwesilinganiso sabantu abane-COVID-19 abalahlekelwa umuzwa wabo wokuhogela ekuqaleni kwakungu-30% futhi kamuva kwehla kwaba ngu-15%.
Eminye imininingwane yendlela lesi sifo esisakazeka ngayo isazolungiswa.
Lesi sifo kukholakala ukuthi sisakazeka ngokuyinhloko lapho umuntu esondelene naye futhi ngamaconsi amancane akhiqizwa lapho ekhwehlela, ethimula noma ekhuluma; lapho umuntu esondelene naye engamamitha angu-1 kuya kwangu-2 (3 kuya ku-6 feet).
Ucwaningo luye lwathola ukuthi ukukhwehlela kungabonakali kungabangela ukuba amaconsi ahambe amamitha angu-4.5 (amamitha angu-15) kuya kwangu-8.2 (amamitha angu-27).
Abanye baye basikisela ukuthi leli gciwane lingadluliselwa futhi ngamaconsi amancane ahlala isikhathi eside emoyeni, angakhiqizwa lapho kukhulunywa. Amaconsi okuphefumula angakhiqizwa nalapho uphefumula, kuhlanganise nalapho ukhuluma, nakuba igciwane lingadluliselwa emoyeni.
La manzi angangena emlonyeni noma emakhaleni abantu abaseduze noma mhlawumbe angangenwa ngamaphaphu.
Ezinye izinqubo zezokwelapha ezinjengokufakwa kwe-intubation nokuvuselelwa kwenhliziyo namaphaphu (CPR) zingenza ukuba izitho eziphuma emaphashini okuphefumula zikhishwe emoyeni bese zisakazeka emoyeni.
Ingase futhi isakazeke lapho umuntu ethinta indawo engcolile, kuhlanganise nesikhumba, bese ethinta amehlo, ikhala noma umlomo.
Nakuba kunokukhathazeka ngokuthi ingase isakazeke ngokukhishwa kwendle, le ngozi kukholakala ukuthi incane.
Uhulumeni waseChina waphika ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 idluliselwe ngomlomo ngomchamo. Leli gciwane litheleleka kakhulu phakathi nezinsuku ezintathu zokuqala ngemuva kokuqala kwezimpawu, nakuba ukusakazeka kungenzeka ngaphambi kokuba kuvele izimpawu nasezigabeni zakamuva zesifo.
Abantu baye bathola lesi sifo ezinsukwini ezintathu ngaphambi kokuba kuqale izimpawu ezibonisa ukuthi kungenzeka ukudluliselwa ngaphambi kokuba kuvele izimpawu ezibalulekile.
Zimbalwa imibiko yamagciwane aqinisekiswe elebhu, kodwa amazwe athile aye athola ukuthi ayadluliselwa ngesikhathi kwenziwa uphenyo lokulandelela abantu abathintekayo.
I-European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC) ithi nakuba kungacaci kahle ukuthi lesi sifo sisakazeka kalula kangakanani, umuntu oyedwa ngokuvamile ugulisa abanye ababili kuya kwabathathu. Igciwane lihlala amahora amaningi noma izinsuku eziningi ezindaweni.
Ngokuqondile, kwatholakala ukuthi leli gciwane lingatholakala izinsuku ezintathu epulasitiki (i-polypropylene) nensimbi engagqwali engu-304, usuku olulodwa ekhadibhodi, namahora amane ethusi.
Nokho, lokhu kuyahlukahluka kuye ngomswakama nezinga lokushisa. Izilwane ezifuywayo nezinye izilwane ziye zahlolwa zaba ne-COVID-19.
Abukho ubufakazi bokuthi izilwane zingadlulisela leli gciwane kubantu, nakuba iziphathimandla zaseBrithani zeluleka umuntu ukuba ageze izandla ngemva kokuthintana nezilwane, njengalapho ethinta ezinye izinto abantu abangase bathinte abantu abanegciwane.
I-coronavirus syndrome yokuphefumula eyingozi kakhulu engu-2 (i-SARS-CoV-2) yigciwane elisha, elahlukaniswa okokuqala kubantu abathathu abanesifo samaphaphu esihlobene neqembu lamacala esifo sokuphefumula esibi eWuhan.
Zonke izici zegciwane elisha le-SARS-CoV-2 zenzeka kuma-coronavirus ahlobene emvelweni.Ngaphandle komzimba womuntu, leli gciwane libulawa insipho yasendlini, echitha isivikelo salo.I-SARS-CoV-2 ihlobene kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV yasekuqaleni.
