Ukuqhathaniswa kwe-genome yonke kuze kube manje kuthole okungenani u-92% wezinto zofuzo ezabiwe phakathi kwe-pangolin coronavirus ne-SARS-CoV-2, okunganele ukufakazela ukuthi ama-pangolin angumgcini ophakathi.
