Abasebenzisi bathola umyalezo uma beye baxhumana eduze nomuntu obonakele ene-COVID-19. Kuye kwavela imibono eyiphutha ngendlela yokuvimbela ukutheleleka; isibonelo, ukugeza ikhala nokugqumisa ngomlomo akuphumeleli.
Awukho umuthi wokugomela i-COVID-19, nakuba izinhlangano eziningi zisebenza ekuthuthukiseni owodwa.
