IJapane yanikela ngezifihla-buso eziyisigidi eWuhan, iTurkey yathumela imishini yezokwelapha, iRussia yathumela izinto zokwelapha ezingaphezu kwamathani angu-13 eWuhan, iMalaysia yamemezela ukunikela ngamasokisi ezokwelapha ayizigidi ezingu-18 eChina, iJalimane yanikela ngezinto zokwelapha ezihlukahlukene kuhlanganise nezingubo ze-Hazmat ezingu-10,000, kanti i-United States yanikela ngamathani angu-17.8 ezimpahla zokwelapha eChina futhi yathembisa ukusiza ngezimali emazweni athintekile ngemali eyengeziwe eyizigidi ezingu-$100. Ngemva kokuba amacala eChina ebonakala ehle, izwe liye lathumela usizo emazweni ahlukahlukene athintwe yilesi sifo.
Ngo-March, iChina, iCuba neRussia bathumela izimpahla zezokwelapha nochwepheshe ukusiza i-Italy ukubhekana nokuqubuka kwayo kwe-coronavirus.
Usomabhizinisi uJack Ma wathumela amakhithi okuhlola ayizigidi ezingu-1,1, izifihla-buso zobuso eziyizigidi eziyisithupha, nezingubo zokuzivikela ezingu-60,000 e-Addis Ababa, e-Ethiopia ukuze zisakazwe yi-African Union.
Kamuva wathumela amathuluzi okuhlola angu-5 000, izifihla-buso zobuso ezingu-100 000 namathuluzi okuphefumula ama-5 ePanama.
UMa waphinde wanikela ngezidingo zezokwelapha eCanada. INetherlands, iSpain, iTurkey, iGeorgia neCzech Republic bazwakalisa ukukhathazeka kwabo ngamamaski namathuluzi okuhlola enziwe eChina.
Ngokwesibonelo, iSpain yakhipha amakhithi okuhlola i-coronavirus angu-58,000 enziwe eChina anenani lokunemba elingama-30% kuphela, kuyilapho iNetherlands ikhumbula izifihla-buso ezingama-600,000 zaseChina ezazinamaphutha.
IBelgium yabiza amaski angu-100 000 angasetshenziswa, okwakuthiwa avela eChina, kodwa empeleni ayevela eColombia.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, usizo lwaseChina lwamukelwa kahle ezingxenyeni ezithile zeLatin America nase-Afrika. Ngo-April 2, iBhange Lomhlaba laqala imisebenzi yosizo oluphuthumayo emazweni asathuthuka.
I-WHO iye yancoma imizamo yeziphathimandla zaseChina ekulawuleni nasekubambeni lolu bhubhane.
"I-WHO yaphawula umehluko phakathi kokuqubuka kwe-SARS ngo-2002 no-2004, lapho iziphathimandla zaseChina zazisola ngokufihla okuthile okwavimbela imizamo yokuvimbela nokuvimbela, kanye nenkinga yamanje lapho uhulumeni omkhulu ""enikeze izibuyekezo ezijwayelekile ukugwema ukwethuka ngaphambi kwamaholide oNyaka Omusha WamaLunar"."
"NgoJanuwari 23, lapho ephendula isinqumo seziphathimandla eziyinhloko sokusebenzisa ukuvinjelwa kokuhamba eWuhan, ummeleli we-WHO uGauden Galea waphawula ukuthi nakuba "kungeyona neze incomo eyenziwe yi-WHO", futhi "kwakuyisibonakaliso esibaluleke kakhulu sokuzibophezela ekuvimbeleni ubhubhane endaweni lapho lugxile khona kakhulu" futhi walibiza ngokuthi "elingenakulinganiswa emlandweni wezempilo yomphakathi".NgoJanuwari 30, ngemuva kokuqinisekiswa kokudluliselwa komuntu nomuntu ngaphandle kweChina nokwanda kwezigameko kwamanye amazwe, i-WHO yamemezela ukuqubuka kwegciwane njenge-Public Health Emergency of International Concern (PHEIC), i-PHEIC yesithupha selokhu kwaqala ukusetshenziswa lesi sinyathelo ngesikhathi somkhuhlane wango-2009.
"UMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO uTedros Adhanom wathi i-PHEIC ibangelwa ""yingozi yokusabalala komhlaba wonke, ikakhulukazi emazweni anemali ephansi naphakathi nendawo angenayo uhlelo lwezempilo oluqinile".
"Ephendula ngokusetshenziswa kwemikhawulo yokuhamba, uTedros wathi ""asikho isizathu sezinyathelo eziphazamisa ngokungadingekile ukuhamba nokuhweba kwamazwe omhlaba"" nokuthi ""i-WHO ayincomi ukukhawulela ukuhweba nokuhamba""".
"Ngo-5 kuFebhuwari, i-WHO yanxusa umphakathi womhlaba wonke ukuba unikele ngezigidi ezingu-675 zamaRandi ukuze kusekelwe ukulungela amasu emazweni anemali encane, isisho ukuphuthuma kokusekela lawo mazwe 'angenazo izinhlelo zokuthola abantu abathole leli gciwane, ngisho noma lingase livele.'"
"UTedros uphinde wenza izitatimende ezithi ""siqine njengesixhumanisi sethu esibuthakathaka kakhulu"" futhi wanxusa umphakathi wamazwe omhlaba ukuba ""utshale imali namuhla noma ukhokhe okuningi kamuva"". NgoFebhuwari 11, i-WHO emhlanganweni wezindaba yamisa i-COVID-19 njengegama lalesi sifo".
"Ngalo lolo suku, uTedros wathi uNobhala-Jikelele we-UN u-António Guterres wayevumile ukuhlinzeka "ngamandla esimiso sonke se-UN ekuphenduleni".
"Ithimba Lokuphatha Izinkinga Le-UN laqala ukusebenza ngenxa yalokho, okuvumela ukuxhumanisa yonke impendulo yeZizwe Ezihlangene, i-WHO ethi izovumela ukuthi ""igxile empendulweni yezempilo ngenkathi ezinye izinhlaka zingaletha ubuchwepheshe bazo ukuze zisebenze emiphumeleni ebanzi yezenhlalo, yezomnotho nentuthuko yalolu bhubhane"."
"Ngo-14 kuFebhuwari, kwaqaliswa iqembu le-WHO eliholwa yi-Joint Mission Team neChina ukuhlinzeka ngochwepheshe bamazwe omhlaba kanye ne-WHO endaweni yaseChina ukusiza ekuphathweni kwasekhaya nasekuhloleni ""ubukhulu nokudluliselwa kwesifo"" ngokubamba ama-workshop nemihlangano nezikhungo ezibalulekile ezingeni likazwelonke kanye nokuqhuba ukuvakasha kwensimu ukuhlola ""umthelela wemisebenzi yokuphendula ezingeni lezifundazwe nezindawo, kufaka phakathi izindawo zasemadolobheni nezasemakhaya"".Ngo-25 kuFebhuwari, i-WHO yamemezela ukuthi ""umhlaba kufanele wenze okuningi ukulungiselela ubhadane lwe-coronavirus olungenzeka","" yathi yize kusesekuseni kakhulu ukuwubiza ngokuthi ubhadane, amazwe kufanele noma kunjalo abe "esigabeni sokulungela"."
"Njengoba kwakukhona ukuqubuka kwesifo e-Iran, i-WHO yathumela iqembu leJoint Mission Team lapho ukuze lihlole isimo. NgoFebhuwari 28, izikhulu ze-WHO zathi ukuhlolwa kwesongo le-coronavirus emhlabeni wonke kuzokwenyuswa kusuka ku- ""high"" kuya ku- ""very high"", okuyisilinganiso esiphakeme kakhulu sokuxwayisa nokuhlola ubungozi".
"UMike Ryan, umqondisi oyinhloko wohlelo lwezimo eziphuthumayo zezempilo lwe-WHO, waxwayisa esitatimendeni esithi ""Lokhu kuwukuhlola iqiniso kuwo wonke ohulumeni emhlabeni: Phaphamani".
"Leli gciwane kungenzeka lisendleleni futhi kudingeka ulungele", ephikelela ngokuthi izinyathelo zokuphendula ezifanele zingasiza umhlaba ugweme "okubi kakhulu".
"URyan uphinde wathi imininingwane yamanje ayibagunyazi izikhulu zezempilo yomphakathi ukuba zimemezele ubhadane lomhlaba wonke, ethi isimemezelo esinjalo singasho ukuthi ""siyakwamukela ukuthi wonke umuntu emhlabeni uzobe ethelelekile ngaleli gciwane""".
Ngo-March 11, i-WHO yamemezela ukuthi ukuqubuka kwe-coronavirus kuyinkinga yomhlaba wonke.
"UMqondisi-Jikelele uthe i-WHO "yayikhathazeke kakhulu ngamazinga asabisayo okusakazeka nobunzima, kanye namazinga asabisayo okungenzi lutho". I-WHO ibhekane nokugxekwa okukhulu ngalokho okubhekwa njengokuphatha kabi ubhadane, kufaka phakathi ukumenyezelwa kwesikhathi okuphuthumayo kwezempilo yomphakathi nokuhlukaniswa kwegciwane njengobhadane. "
Ukuphikisana kwahlanganisa nesicelo sokuba uMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO uTedros Adhanom ashiye isikhundla sakhe, esasayinwe abantu abangu-733,000 kusukela ngo-April 6.
Ngo-March 26, 2020, ochwepheshe abaningi bamalungelo abantu be-UN bagcizelela ukuhlonipha amalungelo omuntu ngamunye ngesikhathi sobhadane lwe-COVID-19.
Leli qembu lochwepheshe lathi wonke umuntu unelungelo lokungenela ukuze kusindiswe ukuphila futhi uhulumeni unomthwalo wemfanelo.
Leli qembu lagcizelela ukuthi ukuntuleka kwemithombo noma umshwalense wezempilo akufanele neze kube isizathu sokubandlulula iqembu elithile.
Ochwepheshe bagcizelela ukuthi wonke umuntu unelungelo lokuthola impilo, kuhlanganise nabantu abakhubazekile, abangamalungu amaqembu amancane, asebekhulile, abantu abaphoqelelwe ukuba baphume emakhaya abo, abangenamakhaya, labo abahlala ezimweni ezimbi kakhulu, abantu abavalelwe ejele, kanye nababaleki namanye amaqembu angachaziwe adinga ukusekelwa uhulumeni.
Izinhlangano zikahulumeni zamazwe ngamazwe zibhekana nemiphumela yezomnotho neyenhlalo yenkinga ye-COVID-19.
Inhlangano Yezokuxhumana Nokuhlakulela Ezomnotho isiqalise ipulatifomu yokunikeza ulwazi olufike ngesikhathi noluphelele ngezimpendulo zezombusazwe emazweni emhlabeni wonke, kanye nemibono nezeluleko.
Kusukela ezinqubomeni zokuqinisa izinhlelo zezempilo kanye nomnotho womhlaba kuya ekubhekaneni nemiphumela yokuvalwa kanye nemikhawulo yokuhamba, isikhungo sedijithali sihlanganisa i-Country Policy Tracker, futhi sihlose ukusiza amazwe afunde komunye nomunye futhi asize ukuphendula okuhlanganisiwe komhlaba wonke enkingeni ye-coronavirus.
Uhulumeni waseChina ugxekwe yi-United States, uNgqongqoshe weKhabhinethi wase-UK uMichael Gove, nendodana kaMongameli waseBrazil uJair Bolsonaro u-Eduardo Bolsonaro ngokusingatha kwayo lolu bhubhane, olwaqala esifundazweni saseChina iHubei.
Izikhulu eziningana eziphezulu eziphezulu zeqembu lamaKhomanisi laseChina (CPC) zaxoshwa ngenxa yokusingatha kwazo imizamo yokuvalelwa kwabantu eChina Ephakathi, okuyisibonakaliso sokunganeliseki ngendlela ezombusazwe eziphendula ngayo kulolu bhubhane kulezo zifunda.
Abanye abahlaziyi bakholelwa ukuthi lesi sinyathelo sasihloselwe ukuvikela unobhala-jikelele weqembu lamaKhomanisi laseChina uXi Jinping olakeni lomphakathi ngenxa yokuqubuka kwegciwane le-coronavirus.
Ezinye izikhulu zaseChina, isibonelo uZhao Lijian, zenqaba ukuvuma kwangaphambilini kokugqashuka kwegciwane le-coronavirus okuqale eWuhan, ngenxa yemibono yomkhankaso mayelana ne-COVID-19 evela e-US noma e-Italy.
"Uhulumeni wase-US kaDonald Trump ubhekise kwi-coronavirus ngokuthi ""igciwane laseChina"" noma ""igciwane laseWuhan"" ethi iChina ""iyenze yaba igciwane manje eseliphenduke ubhadane lomhlaba wonke"", okuye kwagxekwa abanye abagxeki ngokuthi ubuhlanga futhi ""kuphazamisa ukwehluleka kukahulumeni wakhe ukuvimba lesi sifo"."
"I-Daily Beast yathola ucingo lukahulumeni wase-US olwalubonisa iqhinga lokuxhumana ngokusobala elivela eMkhandlwini Wezokuphepha Kazwelonke, futhi isu lacaphuna ngokuthi ""Konke kumayelana neChina".
"Sitshelwa ukuba sizame ukusabalalisa lo myalezo nganoma iyiphi indlela, kuhlanganise nezingqungquthela zabezindaba nokuvela kuthelevishini. ""Izitolo ezinjengePolitico, Foreign Policy, neBloomberg ziye zathi imizamo yaseChina yokuthumela usizo emazweni athintwe yileli gciwane iyingxenye yokufuna ithonya emhlabeni wonke".
"Isikhulu senqubomgomo yezangaphandle ye-EU uJosep Borrell waxwayisa ngokuthi kukhona ""ingxenye yezwe yezombusazwe ehlanganisa umzabalazo wethonya ngokusebenzisa ukujikeleza kanye 'nezepolitiki zokuphana.'"
"UBorrell uphinde wathi ""I-China icindezela ngamandla umyalezo wokuthi, ngokungafani ne-US, ingumlingani onomthwalo wemfanelo nothembekile. """
I-China ibuye yacela i-US ukuba isuse izijeziso zayo eSyria, eVenezuela nase-Iran, kuyilapho kubikwa ukuthi ithumela usizo kula mazwe amabili okugcina.
Umnikelo kaJack Ma wamamaski ayi-100 000 eCuba wavinjelwa yizinhlawulo zase-US ngo-Ephreli 3.
Iziphathimandla zaseMelika ziye zasolwa ngokuqondisa kabusha usizo olwaluhloselwe ezinye izizwe luye ezweni lazo.
Futhi kuye kwabikwa izingxabano ezihlobene nemaski phakathi kwamanye amazwe, njengeJalimane, i-Austria neSwitzerland; neCzech Republic ne-Italy.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, iTurkey yabamba amakhulu ama-ventilator ayeya eSpain.
Ekuqaleni kuka-March, uhulumeni wase-Italy wagxeka ukuntuleka kobumbano lwe-European Union ne-Italy eyathinteka yi-coronavirus.
"UMaurizio Massari, inxusa lase-Italy e-EU, wathi ""YiChina kuphela eyaphendula kabili".
"Ngokuqinisekile, lokhu akusona isibonakaliso esihle sokubambisana kweYurophu".
Ngo-March 22, ngemva kokukhuluma ngocingo noNdunankulu wase-Italy uGiuseppe Conte, umongameli waseRussia uVladimir Putin wahlela ukuba ibutho laseRussia lithumele odokotela bezempi, izimoto ezikhethekile zokubulala amagciwane, nezinye izinto zokwelapha e-Italy.
"Iphephandaba lase-Italy iLa Stampa lacaphuna "umthombo wezombusazwe osezingeni eliphakeme" ongaziwa ukuthi amaphesenti angu-80 osizo lwaseRussia "awalusizo noma alusebenzi kangako e-Italy".
"Umthombo usola iRussia ngokuqala ukuhlasela "kwezombangazwe nezombusazwe".
UMongameli waseLombardy, u-Attilio Fontana, noNgqongqoshe Wezangaphandle wase-Italy uLuigi Di Maio bayixosha imibiko yabezindaba futhi babonga.
IRussia yathumela indiza ethwala izimpahla enosizo lwezokwelapha e-United States.
"Usomlomo waseKremlin uDmitry Peskov wathi ""lapho enikeza usizo kozakwabo baseMelika, [uPutin] ucabanga ukuthi lapho abakhiqizi baseMelika bemishini yezokwelapha nezinto zokwakha bethola umfutho, nabo bazokwazi ukuphendula uma kunesidingo. """
"Ukuzivocavoca kwezempi kweNATO okuhleliwe "Defender 2020"" eJalimane, ePoland, naseBaltic States, ukuzivocavoca kwempi okukhulu kweNATO kusukela ekupheleni kweMpi Yomshoshaphansi, kuzobanjelwa ngezinga elincane".
"Usonobhala-jikelele weCampaign for Nuclear Disarmament uKate Hudson wagxeka ukuzivocavoca kweDefender 2020: ""Enkinga yamanje yezempilo yomphakathi, akubeki engozini izimpilo zamasosha ase-US kanye namazwe amaningi aseYurophu abamba iqhaza kuphela kodwa nezakhamuzi zamazwe asebenza kuwo. ""Uhulumeni wase-Iran uthinteke kakhulu yileli gciwane, amalungu ePhalamende angaba ngu-20 athelelekile kanye nezinye izikhulu zezombusazwe eziyishumi nanhlanu ezikhona noma ezikhona".
UMengameli wase-Iran uHassan Rouhani wabhala incwadi yomphakathi eya kubaholi bomhlaba ecela usizo ngoMashi 14, 2020, ethi izwe lakhe lizama kanzima ukulwa nalolu bhubhane ngenxa yokuntuleka kokufinyelela ezimakethe zomhlaba ngenxa yezinhlawulo zase-United States ngokumelene ne-Iran. Ukuqubuka kwabangela ukuba i-United States yamukele izinqubomgomo zezenhlalo ezivamile kwamanye amazwe acebile, kufaka phakathi ukunakekelwa kwezempilo okujwayelekile, ukunakekelwa kwezingane okujwayelekile, ikhefu lomndeni elikhokhelwayo, namazinga aphezulu okuxhaswa kwezimali kwezempilo yomphakathi.
Abahlaziyi bezombusazwe balindele ukuthi kungathinta kabi amathuba kaDonald Trump okuphinde akhethwe okhethweni lukamongameli lwango-2020. Ubudlelwano bezombusazwe phakathi kweJapan neNingizimu Korea buye baba bubi ngenxa yalolu bhubhane.
"INingizimu Korea yagxeka imizamo yaseJapane "yokugwema ukungacaci nokuzibandakanya" ngemuva kokuba iJapane imemezele ukuthi noma ubani ovela eNingizimu Korea uzobekwa e-quarantine amasonto amabili ezindaweni eziqokwe uhulumeni".
Umphakathi waseNingizimu Korea ekuqaleni wawungqubuzana ngendlela uMengameli uMun Jae-in asabela ngayo kule nkinga.
Abantu abaningi baseKorea basayine izicelo ezifuna ukuthi uMon asolwe ngalokho ababethi ukuphathwa kabi kwalesi sifo nguhulumeni, noma bedumisa impendulo yakhe. Lesi sifo siye savumela amazwe ukuba amise imithetho ephuthumayo.
Abanye abahlaziyi baye bazwakalisa ukukhathazeka ngokuthi kungase kuvumele ohulumeni ukuba baqinise ukubamba kwabo amandla.
EHungary, iphalamende lalo lavuma ukuvumela uNdunankulu, uViktor Orbán, ukuba abuse ngesinqumo ngokungapheli, amise iphalamende kanye nokhetho futhi ajezise labo ababhekwa njengabasakaze ulwazi olungelona iqiniso mayelana naleli gciwane nendlela uhulumeni aphatha ngayo le nkinga.
Ukuqubuka kwe-coronavirus kuye kwabekwa icala ngezimo eziningana zokushoda kwezinto, okubangelwa ukusetshenziswa okwandayo kwemishini emhlabeni wonke ukulwa nokuqubuka, ukuthenga ngokweqile, nokuphazamiseka kokusebenza kwefektri kanye nokuthuthwa kwezinto.
I-United States Food and Drug Administration ikhiphe izixwayiso mayelana nokushoda kwezidakamizwa nemishini yezokwelapha ngenxa yokwanda kwesidingo sabathengi nokuphazamiseka kwabahlinzeki.
Izindawo eziningana nazo zabona ukuthenga okusheshayo okwaholela ekususweni kwamashalofu ezinto ezibalulekile zokudla njengokudla, iphepha langasese namanzi asebhodleleni, okwenza kube nokushoda kokuphakelwa.
Ikakhulukazi imboni yezobuchwepheshe iye yaxwayisa ngokubambezeleka kokuthumela izimpahla zobuchwepheshe.
NgokukaTedros Adhanom, umqondisi-jikelele we-WHO, isidingo semishini yokuzivikela sesikhuphuke ngokuphindwe kayikhulu.
Lokhu kubiza kuye kwaholela ekwandeni kwamanani aphindwe izikhathi ezingu-20 kunamanani ajwayelekile futhi kwabangela nokulibaziseka kokunikezwa kwezinto zezokwelapha ngezinyanga ezine kuya kweziyisithupha.
Kuye kwabangela nokushoda kwemishini yokuzivikela emhlabeni wonke, kuyilapho i-WHO ixwayisa ngokuthi lokhu kuyoba yingozi kubasebenzi bezempilo.
E-Australia, ubhadane lunikeze ithuba elisha labathengi be-daigou lokuthengisa imikhiqizo yase-Australia eChina.
Lo msebenzi udale ukuntuleka kokudla okudayiswayo kwezingane kwezinye izitolo ezinkulu futhi kamuva kwavinjelwa uhulumeni wase-Australia. Naphezu kokwanda okuphezulu kwamacala e-COVID-19 eNyakatho ye-Italy naseWuhan, kanye nesidingo esikhulu semikhiqizo yokudla, zombili lezi zindawo ziye zasindiswa ekushoda okukhulu kokudla.
Izinyathelo ezathathwa yiChina ne-Italy zokulwa nokuqongelela kanye nokuhweba ngokungemthetho ngemikhiqizo ebalulekile ziye zaphumelela, zagwema ukushoda okukhulu kokudla okwakulindeleke eYurophu naseNyakatho Melika.
INyakatho ye-Italy, enomkhiqizo wayo omkhulu wezolimo, ayizange ibone ukwehla okukhulu, kodwa amanani angase akhuphuke ngokusho kwabameleli bezimboni.
Amashalofu okudla angenalutho ayeba khona okwesikhashana, ngisho nasedolobheni laseWuhan, kuyilapho izikhulu zikahulumeni waseChina zikhulula izinsalela zenyama yengulube ukuze ziqinisekise ukuthi abantu banokudla okwanele.
Imithetho efanayo ikhona eItaly edinga abakhiqizi bokudla ukuba bagcine izinqolobane ezimweni eziphuthumayo ezinjalo.
Umonakalo emnothweni womhlaba wonke uzwakale eChina: ngokombiko wezindaba wangoMashi 16, umnotho waseChina washaywa kanzima ezinyangeni ezimbili zokuqala zika-2020 ngenxa yezinyathelo ezathathwa uhulumeni zokunciphisa ukusabalala kwegciwane, futhi ukuthengiswa okuthengiswayo kwehla ngo-20.5%.
Njengoba iChina eyinhloko ingumnotho omkhulu kanye nesikhungo sokukhiqiza, ukuqubuka kwegciwane kuye kwabonakala njengosongo olukhulu lokudideka komnotho womhlaba.
U-Agathe Demarais we-Economist Intelligence Unit ubikezele ukuthi izimakethe ziyohlala ziguquguquka kuze kube yilapho sekubonakala isithombe esicacile ngemiphumela engaba khona.
NgoJanuwari 2020, abanye abahlaziyi balinganisela ukuthi umthelela wezomnotho walolu bhubhane ekukhuleni komhlaba wonke ungadlula lowo wokuqubuka kwe-SARS ngo-20022004.
Esinye isazi saseWashington University eSt. Louis sathola ukuthi umthelela wokuthengwa kwezinto emhlabeni wonke ungase ube ngaphezu kwezigidi eziyizinkulungwane ezingu-300 zamaRandi, futhi lokho kungathatha iminyaka emibili.
