Ukuhlolwa kwamasosha omzimba kubonisa ukuthi bangaki abantu abaye baba nalesi sifo, kuhlanganise nalabo abanezimpawu ezincane kakhulu ukuba zingabikwa noma abangenazo izimpawu.
