Ukugeza izandla (noma ukugeza izandla), okwaziwa nangokuthi inhlanzeko yezandla, kuwukuhlanza izandla zomuntu ngenjongo yokususa ukungcola, amafutha, amagciwane noma ezinye izinto ezingafuneki.
"Ukugeza izandla ngensipho njalo ngezikhathi ezithile "ezibucayi" phakathi nosuku kuvimbela ukusabalala kwezifo eziningi, isibonelo isifo sohudo nekholera, ezidluliselwa ngomlomo".
Abantu bangangenwa nezifo zokuphefumula ezifana nomkhuhlane noma umkhuhlane ovamile, ngokwesibonelo, uma bengazihlanzi izandla ngaphambi kokuthinta amehlo, ikhala noma umlomo (okungukuthi, izindlala zomlomo).
Izikhathi ezinhlanu ezibalulekile phakathi nosuku lapho ukugeza izandla ngensipho kubalulekile zihlanganisa: ngaphambi nangemva kokukhulelwa, ngemva kokuhlanza umlenze wengane noma ukushintsha amapayipi, ngaphambi kokudla ingane, ngaphambi kokudla nangaphambi nangemva kokulungiselela ukudla noma ukuphatha inyama eluhlaza, inhlanzi noma izinkukhu.
Uma amanzi nensipho kungatholakali, izandla zingahlanzwa ngomlotha. Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba incoma ukugeza izandla:
Ngaphambi kokupheka, phakathi nalapho upheka, nangemva kokudla.
Ngaphambi nangemva kokunakekela umuntu ogulayo.
Ngemva kokushintsha amapayipi noma ukuhlanza ingane eseye yangena endlini yangasese.
Ngemva kokuphefumula ikhala, ukukhwehlela noma ukuthimula.
Ngemva kokuthinta isilwane, ukudla kwaso noma indle yaso.
Ukuhlanzeka kwezandla kwezokwelapha kubhekisela emikhubeni yokuhlanzeka ehlobene nezinqubo zezokwelapha.
Ukugeza izandla ngaphambi kokunikeza imithi noma ukunakekelwa kwezokwelapha kungavimbela noma kunciphise ukusabalala kwezifo.
Injongo eyinhloko yokugeza izandla ukuhlanza izandla ezonakalisweni (amabhaktheriya, amagciwane, noma ezinye izinto ezincane ezingadala izifo) namakhemikhali angadala ukulimala noma izifo.
Lokhu kubaluleke kakhulu kubantu abaphatha ukudla noma abasebenza emkhakheni wezokwelapha, kodwa futhi kuwumkhuba obalulekile emphakathini jikelele.
Ukugeza izandla kunezinzuzo eziningi zezempilo, kuhlanganise nokunciphisa ukusabalala komkhuhlane, i-coronavirus nezinye izifo ezithathelwanayo; ukuvimbela izimbangela ezithathelwanayo zohudo; ukunciphisa izifo zokuphefumula;
kanye nokunciphisa izinga lokufa kwezingane lapho zizalwa ekhaya.
Ucwaningo lwango-2013 lwabonisa ukuthi ukuthuthukisa imikhuba yokugeza izandla kungaholela ekuthuthukiseni kancane ekukhuleni kobude ezinganeni ezingaphansi kweminyaka emihlanu.
Emazweni asathuthuka, izinga lokufa kwezingane ezibulawa izifo zokuphefumula nezokushaya unhlangothi lingancishiswa ngokwenza izinguquko ezilula ekuziphatheni, njengokugeza izandla ngensipho.
Lesi senzo esilula singanciphisa izinga lokufa ngenxa yalezi zifo cishe ngo - 50%.
Ukungenelela okukhuthaza ukugeza izandla kunganciphisa izenzakalo zohudo cishe ngengxenye yesithathu, futhi lokhu kungafaniswa nokuhlinzeka ngamanzi ahlanzekile ezindaweni ezinezindleko eziphansi.
Ukwehla okungu-48% kwezifo zohudo kungabangelwa ukugeza izandla ngensipho. Ukugeza izandla ngensipho kuyindlela eyodwa esebenza kahle futhi engabizi kakhulu yokuvimbela uhudo nezifo ezihlasela indlela yokuphefumula (ARI), njengoba lokhu kwenziwa ngokuzenzakalela emakhaya, ezikoleni nasemphakathini emhlabeni wonke.
Isifo samaphaphu, esiyinhloko se-ARI, siyimbangela yokuqala yokufa kwezingane ezingaphansi kweminyaka emihlanu, esibulala izingane ezilinganiselwa ezigidini ezingu - 1,8 ngonyaka.
Isifo sohudo nesifo samaphaphu ndawonye sibangela ukufa kwezingane ezicishe zibe yizigidi ezingu - 3,5 unyaka ngamunye.
Ngokwe-UNICEF, ukugeza izandla ngensipho ngaphambi kokudla nangemva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese kungasindisa ukuphila kwabantu abaningi kunanoma imuphi umuthi wokugoma noma umuthi, kunciphise ukufa kwabantu ngenxa yesifo sohudo cishe ngesigamu nokufa kwabantu ngenxa yezifo ezihlasela amaphaphu okuphefumula ngengxenye eyodwa kwezine.
Ukugeza izandla ngokuvamile kuhlanganiswa nezinye izindlela zokuhlanzeka njengengxenye yezinhlelo zamanzi, ezempilo kanye nokuhlanzeka (WASH).
Ukugeza izandla nakho kuvikela i-impetigo edluliselwa ngokuxhumana nomzimba ngokuqondile.
Umphumela omncane omubi wokugeza izandla ukuthi ukugeza izandla kaningi kungabangela ukulimala kwesikhumba ngenxa yokoma kwesikhumba.
Ucwaningo olwenziwa eDenmark ngo-2012 lwathola ukuthi ukugeza izandla ngokweqile kungabangela isikhumba esivuvukalayo nesinama-flakes esibizwa ngokuthi i-hand eczema noma i-hand dermatitis, evame kakhulu kubasebenzi bezempilo.
Ukugeza izandla njalo kakhulu kubhekwa njengenye yezimpawu zesifo sokuphazamiseka ngokomzwelo (OCD).
Kunezikhathi ezinhlanu ezibalulekile emini lapho ukugeza izandla ngensipho kubalulekile ukuze kuncishiswe ukudluliselwa kwezifo ngomlomo: ngemva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese (ukugxusha, ukuchama), ngemva kokuhlanza umlenze wengane (ukuguqula amapayipi), ngaphambi kokudla ingane, ngaphambi kokudla nangaphambi/ngemva kokulungiselela ukudla noma ukuphatha inyama eluhlaza, inhlanzi noma izinkukhu.
Ezinye izikhathi lapho kufanele kwenziwe khona indlela efanele yokuwasha izandla ukuze kuvinjelwe ukudluliselwa kwezifo zihlanganisa ngaphambi nangemva kokwelapha isilonda noma isilonda; ngemva kokuthimula, ukukhwehlela, noma ukuphefumula ikhala; ngemva kokuthinta udoti wezilwane noma ukuphatha izilwane; nangemva kokuthinta udoti.
Emazweni amaningi, abantu abaningi abagezi izandla ngensipho.
Ucwaningo lokuhlanza izandla emazweni angu-54 ngo-2015 lwathola ukuthi ngokwesilinganiso, amakhaya angu-38.7% ayegeza izandla ngensipho. Ucwaningo lwango-2014 lwabonisa ukuthi iSaudi Arabia yayinezinga eliphakeme lama-97%; i-United States yayiseduze naphakathi nama-77%; neChina inenani eliphansi lama-23%. Manje sekukhona izindlela eziningana zokushintsha ukuziphatha ukuze kwandiswe ukubandakanyeka kokuziphatha kokugeza izandla ngensipho ngezikhathi ezibucayi. Ukugeza izandla kweqembu lezingane zesikole ngezikhathi ezithile zosuku kungenye yezindlela emazweni asathuthuka zokufaka ukugeza izandla ekuziphatheni kwezingane.
"Uhlelo "Lokunakekelwa Kwezempilo Okubalulekile" olusetshenziswa uMnyango Wezemfundo ePhilippines luyisibonelo sesenzo esilinganiselwe sokukhuthaza impilo nezemfundo yezingane".
Ukubulala izimpethu kabili ngonyaka, kanye nokuwasha izandla nsuku zonke ngensipho, ukuxubha amazinyo nsuku zonke nge-fluoride, kuyisici esiyinhloko salolu hlelo lukazwelonke.
