Isenzo esiyinhloko samanzi okugeza nezithako zokuhlanza ukunciphisa izithiyo ekuxazululeni, nokwandisa ukuncibilika.
Amanzi kuphela awasihlanzi kahle isikhumba ngoba amafutha namaprotheni, okuyizinto ezakha inhlabathi, awaqedwa kalula emanzini.
Nokho, ukuhlanza kusizwa ukugeleza kwamanzi okunengqondo..
Insipho eqinile, ngenxa yokuthi ingasetshenziswa kabusha, ingase ibe namagciwane atholakala ekusetshenzisweni kwayo ngaphambili.
Ucwaningo oluncane olubheke ukudluliselwa kwamagciwane ngensipho eqinile engcolisiwe lwaphetha ngokuthi ukudluliselwa akunakwenzeka njengoba amagciwane esuswa ngogwebu.
"I-CDC isasho ukuthi ""isawoti esishisayo enezilawuli ezingenazandla iyathandeka uma inikezwa".
Izinsipho ezilwa namagciwane ziye zakhuthazwa kakhulu emphakathini onendaba nempilo.
Kuze kube manje, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi ukusebenzisa ama-antiseptic noma izibulala-magciwane ezinconywayo kuyazikhethela izinto eziphila emvelweni ezingamelana nemithi elwa namagciwane.
Nokho, insipho elwa namagciwane iqukethe izidakamizwa ezivamile ezifana ne-triclosan, enohlu oluningi lwezinhlobo zezinto eziphilayo eziphikisayo.
Ngakho, ngisho noma izinhlobo eziphikisa imithi elwa namagciwane zingakhethwa ngensipho elwa namagciwane, zingase zingabi nethonya njengoba zikhangiswa.
Ngaphandle kwe-surfactant kanye ne-agent yokuvikela isikhumba, amafomula athuthukile angase aqukethe ama-asidi (i-acetic acid, i-ascorbic acid, i-lactic acid) njengombonisi we-pH, i-benzoic acid esebenzayo ngokumelene namagciwane kanye nezinye izinto ezenza isikhumba sibe ngcono (i-aloe vera, amavithamini, i-menthol, izithako zezitshalo).Ukuhlaziywa okuphelele okuvela e-University of Oregon School of Public Health kwabonisa ukuthi insipho ejwayelekile iyasebenza njengensipho yokulwa namagciwane esezingeni labathengi equkethe i-triclosan ekuvimbeleni izifo nasekususeni amagciwane ezandleni.
Amanzi ashisayo alungele ukugeza izandla awashisi ngokwanele ukuba abulale amagciwane.
Amabhaktheriya akhula ngokushesha okukhulu ekushiseni komzimba (37 °C).
Nokho, amanzi afudumele anensipho asebenza kangcono kunamanzi abandayo anensipho ekususeni amafutha emvelo agcina inhlabathi namagciwane.
Nokho, ngokuphambene nenkolelo evamile, ucwaningo lwesayensi luye lwabonisa ukuthi ukusebenzisa amanzi afudumele akunamthelela ekunciphiseni umthwalo wamagciwane ezandleni.
Isibulala-magciwane sezandla noma i-antiseptic yezandla iyinhlangano yokuhlanzeka yezandla engenawo amanzi.
Ngasekupheleni kwawo-1990 nasekuqaleni kwekhulu lama-21, izidakamizwa zokuhlanzeka ezingasekelwe emanzini ezenziwe ngotshwala (ezaziwa nangokuthi ama-alcohol-based hand rubs, ama-antiseptic hand rubs, noma ama-hand sanitizers) zaqala ukuthandwa.
Iningi lawo lisekelwe ku-isopropyl alcohol noma i-ethanol eyenziwe ndawonye ne-agent eqinisayo efana neCarbomer (i-polymer ye-acrylic acid) ibe ijeli, noma i-humicctant efana ne-glycerin ibe uketshezi, noma i-foam ukuze kube lula ukuyisebenzisa futhi inciphise umphumela wokomisa utshwala.
Ukungeza i-hydrogen peroxide ehlungiwe kwandisa umsebenzi we-antimicrobial. Izingxobo zokuhlanza izandla eziqukethe okungenani u-60 kuya ku-95% wotshwala zibulala amagciwane ngendlela ephumelelayo.
Izithambisi ezihlanza umzimba eziphuzwayo zibulala amagciwane, amagciwane amelana nemithi eminingi (i-MRSA ne-VRE), isifo sofuba, namanye amagciwane (kuhlanganise i-HIV, i-herpes, i-RSV, i-rhinovirus, i-vaccinia, umkhuhlane, ne-hepatitis) namakhowe.
Ama-alcohol rub sanitizer aqukethe u-70% wotshwala abulala ama-99.97% (ukunciphisa ama-log angu-3.5, okufana nokunciphisa ama-decibel angu-35) ama-bacterium ezandleni imizuzwana engu-30 ngemva kokuwasebenzisa kanye nama-99.99% kuya kuma-99.999% (ukunciphisa ama-log angu-4 kuya kwangu-5) ama-bacterium ezandleni umzuzu owodwa ngemva kokuwasebenzisa. Ama-hand sanitizer asebenza kakhulu ngokumelene nama-bacterium futhi awasebenzi kangako ngokumelene namagciwane athile.
Izithambisi-magciwane ezenziwe ngotshwala azisebenzi ngokuphelele ngokumelene namagciwane anjengegciwane le-norovirus (noma i-Norwalk), okuyisona sizathu esivame kakhulu sokutheleleka kwe-gastroenteritis. Isithambisi-magciwane esanele sezandla noma i-alcohol rub kumele isetshenziselwe ukugeza noma ukumboza izandla zombili.
Ingxenye engaphambili nengemuva yezandla zombili naphakathi nokuphela kweminwe yonke iyagcotshwa imizuzwana engaba ngu-30 kuze kube yilapho uketshezi, inhlabathi noma ijeli yomile.
Iziqongo zeminwe nazo kufanele zihlanzwe kahle, zigezwe ezandleni zombili. Isikhungo Sase-US Sokulawulwa Nokuvikelwa Kwezifo sincoma ukugeza izandla phezu kwezinto zokuhlanza izandla, ikakhulukazi uma izandla zingcolile.
Ukusetshenziswa okwandayo kwalezi zinsiza kusekelwe ekusebenzeni kwazo kalula nasekusebenzeni kwazo okusheshayo ekubulaleni amagciwane; kodwa-ke, akufanele kube esikhundleni sokuwasha izandla ngendlela efanele ngaphandle uma insipho namanzi kungatholakali.
Ukusetshenziswa kaningi kwezithambisi-zandla ezenziwe ngotshwala kungabangela isikhumba esomile ngaphandle uma kufakwa izithambisi-zandla kanye/noma izithambisi-zandla ezomisa isikhumba.
Umphumela wokomisa wotshwala ungancishiswa noma uqedwe ngokungeza i-glycerin kanye/noma ezinye izinto ezithambisa umzimba kwifomula.
Ekuhlolweni kwemitholampilo, izihlanzi zezandla ezenziwe ngotshwala eziqukethe izinto ezithambisa isikhumba zabangela ukucasuka nokoma kwesikhumba okuncane kakhulu kunesepha noma izinto zokuhlanza ezilwa namagciwane.
I-allergic contact dermatitis, i- contact urticaria syndrome noma ukuzwela ngokweqile kotshwala noma izithasiselo ezitholakala ekuxubeni izandla ngotshwala kuyaqabukela.
Ukuthambekela okuncane kokubangela i-irritant contact dermatitis kwaba into ekhangayo uma kuqhathaniswa nokuwasha izandla ngensipho namanzi.
Naphezu kokusebenza kahle kwazo, izidakamizwa ezingenawo amanzi azizihlanzi izandla ezingenawo ama-organic, kodwa zimane nje zizibulale amagciwane.
Yingakho izibulala-magciwane ezandleni zingasebenzi kahle njengensipho namanzi ekuvimbeleni ukusabalala kwamagciwane amaningi, ngoba amagciwane asahlala ezandleni.
Ukusebenza kahle kwezihlanza izandla ezingenaluthango kuxhomeke kakhulu ezintweni ezisetshenziswayo nasekwakhiweni kwazo, futhi ngokomlando, ukusetshenziswa kwazo kusuke kungaphansi kakhulu kokuphuza utshwala nokugcoba utshwala.
Muva nje, kuye kwaboniswa ukuthi ama-formulations asebenzisa i-benzalkonium chloride anesimo sokulwa namagciwane esihlala njalo nesinqwabelana ngemva kokuwasebenzisa, ngokungafani notshwala, obonakele ukuthi buyancipha ekusebenzeni ngemva kokusetshenziswa ngokuphindaphindiwe, cishe ngenxa yokuthuthuka kwemiphumela emibi yesikhumba.
Abantu abaningi emphakathini onemali encane abakwazi ukuthenga insipho futhi basebenzisa umlotha noma inhlabathi esikhundleni salokho.
Umlotha noma inhlabathi kungase kusebenze kangcono kunamanzi kuphela, kodwa kungase kungasebenzi kangako kunensipho.
Okunye okukhathazayo ukuthi uma inhlabathi noma umlotha ungcoliswe amagciwane kungase kwenze ukwanda kwezifo kube kukhulu kunokuba kuncishiswe.
Njengensipho, umlotha nawo uyisibulala-magciwane ngoba uma uthintana namanzi, udala uketshezi olune-alkaline.
I-WHO yancoma umlotha noma isihlabathi esikhundleni sesepha lapho isobho lingekho.
Indlela efanele yokuwasha izandla enconywa yi-US Centers for Disease Control yokuvimbela ukudluliselwa kwezifo ihlanganisa lezi zinyathelo ezilandelayo:
Gcoba izandla ngamanzi afudumele noma abandayo.
Kunconywa amanzi agelezayo ngoba amabheseni amile angase angcoliswe, kuyilapho izinga lokushisa lamanzi lingabonakali libalulekile.
Hlanza izandla ngokuzihlikihla ngensipho eningi, kuhlanganise nezingalo, phakathi kweminwe nangaphansi kwezipikili.
Insipho isusa amagciwane esikhumbeni, futhi ucwaningo lubonisa ukuthi abantu bavame ukugeza izandla zabo kahle uma besebenzisa insipho kunamanzi kuphela.
Hlikihla okungenani imizuzwana engu-20.
Ukuxubha kudala ukuchoboza, okusiza ekususeni amagciwane esikhumbeni, futhi ukuxubha isikhathi eside kususa amagciwane amaningi.
Geza kahle ngaphansi kwamanzi agobhozayo.
Ukugeza izandla ngamanzi kungenza izandla ziphinde zingcoliswe.
Yomisa ngethoyizi elihlanzekile noma uvumele umoya womise.
Izandla ezimanzi nezimanzi ziphinde zingcoliswe kalula. Izindawo ezivame kakhulu ezingabonwa yizithupha, izihlakala, izindawo eziphakathi kweminwe nangaphansi kwezipikili.
Izikhonkwane ezenziwe ngomshini ne-nail polish ehlatshwe yizicucu kungase kube nezilokazane ezincane.
Ngokuvamile kunconywa uketshezi lokuthambisa ukuze izandla zingabi mnyama; isikhumba esomile singabangela ukulimala kwesikhumba okungandisa ingozi yokudluliselwa kwesifo.
"Kungaba nezindlela ezihlukahlukene ezingabizi kakhulu zokwenza kube lula ukugeza izandla lapho amanzi ompompi kanye/noma insipho engekho khona, isibonelo, ukuchela amanzi esitsheni noma embotsheni enama-jerrycan alengayo anezimbobo ezifanele kanye/noma ukusebenzisa umlotha uma kudingeka emazweni asathuthuka. Ezimweni lapho amanzi enqunyelwe (njengezikole noma izindawo zasemakhaya emazweni asathuthuka), kunezisombululo zokonga amanzi, njenge-"tippy-tap" nezinye izindlela ezingabizi kakhulu".
I-tip-tap iyinqubo elula yokusebenzisa imbiza esekelwe entanjeni, nesiphenduli esisebenza ngezinyawo ukuze kuthelwe amanzi amancane ezandleni kanye nesibawo.
Ukomiswa kwezandla ngendlela efanele kuyingxenye ebalulekile yenqubo yokuhlanzeka kwezandla, kodwa kunempikiswano ethile mayelana nendlela ephumelela kunazo zonke yokomisa ezindlini zangasese zomphakathi.
Ucwaningo olukhulayo lubonisa ukuthi amathawula ephepha ahlanzeka kangcono kakhulu kunamathuluzi omisa izandla kagesi atholakala emakamelweni amaningi okugeza.
Ngo-2008, kwenziwa ucwaningo e-University of Westminster, eLondon, futhi olwalusekelwa imboni yamathuluzi okugeza ephepha i-European Tissue Symposium, ukuze kuqhathaniswe amazinga okuhlanzeka anikezwa amathuluzi okugeza ephepha, omiswe izandla ngomoya ofudumele kanye namathuluzi omiswe izandla ngomoya we-jet anamuhla.
Ngemva kokuwasha nokomisa izandla ngomswakama womoya ofudumele, kwatholakala ukuthi inani eliphelele lamagciwane landa ngokwesilinganiso ngama-194% ezandleni nangama-254%.
Ukomisa ngomshini wokomisa umoya kwaholela ekwandeni kwesilinganiso senani lamabhaktheriya aphelele ezandleni ngamaphesenti angu-42 nasezandleni ngamaphesenti angu-15.
Ngemva kokuwasha nokomisa izandla ngethulusi lephepha, inani eliphelele lamagciwane lancipha ngokwesilinganiso lafinyelela kuma-76% ezandleni nasezinqeni kuze kufike kuma-77%. Ososayensi baphinde benza izivivinyo zokuthola ukuthi ngabe kwakukhona yini amathuba okuthi abanye abasebenzisa indlu yangasese kanye nendawo yangasese ibe nokungcola ngenxa yohlobo ngalunye lwendlela yokomisa.
Umshini wokomisa umoya, ophefumulela umoya ngaphandle kweyunithi ngesivinini esashiwo esingu-180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), wakwazi ukuphefumulela amagciwane ezandleni nasendlini futhi kungenzeka angcolise abanye abasebenzisi bendlu yangasese kanye nendawo yangasese engamamitha amabili kude.
Ukusebenzisa umshini wokomisa izandla onomoya ofudumele kusakaza amagciwane angamamitha angu-0,25 ukusuka kumshini wokomisa izandla.
Amathoyizi ephepha awazange abonise ukusabalala okuphawulekayo kwamagciwane. Ngo-2005, ocwaningweni olwenziwa yi-TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, kwahlolwa izindlela ezihlukahlukene zokomisa izandla.
Kwabonwa izinguquko ezilandelayo ekubaleni kwamagciwane ngemva kokomisa izandla:
Kunabakhiqizi abaningi abahlukahlukene bezomisi bezandla, futhi izomisi zezandla ziye zaqhathaniswa nokomiswa ngamathawula ephepha.
Ukugeza izandla usebenzisa amathawula okuhlanza izandla kuyindlela yokuzivikela lapho uhamba uma kungekho insipho namanzi.
Isibulala-magciwane sezandla esenziwe ngotshwala kufanele sibe okungenani no-60% wotshwala.
Ukugeza izandla kwezokwelapha kwaba okuyimpoqo ngemva kwesikhathi eside udokotela waseHungary u-Ignaz Semmelweis ethole ukuthi kuyasebenza (ngo-1846) ekuvimbeleni izifo esibhedlela.
Kunamadivayisi kagesi anikeza impendulo ukuze akhumbuze abasebenzi basesibhedlela ukuthi bageze izandla uma bekhohlwa.
Olunye ucwaningo luthole ukuthi ukusetshenziswa kwazo kunciphisa izinga lokutheleleka.
Ukugeza izandla ngokwezokwelapha kufanele kube imizuzwana engu-15 okungenani, kusetshenziswa inqwaba yensipho namanzi noma ijeli ukuze kugcotshwe futhi kugcotshwe ingxenye ngayinye yezandla.
Izandla kufanele zigoqwe ndawonye nezinzwani zixhumane.
Uma kunemfucumfucu ngaphansi kwezipikili, ingasuswa ngebhulashi.
Njengoba amagciwane engase ahlale emanzini ezandleni, kubalulekile ukuwahlanza kahle futhi uwasule ngetawuli elihlanzekile.
Ngemva kokomisa, ithawula lephepha kufanele lisetshenziselwe ukuvala amanzi (futhi uma kudingeka, uvule noma imuphi umnyango wokuphuma).
Lokhu kugwema ukungcoliswa kabusha kwezandla ezivela kulezo zingxenye.
"Injongo yokugeza izandla endaweni yokunakekela impilo ukususa amagciwane abangela izifo ("amagciwane") nokugwema ukudlulisela amagciwane".
I-New England Journal of Medicine ibika ukuthi ukuntuleka kokugeza izandla kuseyizinga elingenakwamukeleka ezindaweni eziningi zezokwelapha, njengoba odokotela abaningi nabahlengikazi ngokuvamile bekhohlwa ukugeza izandla ngaphambi kokuthinta iziguli, ngaleyo ndlela bedlulisela amagciwane.
Olunye ucwaningo lwabonisa ukuthi ukugeza izandla ngendlela efanele nezinye izindlela ezilula kunganciphisa izinga lokutheleleka kwegazi okubangelwa ama-catheter ngamaphesenti angu-66. Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba iye yanyathelisa ishidi elibonisa indlela evamile yokuwasha izandla nokuxubha izandla emkhakheni wezokunakekelwa kwezempilo.
Umklamo wokuqondisa wezandla wenhlangano ungabuye utholakale kuwebhusayithi yayo ukuze abantu baphawule.
Ukubuyekezwa okuhlobene nalokhu kwenziwa uWhitby et al.
Amadivayisi okuhweba angalinganisa futhi aqinisekise inhlanzeko yezandla, uma kudingeka kuboniswe ukuhambisana nemithetho.
"Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba inezikhathi "eziyisihlanu" zokuwasha izandla:"
ngemva kokuthinta igazi/uketshezi lomzimba
ngaphambi komsebenzi wokungasebenzi kahle, futhi
"ngemva kokunakekelwa kwesiguli. Ukungezwa kwamakhemikhali okubulala amagciwane ensipho ("isinye" noma "isinye" insipho) kunikeza isenzo sokubulala kumuthi wokuwasha izandla".
Isenzo esinjalo sokubulala singase sifiswe ngaphambi kokwenza ukuhlinzwa noma ezindaweni lapho izilokazane eziphikisa imithi elwa namagciwane zandile khona. Ukuze 'uhlanze' izandla zakho ngaphambi kokuhlinzwa, kudingeka ube nompompi ongavula futhi ucime ngaphandle kokuthinta izandla, i-chlorhexidine noma iodine wash, amathawula angenabuthi ukuze womise izandla ngemva kokuwasha, nebhulashi elingenabuthi lokuxubha kanye nenye into engenabuthi yokuhlanza ngaphansi kwezipikili.
Zonke izinto zokuhloba kufanele zisuswe.
Le nqubo idinga ukugeza izandla nezingalo kuze kufike engalweni, ngokuvamile imizuzu engu-26.
Akudingekile ukuba usebenzise isikhathi eside (imizuzu eyi-10) ukuze usule.
Lapho ugeza, amanzi asezingalweni kufanele avinjelwe ukuba angabuyeli ezandleni.
Ngemva kokuqeda ukugeza izandla, izandla zomiswa ngendwangu engenamithi bese kugqokwa ingubo yokuhlinza.
Ukuze kuncishiswe ukusabalala kwamagciwane, kungcono ukugeza izandla noma ukusebenzisa umuthi wokubulala amagciwane ngaphambi nangemva kokunakekela umuntu ogulayo.
Ukuze kulawulwe izifo ze-staphylococcal ezibhedlela, kuye kwatholakala ukuthi inzuzo enkulu yokuhlanza izandla yayivela kuma-20% okuqala okugeza, futhi inzuzo encane kakhulu eyengeziwe yatholakala lapho imvamisa yokuhlanza izandla yanda ngaphezu kwama-35%.
Ukugeza ngensipho ejwayelekile kuholela ekwandeni kwezifo ezithathelwanayo ezithathelwanayo ezithathelwanayo ngokudla ngokuphindwe kathathu uma kuqhathaniswa nokuwasha ngensipho elwa namagciwane. Ukuqhathanisa ukugeza izandla ngensipho elwa namagciwane nesisombululo esisekelwe otshwaleni nokuwasha izandla ngensipho elwa namagciwane isikhathi esimaphakathi semizuzwana engu-30 ngamunye kwabonisa ukuthi ukugeza izandla ngensipho elwa namagciwane kunciphise ukungcola kwamagciwane ngama-26% ngaphezu kwensipho elwa namagciwane.
Kodwa insipho namanzi kusebenza kangcono kunokuxubha izandla ngotshwala ukuze kuncishiswe igciwane lomkhuhlane i-H1N1 A kanye ne-Clostridium difficile spores ezandleni. Ukungenelela ukuthuthukisa inhlanzeko yezandla ezindaweni zokunakekela ezempilo kungahlanganisa ukufundisa abasebenzi ngokuwasha izandla, ukwandisa ukutholakala kokuxubha izandla ngotshwala, kanye nezikhumbuzo ezibhaliwe nezomlomo kubasebenzi.
Kudingeka ucwaningo olwengeziwe lokuthi yikuphi kwalokhu kungenelela okusebenza kakhulu ezindaweni ezihlukahlukene zokunakekela impilo.
Emazweni asathuthuka, ukugeza izandla ngensipho kuyaziwa njengendlela engabizi, ebalulekile yokufinyelela impilo enhle, ngisho nokudla okunempilo.
Nokho, ukuntuleka kokunikezwa kwamanzi, insipho noma izindawo zokugeza izandla ezindlini zabantu, ezikoleni nasemsebenzini kwenza kube inselele ukufinyelela ekuziphatheni okuvamile kokugeza izandla.
Ngokwesibonelo, ezindaweni eziningi zasemakhaya e-Afrika, amaphampu okugeza izandla aseduze nawo wonke amathoyilethi angawomuntu siqu noma awomphakathi mancane, nakuba kunezinye izindlela ezingabizi zokwakha iziteshi zokuwasha izandla.
Nokho, amazinga aphansi okugeza izandla angase futhi abangelwe imikhuba egxilile kunokuba abangelwe ukuntuleka kwensipho noma amanzi.
Ukukhuthaza nokukhuthaza ukugeza izandla ngensipho kungathonya izinqumo zenqubomgomo, kukhulise ukuqwashisa ngezinzuzo zokuwasha izandla futhi kuholele ekushintsheni kokuziphatha kwabantu esikhathini eside.
Ukuze lokhu kusebenze ngempumelelo, ukuqapha nokuhlola kuyadingeka.
"Ukubuyekezwa okuhlelekile kwezifundo ezingu-70 kwatholakala ukuthi izindlela ezisekelwe emphakathini ziyasebenza ekwandiseni ukugeza izandla emazweni aseLMIC, kuyilapho imikhankaso yokumaketha kwezenhlalo ingasebenzi kahle kangako. Isibonelo sokukhuthaza ukugeza izandla ezikoleni "i-Three Star Approach" ye-UNICEF ekhuthaza izikole ukuba zithathe izinyathelo ezilula, ezingabizi ukuqinisekisa ukuthi abafundi bageza izandla zabo ngensipho, phakathi kwezinye izidingo zenhlanzeko".
Lapho kufinyelelwa ezindinganisweni ezincane, izikole zingashintsha zisuke kunkanyezi eyodwa ziye kokuthathu.
