Usuku Lokugeza Izandla Lomhlaba Wonke lungesinye isibonelo somkhankaso wokwazisa ozama ukufeza ushintsho ekuziphatheni. Ngenxa yobhadane lwe-coronavirus lwango-2019-20, i-UNICEF yathuthukisa ukusetshenziswa kwe-emoji yokugeza izandla.
