"Ibinzana elithi ""ukugeza izandla zakho"" kusho ukuthi awufuni ukuthatha umthwalo walokho okwenzekile noma ukuhlanganyela kukho".
Livela endimeni yeBhayibheli kuMathewu lapho uPontiyu Pilatu ageza khona izandla zakhe ngesinqumo sokubethela uJesu Kristu, kodwa selibe inkulumo esetshenziswa kabanzi kakhulu kweminye imiphakathi yesiNgisi.
Ku-Macbeth kaShakespeare, uLady Macbeth uqala ukugeza izandla zakhe ngenkani ezama ukuhlanza ibala elicatshangelwayo, elimelela unembeza wakhe onecala maqondana nobugebengu ayebenzile futhi wabangela umyeni wakhe ukuba enze.
Kuye kwaphinde kwatholakala ukuthi abantu, ngemva kokukhumbula noma ukucabanga ngezenzo ezingalungile, bavame ukugeza izandla kaningi kunabanye, futhi bavame ukwazisa kakhulu imishini yokuwasha izandla.
"Ngaphezu kwalokho, labo abavunyelwe ukugeza izandla zabo ngemva kokuzindla okunjalo mancane amathuba okuba bahlanganyele kwezinye izenzo zokuzihlanza, njengokuzithandela".
