Ukulawulwa kwezingozi ze-COVID-19 emsebenzini
Ukulawulwa kwezingozi emsebenzini ze-COVID-19 ukusetshenziswa kwezindlela zokuphepha nezempilo emsebenzini zokulawulwa kwezingozi zokuvimbela isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ukulawulwa kwezingozi okufanele emsebenzini kuncike endaweni yokusebenzela nomsebenzi, okusekelwe ekuhloleni izingozi zemithombo yokuchayeka, ubukhulu besifo emphakathini, kanye nezici zengozi zabasebenzi ngabanye abangase babe sengozini yokungenwa yi-COVID-19.
Ngokwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enobungozi obuncane bokubandakanyeka inokuxhumana okuncane nomphakathi nabanye osebenza nabo, lapho kunconywa khona izinyathelo eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka, ezihlanganisa ukugeza izandla, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya uma begula, isimiso sokuphefumula, nokugcina ukuhlanza nokubulala amagciwane okujwayelekile endaweni yokusebenza.
Imisebenzi enobungozi obuphakathi nendawo ihlanganisa leyo edinga ukuxhumana njalo noma eduze nabantu abangaziwa noma abasolwa nge-COVID-19, kodwa abangase batheleleke ngenxa yokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo noma ukuhamba kwamanye amazwe.
Lokhu kuhlanganisa abasebenzi abaxhumana nomphakathi jikelele njengasezikoleni, ezindaweni zokusebenza ezinabantu abaningi, nakwezinye izindawo zokuthengisa ezinkulu.
Ukulawula izingozi zaleli qembu, ngaphezu kwezinyathelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka okuyisisekelo, kuhlanganisa ukuphefumula usebenzisa izihlungi zomoya ezisebenza kahle, izivikeli zokuthimula, nokuba nemishini yokuzivikela uma kwenzeka umuntu one-COVID-19 etholakala.
I-OSHA ibheka abasebenzi bezempilo nabasebenza emathuneni abavezwe umuntu owaziwayo noma osolwayo nge-COVID-19 njengababhekene nengozi enkulu yokuchayeka, okwenyukela engozini enkulu kakhulu yokuchayeka uma abasebenzi benza izinqubo zokukhiqiza ama-aerosol, noma beqoqa noma baphathe amasampula avela kumuntu owaziwayo noma osolwayo nge-COVID-19.
Ukulawulwa kwezingozi okufanelekayo kulaba basebenzi kuhlanganisa ukulawulwa kwezobunjiniyela njengamakamelo okuphefumula anengcindezi engemihle, nemishini yokuzivikela efanele umsebenzi.
Ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 kungaba nemiphumela eminingi emsebenzini.
Izisebenzi zingase zingabi khona emsebenzini ngenxa yokugula, ngenxa yokunakekela abanye noma ngenxa yokwesaba ukuchayeka.
Izindlela zokuhweba zingashintsha, kokubili ngokuya ngokuthi yiziphi izimpahla ezifunwayo, nezindlela zokuthola lezi zimpahla (njengokuthenga ngaphandle kwamahora okuphakama noma ngezinsizakalo zokulethwa noma zokuhamba ngemoto).
Ekugcineni, ukuthunyelwa kwezinto ezivela ezindaweni ezihlaselwe kakhulu yi-COVID-19 kungaphazamiseka. Uhlelo lokulungela izifo ezithathelwanayo kanye nokusabela lungasetshenziswa ukuqondisa izenzo zokuzivikela.
Izinhlelo zibheka amazinga engozi ahlobene nezindawo ezihlukahlukene zokusebenza nemisebenzi yomsebenzi, kuhlanganise nemithombo yokuchayeka, izimbangela zengozi ezivela ekhaya nasemphakathini, kanye nezimbangela zengozi zabasebenzi ngabanye njengobudala noma izimo zempilo ezingapheli.
Zibeka futhi izindlela zokulawula ezidingekayo zokubhekana nalezo zingcuphe, namapulani okuphuthumayo ezimo ezingase ziphakame ngenxa yokuqubuka kwezifo.
Izinhlelo zokulungela izifo ezithathelwanayo nezokuphendula zingaba ngaphansi kwezincomo zikazwelonke noma ezingaphansi kukazwelonke.
Izinhloso zokubhekana nokuqubuka zifaka ukunciphisa ukudluliselwa phakathi kwabasebenzi, ukuvikela abantu abasengozini enkulu yezinkinga zempilo, ukugcina imisebenzi yebhizinisi, nokunciphisa imiphumela emibi kwezinye izinhlangano emaketangeni abo okuphakelayo.
Ubukhulu besifo emphakathini lapho ibhizinisi likhona buyakuthinta ukusabela okwenziwe.
I-hierarchy yokulawula izingozi iwuhlaka olusetshenziswa kabanzi ekuphepheni nasempilweni emsebenzini ukuze kuqoqwe ukulawula izingozi ngokusebenza kahle.
Lapho izingozi ze-COVID-19 zingeke zisuswe, izindlela eziphumelela kakhulu zokulawula ukulawulwa kwezobunjiniyela, ezilandelwa ukulawulwa kokuphatha, futhi ekugcineni, izinto zokuzivikela.
Ukulawulwa kobuchwepheshe kuhilela ukuhlukanisa abasebenzi ezingozini ezihlobene nomsebenzi ngaphandle kokuncika ekuziphatheni kwabasebenzi, futhi kungaba yisixazululo esonga kakhulu.
Ukulawulwa kokuphatha yizinguquko ezenzweni zomsebenzi noma izinqubo ezidinga isinyathelo esenziwa isisebenzi noma umqashi.
Imishini yokuzivikela (PPE) ibhekwa njengengaphumeleli kangako kunokuhlolwa kwezobunjiniyela nokulawula, kodwa ingasiza ekuvimbeleni ukuchayeka okuthile.
Zonke izinhlobo ze-PPE kufanele zikhethwe ngokususelwa engozini ezokwehlelwa isisebenzi, zifakwe kahle njengoba kufanele (isibonelo, iziphefumuleli), zigqokwe njalo futhi ngendlela efanele, zihlolwe njalo, zigcinwe futhi zishintshwe, njengoba kudingeka, futhi zisuswe, zihlanzwe, futhi zigcinwe noma zilahlwe ngendlela efanele ukuze kugwenywe ukungcola.
Ngokwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enengozi ephansi yokuchayeka inokuxhumana okuncane nomphakathi nabanye abasebenza nabo.
Izinyathelo eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka ezinconyelwe zonke izindawo zokusebenza zihlanganisa ukugeza izandla njalo nangokuphelele, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya uma begula, imithetho yokuphefumula kuhlanganise nokumboza ukukhwehlela nokuhogela, ukuhlinzeka ngezicubu nemigqomo kadoti, ukulungiselela ukusebenza kude noma ukushintshana ngezikhathi uma kudingeka, ukuvimbela abasebenzi ekusebenziseni amathuluzi nemishini yabanye, nokugcina ukuhlanza nokubulala amagciwane okujwayelekile endaweni yokusebenza.
Ukuhlonza ngokushesha nokuhlukanisa abantu abangase batheleleke kuyisinyathelo esibalulekile ekuvikeleni abasebenzi, amakhasimende, izivakashi nabanye endaweni yokusebenzela.
Izikhungo Zase-United States Zokulawulwa Nokuvikelwa Kwezifo (CDC) zincoma ukuthi abasebenzi abanezimpawu zesifo esibucayi sokuphefumula bahlale ekhaya kuze kube yilapho bengenawo umkhuhlane, izimpawu zomkhuhlane, nanoma yiziphi ezinye izimpawu okungenani amahora angu-24 ngaphandle kokusebenzisa imithi yokwehlisa umkhuhlane noma eminye imithi eguqula izimpawu, nokuthi izinqubomgomo zokungabikho emsebenzini ngenxa yokugula ziguquguquke, zivumele abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya ukuze banakekele ilungu lomndeni eligulayo, nokuthi abasebenzi bayazazi lezi zinqubomgomo.
Ngokusho kwe-OSHA, imisebenzi enobungozi obuphakathi nendawo ihlanganisa leyo edinga ukuxhumana njalo noma eduze nabantu abangekho noma abasolwa ngokuba neziguli ze-COVID-19, kodwa abangase batheleleke nge-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo endaweni yebhizinisi, noma ngoba umuntu usanda kuhamba emazweni omhlaba waya endaweni yokudluliselwa kwe-COVID-19.
Lezi zihlanganisa abasebenzi abaxhumana nomphakathi jikelele njengezikole, izindawo zokusebenza ezinabantu abaningi, kanye nezinye izindawo zokuthengisa ezinezindawo eziningi.Ukulawulwa kobunjiniyela kwalaba kanye namaqembu anezingozi eziphezulu kuhlanganisa ukufakwa kwezihlungi zomoya ezisebenza kahle kakhulu, ukwandisa amazinga okuphefumula, ukufakwa kwezithiyo zomzimba ezifana nezivikelo ezihlanzekile zokuthimula zepulasitiki, nokufakwa kwefasitela lokuhamba ukuze kusetshenziswe amakhasimende.Ukulawulwa kokuphatha kwalaba kanye namaqembu anezingozi eziphezulu kuhlanganisa ukukhuthaza abasebenzi abagulayo ukuba bahlale emakhaya, ukufaka izingxoxo ezibonakalayo esikhundleni semihlangano ebonakalayo, ukusungula ama-shift ahlukene, ukuyeka ukuhamba okungadingekile ezindaweni lapho kuqhubeka khona ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19, ukuthuthukisa izinhlelo eziphuthumayo ezihlanganisa isithangami sokuphendula izikhalo zabasebenzi, ukuhlinzeka ngemfundo nokuqeqeshwa okusha mayelana nezici eziyingozi ze-COVID-19 kanye namagilavu okuvikela, abasebenzi abadinga ukusebenzisa izingubo zokuzivikela nokuziphatha nokuthi bangazisebenzisa kanjani, ukuhlinzeka abasebenzi ngemishini yokuzivikela kanye nokuxhumana okubonakalayo, ukuthumela izibonisi noma ezinye izinyathelo ezivamile, okuhlanganisa ukugeza ubuso noma izandla, ukuthuthukisa ukufinyelela kwabasebenzi noma ukufinyelela emithonjeni zomphakathi komphakathi komphakathi, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi noma ezinye izinsiza zokukhoma mayelana ne-COVID-19, ukuvikela, ukuvikela ubuso noma izivikelo zomuntu siqu, ukuvikela abasebenzi kanye nezinye izinsizabasebenzi, ukuthuthukisa ukuvikela, ukuthuthukisa ukuvikelwa kwamakhasimende noma ukuvikela ubuso noma izivikelo zomphakathi komphakathi komphakathi komphakathi komphakathi, ukuthumela noma ezinye izisebenzi, ukuthumela izinsiza, ukuthuthukisa ukusetshenziswa noma ezinye izinsiza, ukuthuthukisa ukusetshenziswa noma ezinye izinsiza noma ezinye izinsiza, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi, ukuthuthukisa ukufin