Izisebenzi ezikuleli qembu eliyingozi azivamile ukusebenzisa izinto zokuphefumula.
Uma umuntu egula endizeni, izindlela ezifanele zokuvikela abasebenzi nabanye abagibeli zihlanganisa ukuhlukanisa umuntu ogulayo nabanye abantu ngebanga elingamamitha ayisithupha, ukukhetha ilungu elilodwa labasebenzi ukuba likhonze ogulayo, nokunikeza umuntu ogulayo imaski yobuso noma ukucela umuntu ogulayo ukuba amboze umlomo wakhe nekhala lakhe ngamaswidi lapho ekhwehlela noma ethimula.
Abasebenzi basendlini kufanele bagqoke amagilavu okudlala ngawo lapho benakekela isihambi esigulayo noma lapho bethinta uketshezi lomzimba noma izinto ezingase zingcoliswe, futhi mhlawumbe bagqoke izinto zokuzivikela ezengeziwe uma isihambi esigulayo sinomkhuhlane, ukukhwehlela okungapheli noma inkinga yokuphefumula.
Amagilavu nezinye izinto ezilahlwayo kufanele zilahlwe esikhwameni esivikela izingozi, futhi izindawo ezingcolile kufanele zihlanzwe futhi ziqedwe amagciwane ngemva kwalokho. Ezokuthutha ngomkhumbi, kuhlanganise nemikhumbi yokuhamba ngezindiza nezinye imikhumbi yabagibeli, izindlela zokulawula izingozi zihlanganisa ukuhlehlisa ukuhamba lapho ugula, nokuzihlukanisa nokuxwayisa isikhungo sezokwelapha esisemkhunjini ngokushesha uma umuntu eba nomkhuhlane noma ezinye izimpawu ngenkathi esemkhunjini.
Ngokufanelekile, ukulandelwa kwezokwelapha kufanele kwenzeke ekhabetheni lomuntu ohlukanisiwe. Ezikoleni nasezikhungweni zokunakekela izingane, i-CDC incoma ukuvalwa kwesikhashana ukuze kuhlanzwe noma kubulawe amagciwane uma umuntu onegciwane esebe sesakhiweni sesikole kungakhathalekile ukuthi isakazeka emphakathini.
Lapho kunokusakazeka komphakathi okuncane kuya kokulinganiselwe, amasu okuxhumana nabantu angasetshenziswa njengokukhansela uhambo, imihlangano, neminye imihlangano emikhulu efana nemfundo yomzimba noma amakilasi e-choir noma ukudla endaweni yokudlela, ukwandisa isikhala phakathi kwamatafula, isikhathi sokufika nokuxoshwa, ukunciphisa izivakashi ezingadingekile, nokusebenzisa indawo ehlukile yasehhovisi lezempilo yezingane ezinezimpawu ezifana nomkhuhlane.
Lapho kukhona ukudluliselwa okukhulu emphakathini wendawo, ngaphezu kwamasu okuxhumana nabantu, ukudilizwa kwesikole okuqhubekayo kungacatshangelwa. Kubasebenzi bezomthetho abenza imisebenzi yansuku zonke, ingozi yezempilo esheshayo ibhekwa njengephansi yi-CDC.
Izikhulu zomthetho okumelwe zithinte abantu abaqinisekisiwe noma abasolwa ngokuba ne-COVID-19 zinconywa ukuba zilandele imihlahlandlela efanayo neyezimo eziphuthumayo, kuhlanganise nezinto ezifanele zokuzivikela.
Uma kwenzeka ukuxhumana eduze ngesikhathi sokuboshwa, abasebenzi kufanele bahlanze futhi babulale amagciwane amabhande abo nemishini ngaphambi kokuyisebenzisa kabusha besebenzisa ispray yokuhlanza yasendlini noma isicwebezelisi, futhi balandele izinqubo zokusebenza ezijwayelekile zokuvalela nokulahla i-PPE esetshenzisiwe kanye nokufaka nokuwasha izingubo.
I-OSHA ibheka abasebenzi abathile bezempilo nabasebenza emathuneni njengababhekene nezinga eliphakeme noma eliphakeme kakhulu lokuchayeka.
Imisebenzi enobungozi obukhulu ihlanganisa ukuhlinzekwa kwezempilo, ukwesekwa, abasebenzi baselabhorethri, nabathutha ezokwelapha abavezwa iziguli ze-COVID-19 ezaziwayo noma ezisolwayo.
Lezi ziba nengozi enkulu kakhulu yokuchayeka uma abasebenzi benza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol, noma baqoqa noma baphathe amasampula eziguli ze-COVID-19 ezaziwayo noma ezisolwayo.
Izinqubo zokukhiqiza ama-aerosol zihlanganisa ukufakwa kwe-intuba, izinqubo zokukhwehlela, ama-bronchoscopy, ezinye izinqubo zokuhlolwa kwamazinyo noma ukuqoqwa kwesampula okuhlaselayo.
Imisebenzi yezidumbu enobungozi obukhulu ihlanganisa abasebenzi abahilelekile ekulungiseleleni izidumbu zabantu ababekwazi noma abasolwa ukuthi bane-COVID-19 ngesikhathi beshona; laba baba nengozi enkulu kakhulu yokuchayeka uma benza ukuhlolwa kwesidumbu. Ukulawulwa kobunjiniyela okwengeziwe kwala maqembu anobungozi kuhlanganisa amakamelo okuhlukanisa iziguli ezine-COVID-19 eyaziwayo noma okusolwa ukuthi zinawo, kuhlanganise nalapho kwenziwa izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol.
Ukuphefumula okucindezela umoya okungathandeki kungase kufaneleke kwezinye izindawo zokunakekela impilo nezingcwaba.
Amaphethini kufanele aphathwe ngezindlela zokuphepha ezingeni le-3 le-biosafety.
Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba (i-WHO) incoma ukuthi iziguli ezifikayo zihlukaniswe zibe yizindawo ezahlukene zokulinda kuye ngokuthi ngabe zinesimo sokusola ukuthi zine-COVID-19. Ngaphezu kwezinye izinto zokusiza abantu, i-OSHA incoma ukuthi kusetshenziswe amapayipi okuphefumula kulabo abasebenza ngaphakathi kwamamitha ayisithupha eziguli ezaziwayo ukuthi zinegciwane le-SARS-CoV-2, noma abasolwa ukuthi zinalo, nalabo abenza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol.
E-United States, iziphequluli zokuphefumula zobuso ze-N95 ezihlungiwe ze-NIOSH noma ezingcono kufanele zisetshenziswe kumongo wohlelo oluphelele, olubhaliwe lokuvikela ukuphefumula oluhlanganisa ukuhlolwa kokufaneleka, ukuqeqeshwa nokuhlolwa kwezokwelapha.
Ezinye izinhlobo zezinto zokuphefumula zinganikeza ukuvikeleka okukhulu futhi zithuthukise ukuphumula kwabasebenzi. I-WHO ayincomi ama-coversalls, njengoba i-COVID-19 iyisifo sokuphefumula kunokuba idluliselwe ngamanzi omzimba.
I-WHO incoma kuphela imaski yokuhlinza yabasebenzi abahlola indawo yokungena.
Kulabo abaqoqa amasampula okuphefumula ezigulini ze-COVID-19, abazinakekelayo noma abazithutha ngaphandle kwezinqubo zokukhiqiza ama-aerosol, i-WHO incoma imaski yokuhlinza, izibuko, noma izivikelo zobuso, ingubo namagilavu.
Uma kwenziwa inqubo yokwakhiwa kwe-aerosol, imaski yokuhlinza ithathelwa indawo i-N95 noma i-FFP2 respirator.
Njengoba ukunikezwa kwe-PPE emhlabeni wonke kunganele, i-WHO incoma ukunciphisa isidingo se-PPE ngokusebenzisa i-telemedicine, izithiyo zomzimba ezifana namafasitela ahlanzekile, ukuvumela kuphela labo abahilelekile ekunakekelweni ngqo ukuba bangene egumbini nesiguli se-COVID-19, ukusebenzisa kuphela i-PPE edingekayo emsebenzini othile, ukuqhubeka nokusebenzisa i-respirator efanayo ngaphandle kokuyisusa ngenkathi unakekela iziguli eziningi ezinokuxilongwa okufanayo, ukuqapha nokuxhumanisa uchungechunge lokunikezwa kwe-PPE, nokudambisa ukusetshenziswa kwamamaski kubantu abangenazimpawu.
