b' I-Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) iyi-enzyme enamathiselwe ebusweni bangaphandle (izingqimba zamangqamuzana) zamangqamuzana emaphashini, emithanjeni, enhliziyweni, ezinso nasemathunjini.
I-ACE2 ivimbela umsebenzi we-angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ehlobene ngokunciphisa inani le-angiotensin-II nokwandisa i-Ang ((1-7) okwenza kube umgomo omuhle wezidakamizwa zokwelapha izifo zenhliziyo. I-ACE2 iphinde isebenze njengendawo yokungena kumaseli kwamanye ama-coronavirus.
Uhlobo lomuntu lwale enzyme luvame ukubizwa ngokuthi i- hACE2.
I-angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 iyinhlanganisela ye-metalloenzyme equkethe i-zinc etholakala ebusweni bamangqamuzana endothelial namanye amangqamuzana.
I-ACE2 protein iqukethe i-N-terminal peptidase M2 domain ne-C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
I-ACE2 iyiprotheni ye-membrane yohlobo I edlula kanye, enendawo yayo esebenzayo ye-enzymatically evezwe ebusweni bamangqamuzana emaphashini nakwezinye izicubu.
I-ACE2 ihlukaniswa nenye i-enzyme ebizwa ngokuthi i-sheddase, bese i-protein encibilikayo ikhishwa egazini futhi ekugcineni ikhishwe emchameni.
I-ACE2 ikhona ezithweni eziningi: I-ACE2 inamathele esikhumbeni samangqamuzana ikakhulukazi amangqamuzana e-alveolar asezinhlungwini zohlobo II, ama-enterocyte emathunjini amancane, amangqamuzana e-arterial and venous endothelial kanye namangqamuzana omzimba we-arterial smooth muscle ezithweni eziningi.
Ukuvezwa kwe-mRNA ye-ACE2 kutholakala nasengqamuzaneni yengqondo, i-striatum, i-hypothalamus, kanye nesiqu somqondo.
Umsebenzi oyinhloko we-ACE2 ukwenza umsebenzi wokulinganisa i-ACE.
I-ACE ihlukanisa i-angiotensin I hormone ibe i-angiotensin II evimbela imithambo yegazi.
I-ACE2 yona ihlukanisa i-carboxyl-terminal amino acid i-phenylalanine ne-angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) futhi iyi-hydrolyzes ibe i-angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
I-ACE2 ingahlukanisa namanye ama-peptide amaningi kuhlanganise [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, ne- ghrelin.
I-ACE2 ibuye ilawulwe ukuhwebelana ngamagciwane kwe-neutral amino acid transporter SLC6A19 futhi iye yahlotshaniswa nesifo sikaHartnup.
Njengeprotheni ye-transmembrane, i-ACE2 iyindawo eyinhloko yokungena emangqamuzaneni amanye ama-coronavirus, kuhlanganise i-HCoV-NL63; i-SARS-CoV (igciwane elibangela i-SARS); ne-SARS-CoV-2 (igciwane elibangela i-COVID-19).
Ngokuqondile, ukubopha i-spike S1 protein ye-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV2 endaweni ye-enzymatic ye-ACE2 ebusweni bamaseli kuphumela ekufakeni i-endocytosis nasekuhambeni kokubili igciwane ne-enzyme kuma-endosomes atholakala ngaphakathi kwamaseli.
Le nqubo yokungena futhi idinga ukuqala kweprotheni ye-S yi-host serine protease TMPRSS2, ukuvimbela kwayo okuphenywa njengamanje njengendlela yokwelapha. Lokhu kuye kwaholela abanye ukuba bacabange ukuthi ukwehlisa amazinga e-ACE2, kumaseli, kungasiza ekulweni nokutheleleka.
Nokho, izinhlangano eziningi eziqeqeshiwe nezinhlangano ezilawulayo ziye zancoma ukuqhubeka nokwelashwa okujwayelekile kwe-ACE inhibitor ne-ARB.
"Ukubuyekezwa okuhlelekile nokuhlaziywa kwe-meta okushicilelwe ngoJulayi 11, 2012, kutholakale ukuthi ""ukusetshenziswa kwama-ACE inhibitors kuhlotshaniswa nokwehliswa okukhulu ngo-34% kwengozi yesifo samaphaphu uma kuqhathaniswa nokulawula. """
"Ngaphezu kwalokho, ""ingozi yokuvuvukala kwamaphaphu nayo yancipha ezigulini ezalashwa ngama-ACE inhibitors ezazinengozi enkulu yokuvuvukala kwamaphaphu, ikakhulukazi lezo ezazinesifo sohlangothi nokwehluleka kwenhliziyo".
"Ukusetshenziswa kwama-ACE inhibitors nakho kwahlotshaniswa nokwehla kokufa okuhlobene nesifo samaphaphu, nakuba imiphumela yayingaqinile njengengozi ephelele yesifo samaphaphu".
I-ACE2 yomuntu ehlanganisiwe (rhACE2) kucatshangwa ukuthi iyindlela yokwelapha entsha yokulimala kwamaphaphu okubucayi, futhi kubonakala sengathi ithuthukisa i-hemodynamics yamaphaphu nokugcwala komoya-mpilo ezingulubeni ezine-lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Isikhathi sokuphindeka kabili kwe-rhaCE2 kubantu singamahora angaba ngu-10 futhi isikhathi sokuqala kokusebenza singemizuzu engu-30 ngaphezu kwesikhathi sokusebenza (isikhathi) samahora angu-24.
Imiphumela eminingi ibonisa ukuthi i-rhace2 ingaba umuthi othembisayo kulabo abangakwazi ukubekezelela ama-renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (ama-RAS inhibitors) noma ezifweni lapho i-angiotensin II ejikelezayo iphakeme khona. I-rhace2 efakwe ngomlomo iye yahlolwa ezivivinyweni zomtholampilo zokwelapha i-acute respiratory distress syndrome.
