i-nucleic acid (i-DNA ne-RNA) (Umklami kanye nomuntu ozokwazi ukuthola umuthi wokugoma wesigaba I: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
umhambisi wegciwane (umqambi kanye nomfakisicelo womuthi wokugoma wesigaba I: CanSino Biologics, umhambisi wegciwane le-adenovirus uhlobo 5)
