Isu lesithathu elisetshenziswayo imithi yokugoma i-nucleic acid (i-DNA noma i-RNA, indlela entsha yokugoma).
Imigomo yokuhlola evela kunoma imaphi ala maqhinga bekufanele ihlolwe ukuphepha nokusebenza kahle. Ngo-16 Mashi 2020, kwaqala ukuhlolwa kokuqala komuthi wokugoma namavolontiya amane eSeattle.
Umuthi wokugoma uqukethe ikhodi yemvelo engenabungozi ekopishwe egciwaneni elibangela lesi sifo. Ukuthuthukiswa komzimba oncike kuma-antibody kuye kwaphakanyiswa njengenselele ekuthuthukisweni komuthi wokugoma i-SARS-COV-2, kodwa lokhu kuyimpikiswano.
Kusukela ngo-April 2020, sekunezilingo zomtholampilo ezingaphezu kuka-300 eziqhubekayo.
Izivivinyo eziyisikhombisa zazihlola izindlela zokwelapha isifo sikamalaleveva esezivunyelwe kakade, kuhlanganise nezifundo ezine ezihilela i-hydroxychloroquine noma i-chloroquine.
Imithi elwa namagciwane esetshenziswe kabusha yakha ingxenye enkulu yocwaningo lwaseChina, kanti izivivinyo eziyisishiyagalolunye zesigaba III ze-remdesivir emazweni amaningana zizobikwa ekupheleni kuka-Ephreli.
Ukubuyekezwa okunamandla kokuthuthukiswa kwemitholampilo kwemithi yokugoma i-COVID-19 kanye nezidakamizwa kwakukhona, kusukela ngo-Ephreli 2020. Imithi eminingi esebenzayo yokulwa negciwane iyahlolwa ukwelashwa kwe-COVID-19, kufaka phakathi i-remdesivir, i-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine, i-lopinavir/ritonavir ne-lopinavir/ritonavir ehlanganiswe ne-interferon beta.
Kunobufakazi obungatheni bokusebenza kwe-remdesivir, kusukela ngoMashi 2020.
Kwabonwa ukuthuthuka kwemitholampilo ezigulini ezathola i-remdesivir yokusetshenziswa ngokuzwelana.
Ukuhlolwa kwesigaba III kwenziwa e-US, China nase-Italy. I-Chloroquine, eyayisetshenziswa ngaphambili ekwelapheni umalaleveva, yahlolwa eChina ngoFebhuwari 2020, ngemiphumela yokuqala.
Nokho, kunezingcingo zokubuyekezwa kocwaningo.
Iziphathimandla Zezempilo zaseKorea nezaseChina zincoma ukusetshenziswa kwe-chloroquine.
Nokho, i-Wuhan Institute of Virology, nakuba incoma umthamo wansuku zonke ongegremu elilodwa, iphawula ukuthi umthamo ophindwe kabili uyingozi kakhulu futhi ungabulala.
Ngo-March 28, 2020, i-FDA yakhipha imvume yokusetshenziswa okuphuthumayo kwe-hydroxychloroquine ne-chloroquine ngokubona kodokotela abaphatha abantu abane-COVID-19. Imihlahlandlela yesi-7 yesiShayina ifaka phakathi i-interferon, i-ribavirin noma i-umifenovir yokusetshenziswa ngokumelene ne-COVID-19.
Idatha yokuqala ibonisa ukuthi kudingeka imithamo ephezulu ye-ribavirin ukuze kuvinjelwe i-SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
INitazoxanide iye yanconywa ukuba iqhubeke nokucwaninga in vivo ngemuva kokukhombisa ukuvinjelwa okuphansi kwe-SARS-CoV-2. Ucwaningo luye lwabonisa ukuthi ukuqala kwe-spike protein priming nge-transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) kubalulekile ekungeneni kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngokuxhumana ne-ACE2 receptor.
Ucwaningo lwe-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine nge-azithromycin noma ngaphandle kwayo lunemikhawulo emikhulu evimbela umphakathi wezokwelapha ukuba usebenzise lezi zindlela zokwelapha ngaphandle kokucwaninga okwengeziwe. I-Oseltamivir ayivimbeli i-SARS-CoV-2 in vitro futhi ayinandima eyaziwayo ekwelashweni kwe-COVID-19.
Isiphepho se-cytokine singaba inkinga ezigabeni zokugcina ze-COVID-19 enzima.
Kunobufakazi bokuthi i-hydroxychloroquine ingaba nezakhiwo zokulwa nesiphepho sama-cytokine. I-Tocilizumab ifakiwe emiyalweni yokwelashwa yiKhomishini Yezwe Yezempilo yaseChina ngemuva kokuqedwa kocwaningo oluncane.
Isingena esivivinyweni sesigaba sesibili esingahleliwe ezingeni likazwelonke e-Italy ngemva kokubonisa imiphumela emihle kubantu abanesifo esibi.
Uma kuhlanganiswa nokuhlolwa kwegazi kwe-serum ferritin ukuze kutholakale iziphepho zama-cytokine, kuhloswe ukuba kuvimbele ukuthuthukiswa okunjalo, okucatshangwa ukuthi kuyimbangela yokufa kwabanye abantu abathintekile.
I-interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yavunywa yi-FDA ngokusekelwe ezifundweni zecala emuva kokwelashwa kwe-steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome ebangelwa imbangela ehlukile, ukwelashwa kwamangqamuzana e-CAR T, ngo-2017.
Kuze kube manje, abukho ubufakazi obuhleliwe, obulawulwayo bokuthi i-tocilizumab iyindlela ephumelelayo yokwelapha i-CRS.
Ukudlulisela ama-antibody ahlanziwe futhi agxile akhiqizwa amasosha omzimba alabo asebephulukisiwe ku-COVID-19 kubantu abadinga wona kuyaphenywa njengendlela yokugoma engafakwanga imithi yokugoma.
Lendlela yahlolwa nge-SARS kodwa ayizange iphumelele.
Ukungasebenzi kwegciwane kuyindlela elindelwe yokusebenza lapho ukwelashwa kwama-antibody okungahambi kahle kungasiza khona ekuvikeleni i-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, kungenzeka kube nezinye izindlela, njengokuthonywa kwamangqamuzana okuxhomeke kumzimba omelene nawo kanye/noma i-phagocytosis.
Ezinye izindlela zokwelapha ngama-antibody, ngokwesibonelo, ukusebenzisa ama-antibody e-monoclonal akhiqizwayo, zisekuthuthukisweni.
Ukukhiqizwa kwe-serum yokutakula, okuyingxenye yamanzi yegazi leziguli esezilulame futhi equkethe ama-antibody akhethekile kuleligciwane, kungakhuphuka ukuze kusetshenziswe ngokushesha.
